602	Dirb Cheatsheet	Dirb Cheatsheet	# Dirb - Web Content Scanner\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n**Basit tarama (default wordlist):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com\n```\n\n**Özel wordlist ile:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt\n```\n\n**HTTPS tarama:**\n```\ndirb https://target.com\n```\n\n**Belirli port:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com:8080\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Proxy Kullanımı\n\n**HTTP proxy:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -p socks://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**Burp Suite üzerinden:**\n```\ndirb https://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n### Authentication\n\n**HTTP Basic Auth:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -u username:password\n```\n\n**Custom header ekleme:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN"\n```\n\n**Multiple header:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" -H "X-Custom: value"\n```\n\n### Cookie Kullanımı\n\n**Cookie ile tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -c "PHPSESSID=abc123; role=admin"\n```\n\n**Session tabanlı tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -c "SESSION=xyz789"\n```\n\n### User-Agent Değiştirme\n\n**Custom user-agent:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -a "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64)"\n```\n\n**Mobile user-agent:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -a "Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 14_0)"\n```\n\n### Extension Brute-forcing\n\n**Extension listesi:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -X .php,.txt,.html,.jsp,.asp\n```\n\n**Büyük harf extension:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -X .PHP,.Php,.pHp\n```\n\n### Recursion & Depth\n\n**Non-recursive (sadece root):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -r\n```\n\n**Recursive tarama (default):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com\n```\n\n### Rate-Limit / WAF Bypass\n\n**Delay ekleme (milliseconds):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -z 1000\n```\n\n**Yavaş tarama (WAF bypass):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -z 2000 -a "GoogleBot/2.1"\n```\n\n**Timeout ayarı:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -t\n```\n\n### Output Kaydetme\n\n**Sonuçları kaydet:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n**HTML format:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -o results.html\n```\n\n**Sessiz mod + output:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -S -o results.txt\n```\n\n### Custom Wordlist\n\n**Kendi wordlist'iniz:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com /path/to/custom-wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple wordlist (sırayla):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/big.txt\ndirb http://target.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt\n```\n\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`-a <user-agent>`**\n*User-Agent string'ini özelleştir.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -a "Mozilla/5.0..."\n```\n\n**`-c <cookie>`**\n*HTTP Cookie gönder.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -c "PHPSESSID=abc123"\n```\n\n**`-f`**\n*Fine-tuning: Her dizin için trailing slash (/) ile ve olmadan dene.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -f\n```\n\n**`-H <header>`**\n*Custom HTTP header ekle (multiple kullanılabilir).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN"\n```\n\n**`-i`**\n*Case-insensitive mod (büyük/küçük harf duyarsız).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -i\n```\n\n**`-l`**\n*Location header'ları da yazdır.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -l\n```\n\n**`-N <status_code>`**\n*Belirtilen HTTP status code'u gösterme.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -N 404\n```\n\n**`-o <output_file>`**\n*Sonuçları dosyaya kaydet.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n**`-p <proxy[:port]>`**\n*Proxy server kullan (HTTP veya SOCKS).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**`-r`**\n*Non-recursive mod (alt dizinlere girme).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -r\n```\n\n**`-R`**\n*Interactive recursion (her dizin için sor).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -R\n```\n\n**`-S`**\n*Silent mode (banner/başlık gösterme).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -S\n```\n\n**`-t`**\n*Timeout'u etkinleştir (connect/read timeout).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -t\n```\n\n**`-u <username:password>`**\n*HTTP Basic Authentication.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -u admin:pass123\n```\n\n**`-v`**\n*Verbose output (tüm response'ları göster).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -v\n```\n\n**`-w`**\n*Warning mesajlarını gösterme.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -w\n```\n\n**`-X <extensions>`**\n*Extension listesi ekle (virgülle ayır).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -X .php,.txt,.html\n```\n\n**`-z <milliseconds>`**\n*Her istek arasına delay ekle (milliseconds).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -z 1000\n```\n\n### Argüman Kombinasyonları\n\n**Stealth tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -z 2000 -a "Googlebot" -S -o stealth.txt\n```\n*-z: 2 saniye delay, -a: Bot UA, -S: Sessiz, -o: Kaydet*\n\n**Authenticated tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -u admin:pass -c "session=xyz" -H "X-CSRF-Token: abc"\n```\n*-u: Basic Auth, -c: Cookie, -H: Custom header*\n\n**Proxy + Extension:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080 -X .php,.bak -f\n```\n*-p: Burp proxy, -X: Extensions, -f: Trailing slash test*\n\n**Fast & Quiet:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -S -w -N 404 -o quick-scan.txt\n```\n*-S: Silent, -w: No warnings, -N: Ignore 404, -o: Save*\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Sessiz mod (banner gizle):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -S\n```\n*Output'u temiz tutar, banner/bilgi göstermez.*\n\n**Belirli status code gösterme:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -N 404\n```\n*404 dönen sonuçları göstermez.*\n\n**Case-insensitive tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -i\n```\n*admin, Admin, ADMIN aynı kabul edilir.*\n\n**Fine-tuning:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -f\n```\n*Her dizin için '/' ile ve '/' olmadan dener.*\n\n**Ignore eşleşen kelimeler:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -v\n```\n*Location header'daki redirect'leri gösterir.*\n\n**Speed mode (hızlı tarama):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -w\n```\n*Warning mesajları göstermez, daha hızlı.*\n\n**Tüm response göster:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -l\n```\n*Tüm yanıtları detaylı gösterir (debug için).*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: WAF Arkasında Dizin Bulma\n\n```\ndirb https://target.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt \\\n  -z 2000 \\\n  -a "Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1)" \\\n  -H "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1" \\\n  -o waf-bypass-results.txt\n```\n*2 saniye delay, GoogleBot UA, IP spoofing.*\n\n### Senaryo 2: Auth Zorunlu Dizinler\n\n```\ndirb https://target.com/admin \\\n  -c "PHPSESSID=valid_session_token; role=admin" \\\n  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGc..." \\\n  -X .php,.inc,.conf\n```\n*Cookie + JWT token ile authenticated tarama.*\n\n### Senaryo 3: Proxy Üzerinden Tarama (Burp)\n\n```\ndirb https://target.com \\\n  -p http://127.0.0.1:8080 \\\n  -c "session=abc123" \\\n  /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/big.txt \\\n  -o burp-scan.txt\n```\n*Tüm trafik Burp'ten geçer, manuel analiz için.*\n\n### Senaryo 4: Büyük Wordlist + Multi-Extension\n\n```\ndirb http://target.com \\\n  /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-big.txt \\\n  -X .php,.bak,.old,.txt,.inc,.zip,.sql \\\n  -z 500 \\\n  -S \\\n  -o massive-scan.txt\n```\n*220k+ kelime, 7 extension, sessiz mod.*\n\n### Senaryo 5: API Endpoint Discovery\n\n```\ndirb https://api.target.com/v1 \\\n  /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt \\\n  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\\n  -H "X-API-Key: your_key" \\\n  -X .json\n```\n*API-specific tarama.*\n\n### Senaryo 6: Backup File Hunting\n\n```\ndirb http://target.com \\\n  /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt \\\n  -X .bak,.old,.backup,.swp,.save,.1,.orig\n```\n*Backup dosya avcılığı.*\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Wordlist seçimi:**\n- Başlangıç: `common.txt` (4600 kelime)\n- Orta: `big.txt` (20k kelime)\n- Agresif: `directory-list-2.3-big.txt` (220k kelime)\n\n**2. Extension stratejisi:**\n- Backend tespiti yap (PHP, ASP, JSP)\n- İlgili extension'ları hedefle\n- .bak, .old, .zip ekle\n\n**3. Rate limiting:**\n- WAF varsa `-z 1000` ile başla\n- Engellenme yoksa hızlandır\n- Başarılı istek sonrası delay azalt\n\n**4. Proxy kullanımı:**\n- Her zaman Burp/ZAP ile tara\n- Manuel doğrulama için\n- False-positive tespiti\n\n**5. Cookie/Auth:**\n- Authenticated dizinler için gerekli\n- Session expire kontrolü\n- Multi-role test (user, admin, moderator)\n\n**6. Recursion:**\n- İlk tarama non-recursive `-r`\n- İlginç dizinler için recursive\n- Sonsuz döngü riski (symlink)\n\n**7. Output yönetimi:**\n- Her zaman `-o` ile kaydet\n- Timestamp ekle filename'e\n- Büyük taramalar için `-S` (silent)\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. Delay kullanmama:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb https://waf-protected.com\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb https://waf-protected.com -z 1500\n```\n*WAF/IDS tarafından engellenir.*\n\n**2. Extension eksikliği:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb http://target.com\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb http://target.com -X .php,.inc,.bak\n```\n*Önemli dosyaları kaçırırsın.*\n\n**3. 404 kontrolü yapmama:**\n```\n# Test et\ncurl -I http://target.com/nonexistentfile12345\n```\n*Bazı serverlar her şey için 200 döner (wildcard).*\n\n**4. Proxy olmadan tarama:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb https://target.com\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb https://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n*Manuel analiz/exploit imkanı kaçar.*\n\n**5. Recursive bombing:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (symlink loop varsa)\ndirb http://target.com /huge-wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb http://target.com -r /huge-wordlist.txt\n```\n*İlk tarama non-recursive yap.*\n\n**6. Wordlist seçimi:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (gereksiz büyük)\ndirb http://small-site.com /usr/share/seclists/.../raft-large.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (kademeli)\ndirb http://small-site.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt\n```\n*Küçük hedefler için küçük wordlist.*\n\n**7. User-Agent değiştirmeme:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb http://target.com\n\n# DOĞRU (WAF bypass)\ndirb http://target.com -a "Mozilla/5.0..."\n```\n*Default UA engellenebilir.*\n\n**8. Output kaydetmeme:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb http://target.com /huge-wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb http://target.com /huge-wordlist.txt -o scan_$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M).txt\n```\n*Terminal kapanırsa tüm sonuçlar kaybolur.*\n\n## Wordlist Konumları\n\n```\n/usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt          # 4600 entries\n/usr/share/dirb/wordlists/big.txt             # 20k entries\n/usr/share/dirb/wordlists/small.txt           # 980 entries\n/usr/share/dirb/wordlists/extensions_common.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/    # SecLists\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n- SSL hatası: Dirb SSL cert doğrulaması yapmaz (avantaj)\n- Wildcard detection: İlk 10 istekte pattern arar\n- Case-sensitive: `-i` flag'i kullan\n- Speed vs Stealth: `-z` değerini dengele\n- False-positive: Proxy'den manuel kontrol et\n- Multi-stage: common.txt → bulduklarını recursive tara\n	# Dirb - Web Content Scanner\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n**Basit tarama (default wordlist):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com\n```\n\n**Özel wordlist ile:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt\n```\n\n**HTTPS tarama:**\n```\ndirb https://target.com\n```\n\n**Belirli port:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com:8080\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Proxy Kullanımı\n\n**HTTP proxy:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -p socks://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**Burp Suite üzerinden:**\n```\ndirb https://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n### Authentication\n\n**HTTP Basic Auth:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -u username:password\n```\n\n**Custom header ekleme:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN"\n```\n\n**Multiple header:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" -H "X-Custom: value"\n```\n\n### Cookie Kullanımı\n\n**Cookie ile tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -c "PHPSESSID=abc123; role=admin"\n```\n\n**Session tabanlı tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -c "SESSION=xyz789"\n```\n\n### User-Agent Değiştirme\n\n**Custom user-agent:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -a "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64)"\n```\n\n**Mobile user-agent:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -a "Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 14_0)"\n```\n\n### Extension Brute-forcing\n\n**Extension listesi:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -X .php,.txt,.html,.jsp,.asp\n```\n\n**Büyük harf extension:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -X .PHP,.Php,.pHp\n```\n\n### Recursion & Depth\n\n**Non-recursive (sadece root):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -r\n```\n\n**Recursive tarama (default):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com\n```\n\n### Rate-Limit / WAF Bypass\n\n**Delay ekleme (milliseconds):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -z 1000\n```\n\n**Yavaş tarama (WAF bypass):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -z 2000 -a "GoogleBot/2.1"\n```\n\n**Timeout ayarı:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -t\n```\n\n### Output Kaydetme\n\n**Sonuçları kaydet:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n**HTML format:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -o results.html\n```\n\n**Sessiz mod + output:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -S -o results.txt\n```\n\n### Custom Wordlist\n\n**Kendi wordlist'iniz:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com /path/to/custom-wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple wordlist (sırayla):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/big.txt\ndirb http://target.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt\n```\n\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`-a <user-agent>`**\n*User-Agent string'ini özelleştir.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -a "Mozilla/5.0..."\n```\n\n**`-c <cookie>`**\n*HTTP Cookie gönder.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -c "PHPSESSID=abc123"\n```\n\n**`-f`**\n*Fine-tuning: Her dizin için trailing slash (/) ile ve olmadan dene.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -f\n```\n\n**`-H <header>`**\n*Custom HTTP header ekle (multiple kullanılabilir).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN"\n```\n\n**`-i`**\n*Case-insensitive mod (büyük/küçük harf duyarsız).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -i\n```\n\n**`-l`**\n*Location header'ları da yazdır.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -l\n```\n\n**`-N <status_code>`**\n*Belirtilen HTTP status code'u gösterme.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -N 404\n```\n\n**`-o <output_file>`**\n*Sonuçları dosyaya kaydet.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n**`-p <proxy[:port]>`**\n*Proxy server kullan (HTTP veya SOCKS).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**`-r`**\n*Non-recursive mod (alt dizinlere girme).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -r\n```\n\n**`-R`**\n*Interactive recursion (her dizin için sor).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -R\n```\n\n**`-S`**\n*Silent mode (banner/başlık gösterme).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -S\n```\n\n**`-t`**\n*Timeout'u etkinleştir (connect/read timeout).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -t\n```\n\n**`-u <username:password>`**\n*HTTP Basic Authentication.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -u admin:pass123\n```\n\n**`-v`**\n*Verbose output (tüm response'ları göster).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -v\n```\n\n**`-w`**\n*Warning mesajlarını gösterme.*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -w\n```\n\n**`-X <extensions>`**\n*Extension listesi ekle (virgülle ayır).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -X .php,.txt,.html\n```\n\n**`-z <milliseconds>`**\n*Her istek arasına delay ekle (milliseconds).*\n```\ndirb http://target.com -z 1000\n```\n\n### Argüman Kombinasyonları\n\n**Stealth tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -z 2000 -a "Googlebot" -S -o stealth.txt\n```\n*-z: 2 saniye delay, -a: Bot UA, -S: Sessiz, -o: Kaydet*\n\n**Authenticated tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -u admin:pass -c "session=xyz" -H "X-CSRF-Token: abc"\n```\n*-u: Basic Auth, -c: Cookie, -H: Custom header*\n\n**Proxy + Extension:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080 -X .php,.bak -f\n```\n*-p: Burp proxy, -X: Extensions, -f: Trailing slash test*\n\n**Fast & Quiet:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -S -w -N 404 -o quick-scan.txt\n```\n*-S: Silent, -w: No warnings, -N: Ignore 404, -o: Save*\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Sessiz mod (banner gizle):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -S\n```\n*Output'u temiz tutar, banner/bilgi göstermez.*\n\n**Belirli status code gösterme:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -N 404\n```\n*404 dönen sonuçları göstermez.*\n\n**Case-insensitive tarama:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -i\n```\n*admin, Admin, ADMIN aynı kabul edilir.*\n\n**Fine-tuning:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -f\n```\n*Her dizin için '/' ile ve '/' olmadan dener.*\n\n**Ignore eşleşen kelimeler:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -v\n```\n*Location header'daki redirect'leri gösterir.*\n\n**Speed mode (hızlı tarama):**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -w\n```\n*Warning mesajları göstermez, daha hızlı.*\n\n**Tüm response göster:**\n```\ndirb http://target.com -l\n```\n*Tüm yanıtları detaylı gösterir (debug için).*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: WAF Arkasında Dizin Bulma\n\n```\ndirb https://target.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt \\\n  -z 2000 \\\n  -a "Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1)" \\\n  -H "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1" \\\n  -o waf-bypass-results.txt\n```\n*2 saniye delay, GoogleBot UA, IP spoofing.*\n\n### Senaryo 2: Auth Zorunlu Dizinler\n\n```\ndirb https://target.com/admin \\\n  -c "PHPSESSID=valid_session_token; role=admin" \\\n  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGc..." \\\n  -X .php,.inc,.conf\n```\n*Cookie + JWT token ile authenticated tarama.*\n\n### Senaryo 3: Proxy Üzerinden Tarama (Burp)\n\n```\ndirb https://target.com \\\n  -p http://127.0.0.1:8080 \\\n  -c "session=abc123" \\\n  /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/big.txt \\\n  -o burp-scan.txt\n```\n*Tüm trafik Burp'ten geçer, manuel analiz için.*\n\n### Senaryo 4: Büyük Wordlist + Multi-Extension\n\n```\ndirb http://target.com \\\n  /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-big.txt \\\n  -X .php,.bak,.old,.txt,.inc,.zip,.sql \\\n  -z 500 \\\n  -S \\\n  -o massive-scan.txt\n```\n*220k+ kelime, 7 extension, sessiz mod.*\n\n### Senaryo 5: API Endpoint Discovery\n\n```\ndirb https://api.target.com/v1 \\\n  /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt \\\n  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\\n  -H "X-API-Key: your_key" \\\n  -X .json\n```\n*API-specific tarama.*\n\n### Senaryo 6: Backup File Hunting\n\n```\ndirb http://target.com \\\n  /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt \\\n  -X .bak,.old,.backup,.swp,.save,.1,.orig\n```\n*Backup dosya avcılığı.*\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Wordlist seçimi:**\n- Başlangıç: `common.txt` (4600 kelime)\n- Orta: `big.txt` (20k kelime)\n- Agresif: `directory-list-2.3-big.txt` (220k kelime)\n\n**2. Extension stratejisi:**\n- Backend tespiti yap (PHP, ASP, JSP)\n- İlgili extension'ları hedefle\n- .bak, .old, .zip ekle\n\n**3. Rate limiting:**\n- WAF varsa `-z 1000` ile başla\n- Engellenme yoksa hızlandır\n- Başarılı istek sonrası delay azalt\n\n**4. Proxy kullanımı:**\n- Her zaman Burp/ZAP ile tara\n- Manuel doğrulama için\n- False-positive tespiti\n\n**5. Cookie/Auth:**\n- Authenticated dizinler için gerekli\n- Session expire kontrolü\n- Multi-role test (user, admin, moderator)\n\n**6. Recursion:**\n- İlk tarama non-recursive `-r`\n- İlginç dizinler için recursive\n- Sonsuz döngü riski (symlink)\n\n**7. Output yönetimi:**\n- Her zaman `-o` ile kaydet\n- Timestamp ekle filename'e\n- Büyük taramalar için `-S` (silent)\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. Delay kullanmama:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb https://waf-protected.com\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb https://waf-protected.com -z 1500\n```\n*WAF/IDS tarafından engellenir.*\n\n**2. Extension eksikliği:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb http://target.com\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb http://target.com -X .php,.inc,.bak\n```\n*Önemli dosyaları kaçırırsın.*\n\n**3. 404 kontrolü yapmama:**\n```\n# Test et\ncurl -I http://target.com/nonexistentfile12345\n```\n*Bazı serverlar her şey için 200 döner (wildcard).*\n\n**4. Proxy olmadan tarama:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb https://target.com\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb https://target.com -p http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n*Manuel analiz/exploit imkanı kaçar.*\n\n**5. Recursive bombing:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (symlink loop varsa)\ndirb http://target.com /huge-wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb http://target.com -r /huge-wordlist.txt\n```\n*İlk tarama non-recursive yap.*\n\n**6. Wordlist seçimi:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (gereksiz büyük)\ndirb http://small-site.com /usr/share/seclists/.../raft-large.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (kademeli)\ndirb http://small-site.com /usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt\n```\n*Küçük hedefler için küçük wordlist.*\n\n**7. User-Agent değiştirmeme:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb http://target.com\n\n# DOĞRU (WAF bypass)\ndirb http://target.com -a "Mozilla/5.0..."\n```\n*Default UA engellenebilir.*\n\n**8. Output kaydetmeme:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\ndirb http://target.com /huge-wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\ndirb http://target.com /huge-wordlist.txt -o scan_$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M).txt\n```\n*Terminal kapanırsa tüm sonuçlar kaybolur.*\n\n## Wordlist Konumları\n\n```\n/usr/share/dirb/wordlists/common.txt          # 4600 entries\n/usr/share/dirb/wordlists/big.txt             # 20k entries\n/usr/share/dirb/wordlists/small.txt           # 980 entries\n/usr/share/dirb/wordlists/extensions_common.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/    # SecLists\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n- SSL hatası: Dirb SSL cert doğrulaması yapmaz (avantaj)\n- Wildcard detection: İlk 10 istekte pattern arar\n- Case-sensitive: `-i` flag'i kullan\n- Speed vs Stealth: `-z` değerini dengele\n- False-positive: Proxy'den manuel kontrol et\n- Multi-stage: common.txt → bulduklarını recursive tara\n	{dirb,bruteforce,directories,web-scanner,pentest}	{https://tools.kali.org/web-applications/dirb,http://dirb.sourceforge.net/}	192	2026-01-23 22:21:30.117	2026-01-23 22:21:30.117
603	Gobuster Cheatsheet	Gobuster Cheatsheet	# Gobuster - Advanced Directory, File, DNS & VHost Fuzzing\n\n**TR:** Gobuster, Go dilinde yazılmış, çoklu mode destekleyen hızlı ve hafif bir brute-force/fuzzing aracıdır.\n**EN:** Gobuster is a fast and lightweight brute-force/fuzzing tool written in Go, supporting multiple modes.\n\n## 1. What is Gobuster? / Gobuster Nedir?\n\n**TR:** **Dir, DNS, VHost ve Fuzz** modlarıyla directory, file, subdomain ve virtual host keşfi yapar.\n\n**EN:** Performs directory, file, subdomain and virtual host discovery with **Dir, DNS, VHost and Fuzz** modes.\n\n**TR - Temel Özellikler:**\n**EN - Key Features:**\n\n- Multi-threaded performance (high speed) / Çoklu thread performans (yüksek hız)\n- Low memory usage / Düşük bellek kullanımı\n- Advanced status-code/length/word/line filtering / Gelişmiş status-code/length/word/line filtreleme\n- Recursive directory discovery / Recursive directory keşfi\n- Wildcard detection / Wildcard tespiti\n- Proxy support (Burp/ZAP integration) / Proxy desteği (Burp/ZAP entegrasyonu)\n\n## 2. Installation / Kurulum\n\n```\napt install gobuster\n```\n\n```\ngo install github.com/OJ/gobuster/v3@latest\n```\n\n**TR - Version kontrol:**\n**EN - Version check:**\n```\ngobuster version\n```\n\n## 3. Basic Usage / Temel Kullanım\n\n### Simple Directory Brute-Force / Basit Directory Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `dir` → Directory/file brute-force mode / Directory/file brute-force modu\n- `-u` → Target URL / Hedef URL\n- `-w` → Wordlist file / Wordlist dosyası\n\n---\n\n### File Brute-Force (Extensions)\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -x php,txt,html,bak\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x` → Extension list (comma-separated) / Extension listesi (virgülle ayrılmış)\n- `php,txt,html,bak` → File extensions to test / Test edilecek dosya uzantıları\n\n---\n\n### DNS Subdomain Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `dns` → DNS subdomain discovery mode / DNS subdomain discovery modu\n- `-d` → Domain name / Domain adı\n- `-w` → Subdomain wordlist\n\n---\n\n### VHost Fuzzing\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster vhost -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `vhost` → Virtual host discovery mode / Virtual host discovery modu\n- `-u` → Base URL\n- `-w` → VHost wordlist\n\n---\n\n### Wordlist Usage / Wordlist Kullanımı\n\n**TR - Yaygın wordlistler:**\n**EN - Common wordlists:**\n```\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt                             # 4600 entries\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt     # 220k entries\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-files.txt  # 37k files\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n```\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-w` → Wordlist file path / Wordlist dosya yolu\n\n---\n\n### Status Code Filtering / Status Code Filtreleme\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-s` → Show only these status codes (whitelist) / Sadece bu status kodlarını göster (whitelist)\n- `200,204,301,302,307,401,403` → Relevant HTTP status codes / İlgili HTTP status kodları\n\n**Blacklist (negative filter) / Blacklist (negatif filtre):**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -b 404,403\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-b` → Don't show these status codes (blacklist) / Bu status kodlarını gösterme (blacklist)\n\n---\n\n### Recursive Discovery / Recursive Keşif\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -r\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-r` → Recursive mode (auto-enter found directories) / Recursive mode (bulunan dizinlere otomatik gir)\n\n**Depth control (3 levels) / Depth control (3 seviye):**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -r --depth 3\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--depth 3` → Maximum recursive depth / Maksimum recursive derinlik\n\n---\n\n### Output Saving / Output Kaydetme\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -o results.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-o` → Output file / Output dosyası\n\n**Quiet mode + output:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -q -o results.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-q` → Quiet mode (only results printed) / Quiet mode (sadece sonuçlar yazdırılır)\n\n---\n\n## 4. Advanced Usage / İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Multiple Extension Brute-Force / Çoklu Extension Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-words.txt -x php,asp,aspx,jsp,txt,bak,old,zip,tar,gz,sql,conf,inc,log\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x` → Extension list / Extension list\n- `php,asp,aspx,jsp,txt,bak,old,zip,tar,gz,sql,conf,inc,log` → Total 14 extensions / Toplam 14 extension\n\n---\n\n### Status/Length/Word/Line Based Filtering / Status/Length/Word/Line Tabanlı Filtreleme\n\n**Status code blacklist:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -b 404,403\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-b 404,403` → Hide 404 and 403 codes / 404 ve 403 kodlarını gizle\n\n---\n\n**Length-based filtering:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --exclude-length 1234\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--exclude-length 1234` → Hide results with response body length = 1234 / Response body length = 1234 olan sonuçları gizle\n\n**Multiple lengths:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --exclude-length 1234,5678\n```\n\n---\n\n### Proxy Through Gobuster (Burp/ZAP) / Proxy Üzerinden Gobuster (Burp/ZAP)\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--proxy` → HTTP proxy address (Burp/ZAP) / HTTP proxy adresi (Burp/ZAP)\n\n---\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --proxy socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--proxy socks5://...` → SOCKS5 proxy\n\n---\n\n### DNS Wildcard Detection / DNS Wildcard Tespiti\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w subdomains.txt --wildcard\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--wildcard` → Wildcard DNS detection enabled / Wildcard DNS detection etkin\n\n**TR:** *Gobuster wildcard pattern tespit ederse uyarır ve false-positive'leri filtreler.*\n**EN:** *Gobuster warns if wildcard pattern detected and filters false-positives.*\n\n---\n\n### Rate-Limit Bypass\n\n**Slow fuzzing (delay):**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --delay 500ms -t 10\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--delay 500ms` → 500ms delay between each request / Her istek arasında 500ms gecikme\n- `-t 10` → Low thread count (10) / Thread sayısı düşük (10)\n\n---\n\n**Custom User-Agent:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -a "Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1; +http://www.google.com/bot.html)"\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-a` → Custom User-Agent\n\n---\n\n## 5. Annotated Commands (EXTENSIVE LIST) / Açıklamalı Komutlar (GENİŞ LİSTE)\n\n### Command 1: Simple Directory Brute-Force / Komut 1: Basit Directory Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://192.168.1.10 -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\nHedef URL'de yaygın directory adlarını test eder. 4600 kelimelik küçük wordlist ile hızlı tarama.\n\n**EN - Description:**\nTests common directory names on the target URL. Fast scan with 4600-word small wordlist.\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `dir` → Directory mode / Directory mod\n- `-u http://192.168.1.10` → Target URL / Hedef URL\n- `-w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt` → Wordlist file / Wordlist dosyası\n\n---\n\n### Command 2: Extension Brute-Force / Komut 2: Extension Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -x php,txt,html\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\nDirectory + PHP/TXT/HTML dosya keşfi. Her kelime için `admin`, `admin.php`, `admin.txt`, `admin.html` test edilir.\n\n**EN - Description:**\nDirectory + PHP/TXT/HTML file discovery. Tests `admin`, `admin.php`, `admin.txt`, `admin.html` for each word.\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x php,txt,html` → Extension list to test / Test edilecek extension listesi\n\n---\n\n### Command 3: Status Code Filtering / Komut 3: Status Code Filtreleme\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\nSadece ilgili status kodlarını göster. 404, 500 gibi noise gösterilmez.\n\n**EN - Description:**\nShow only relevant status codes. Noise like 404, 500 is not shown.\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403` → Whitelist status codes\n\n---\n\n## 6. Real Pentest Scenarios / Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Scenario 1: Large-Scale Directory Brute-Force / Senaryo 1: Büyük Ölçekli Directory Brute-Force\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nComprehensive directory discovery with 220k wordlist / 220k wordlist ile kapsamlı directory keşfi\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -x php,html,txt,bak -t 100 --timeout 15s -o big-scan.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- 220,000 words + 4 extensions = 880,000 requests / 220,000 kelime + 4 extension = 880,000 request\n- ~30-60 minutes with 100 threads / 100 thread ile ~30-60 dakika\n- 15s timeout (for slow servers) / Timeout 15s (yavaş server için)\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-w ...medium.txt` → 220k wordlist\n- `-x php,html,txt,bak` → 4 extensions\n- `-t 100` → 100 threads\n- `--timeout 15s` → 15 second timeout / 15 saniye timeout\n\n---\n\n### Scenario 2: Backup File Hunting with Multiple Extensions / Senaryo 2: Çoklu Extension ile Backup File Avı\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nFind backup files (source code leak) / Yedekleme dosyalarını bul (source code sızıntısı)\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-files.txt -x bak,old,backup,~,swp,tmp,save,orig,1,2,copy -t 50 -o backup-files.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- Backup extensions like `.bak`, `.old`, `~`, `.swp` / `.bak`, `.old`, `~`, `.swp` gibi backup uzantıları\n- 37k file wordlist\n- Source code leak detection / Source code leak tespiti\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x bak,old,backup,~,swp,tmp,save,orig,1,2,copy` → 11 backup extensions\n\n---\n\n### Scenario 3: Source Code Leak Discovery (.git, .svn, .env) / Senaryo 3: Source Code Sızıntısı Keşfi (.git, .svn, .env)\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nFind Git, SVN, .env files / Git, SVN, .env dosyalarını bul\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/web-all.txt -x git,svn,env,DS_Store,htaccess,htpasswd,sql,log,conf -t 50 -o source-leak.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- Sensitive files like `.git/HEAD`, `.git/config`, `.env`, `.htaccess` / `.git/HEAD`, `.git/config`, `.env`, `.htaccess` gibi hassas dosyalar\n- Web server misconfiguration detection / Web sunucu misconfiguration tespiti\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x git,svn,env,DS_Store,htaccess,htpasswd,sql,log,conf` → Sensitive file extensions / Hassas dosya uzantıları\n\n**TR - Manuel kontrol:**\n**EN - Manual check:**\n```\ncurl http://target.com/.git/HEAD\ncurl http://target.com/.env\n```\n\n---\n\n### Scenario 4: DNS Zone Discovery + Wildcard Bypass / Senaryo 4: DNS Zone Keşfi + Wildcard Bypass\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nSubdomain discovery + wildcard DNS filtering / Subdomain keşfi + wildcard DNS filtering\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-110000.txt --wildcard -i -o dns-scan.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- 110,000 subdomain test\n- Automatic wildcard DNS detection and filtering / Wildcard DNS otomatik tespit ve filtreleme\n- Show IP addresses (`-i`) / IP adresleri göster (`-i`)\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-d target.com` → Domain\n- `--wildcard` → Wildcard DNS detection\n- `-i` → Show IPs\n\n**TR - Wildcard test:**\n**EN - Wildcard test:**\n```\ndig randomnonexistent12345.target.com\n```\n**TR:** *Eğer response dönüyorsa wildcard aktif. Gobuster otomatik filtreler.*\n**EN:** *If response returns, wildcard is active. Gobuster automatically filters.*\n\n---\n\n### Scenario 5: VHost Brute-Force for Hidden Domains / Senaryo 5: VHost Brute-Force ile Gizli Domain Bulma\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nSites accessible with different Host header on the same IP / Aynı IP'de farklı Host header ile erişilebilen siteler\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster vhost -u http://192.168.1.10 -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt --append-domain -t 50 -o vhosts.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- Virtual host discovery\n- Finding internal panels, dev, staging sites / Internal panel, dev, staging siteleri bulma\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `vhost` → VHost mode\n- `--append-domain` → Automatically append `.192.168.1.10` (manual domain for internal network) / `.192.168.1.10` ekle (iç ağda manuel domain)\n\n**TR - Manuel test:**\n**EN - Manual test:**\n```\ncurl -H "Host: admin.target.local" http://192.168.1.10\n```\n\n---\n\n## 7. Basic Arguments / Temel Argümanlar\n\n### `-u <URL>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nTarget URL / Hedef URL\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-w <wordlist>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nWordlist file path / Wordlist dosya yolu\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-t <threads>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nConcurrent thread count (default: 10) / Concurrent thread sayısı (default: 10)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -t 50\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-x <extensions>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nFile extensions (comma-separated) / Dosya uzantıları (virgülle ayrılmış)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -x php,txt,html\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-o <output>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nOutput file / Output dosyası\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -o results.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-q`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nQuiet mode (results only) / Quiet mode (sadece sonuçlar)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -q\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-k`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nSkip SSL certificate verification / SSL certificate verification kapatma\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u https://target.com -w wordlist.txt -k\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-s <status codes>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nShow only these status codes (whitelist) / Sadece bu status kodlarını göster (whitelist)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200,301,302\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-b <status codes>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nDon't show these status codes (blacklist) / Bu status kodlarını gösterme (blacklist)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -b 404,403\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-r`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nFollow redirects\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -r\n```\n\n---\n\n## 8. Best Practices (Expert Level) / Best Practices (Uzman Seviye)\n\n### Correct Wordlist Selection (SecLists Recommendations) / Doğru Wordlist Seçimi (SecLists Önerileri)\n\n**TR - Başlangıç (Hızlı):**\n**EN - Beginner (Fast):**\n```\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt                # 4,600\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt # 4,700\n```\n\n**TR - Orta (Balanced):**\n**EN - Medium (Balanced):**\n```\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories.txt  # 30k\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-files.txt        # 17k\n```\n\n**TR - Agresif (Kapsamlı):**\n**EN - Aggressive (Comprehensive):**\n```\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt  # 220k\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-words.txt # 107k\n```\n\n**DNS:**\n```\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt   # 5k\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-110000.txt # 110k\n```\n\n---\n\n### Status-Code Filtering Strategies / Status-Code Filtreleme Stratejileri\n\n**Whitelist approach (recommended) / Whitelist yaklaşımı (önerilen):**\n```\n-s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403\n```\n**TR:** *Sadece ilgili kodları göster, noise azalt.*\n**EN:** *Show only relevant codes, reduce noise.*\n\n---\n\n**Blacklist approach / Blacklist yaklaşımı:**\n```\n-b 404,403\n```\n**TR:** *404 ve 403'ü gizle, geriye kalanları göster.*\n**EN:** *Hide 404 and 403, show the rest.*\n\n---\n\n**Wildcard test:**\n```\ncurl -I http://target.com/nonexistentpath12345\n```\n**TR:** *Response status ve length kontrol et. Eğer 200 dönüyorsa wildcard aktif.*\n**EN:** *Check response status and length. If 200 returns, wildcard is active.*\n\n---\n\n## 9. Common Mistakes / Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n### 1. Too High Threads → Target Crash / Çok Yüksek Thread → Hedef Çökmesi\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w huge-wordlist.txt -t 500\n```\n**TR:** *500 thread → Server crash, network congestion*\n**EN:** *500 threads → Server crash, network congestion*\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w huge-wordlist.txt -t 50 --timeout 10s\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Wrong Status-Code Filtering / Yanlış Status-Code Filtreleme\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200\n```\n**TR:** *301, 302, 403 gibi önemli kodları kaçırırsın*\n**EN:** *You miss important codes like 301, 302, 403*\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Wordlist Doesn't Match Technology (PHP/ASP) / Wordlist Teknolojisiyle Uyuşmuyor (PHP/ASP)\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\n# ASP.NET backend, PHP wordlist\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w php-wordlist.txt -x php\n```\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w generic-wordlist.txt -x asp,aspx,config\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Recursive Mode Not Used Correctly / Recursive Mod Doğru Kullanılmıyor\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w huge-wordlist.txt -r\n```\n**TR:** *Sonsuz döngü riski, çok uzun sürer*\n**EN:** *Infinite loop risk, takes too long*\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\n# First scan non-recursive / İlk tarama non-recursive\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -o dirs.txt\n\n# Manual recursive when interesting dirs found / İlginç dizinler bulunca manuel recursive\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com/admin -w wordlist.txt -r --depth 2\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Ignoring Wildcard DNS / Wildcard DNS Göz Ardı Etmek\n\n**Test:**\n```\ndig randomnonexistent12345.target.com\n```\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w subdomains.txt\n```\n**TR:** *Wildcard aktifse tüm sonuçlar false-positive*\n**EN:** *If wildcard active, all results are false-positive*\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w subdomains.txt --wildcard\n```\n\n---\n\n## 10. Tips / İpuçları\n\n**Version check / Version kontrol:**\n```\ngobuster version\n```\n\n---\n\n**Help:**\n```\ngobuster help\ngobuster dir --help\ngobuster dns --help\ngobuster vhost --help\ngobuster fuzz --help\n```\n\n---\n\n**Wordlist line count:**\n```\nwc -l /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n**TR - Tahmini süre:**\n**EN - Estimated time:**\n```\n# Wordlist: 10,000 lines\n# Extensions: 3 (php,txt,html)\n# Total requests: 10,000 * 3 = 30,000\n# Threads: 50\n# Estimated: 30,000 / 50 = 600 seconds ≈ 10 minutes / dakika\n```\n\n---\n\n**TR - Real-time progress:**\n**EN - Real-time progress:**\n**TR:** Gobuster otomatik progress bar gösterir:\n**EN:** Gobuster automatically shows progress bar:\n```\nProgress: 1234 / 10000 (12.34%)\n```\n\n---\n\n**Quick wildcard test:**\n```\ncurl -I http://target.com/$(openssl rand -hex 16)\n```\n\n---\n\n**DNS resolver test:**\n```\ndig @8.8.8.8 target.com\n```\n\n---\n\n**Proxy test:**\n```\ncurl --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080 http://target.com\n```\n\n---\n\n## 11. Resources / Kaynaklar\n\n- **GitHub:** https://github.com/OJ/gobuster\n- **SecLists Wordlists:** https://github.com/danielmiessler/SecLists\n- **OWASP Testing Guide:** https://owasp.org/www-project-web-security-testing-guide/\n	# Gobuster - Advanced Directory, File, DNS & VHost Fuzzing\n\n**TR:** Gobuster, Go dilinde yazılmış, çoklu mode destekleyen hızlı ve hafif bir brute-force/fuzzing aracıdır.\n**EN:** Gobuster is a fast and lightweight brute-force/fuzzing tool written in Go, supporting multiple modes.\n\n## 1. What is Gobuster? / Gobuster Nedir?\n\n**TR:** **Dir, DNS, VHost ve Fuzz** modlarıyla directory, file, subdomain ve virtual host keşfi yapar.\n\n**EN:** Performs directory, file, subdomain and virtual host discovery with **Dir, DNS, VHost and Fuzz** modes.\n\n**TR - Temel Özellikler:**\n**EN - Key Features:**\n\n- Multi-threaded performance (high speed) / Çoklu thread performans (yüksek hız)\n- Low memory usage / Düşük bellek kullanımı\n- Advanced status-code/length/word/line filtering / Gelişmiş status-code/length/word/line filtreleme\n- Recursive directory discovery / Recursive directory keşfi\n- Wildcard detection / Wildcard tespiti\n- Proxy support (Burp/ZAP integration) / Proxy desteği (Burp/ZAP entegrasyonu)\n\n## 2. Installation / Kurulum\n\n```\napt install gobuster\n```\n\n```\ngo install github.com/OJ/gobuster/v3@latest\n```\n\n**TR - Version kontrol:**\n**EN - Version check:**\n```\ngobuster version\n```\n\n## 3. Basic Usage / Temel Kullanım\n\n### Simple Directory Brute-Force / Basit Directory Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `dir` → Directory/file brute-force mode / Directory/file brute-force modu\n- `-u` → Target URL / Hedef URL\n- `-w` → Wordlist file / Wordlist dosyası\n\n---\n\n### File Brute-Force (Extensions)\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -x php,txt,html,bak\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x` → Extension list (comma-separated) / Extension listesi (virgülle ayrılmış)\n- `php,txt,html,bak` → File extensions to test / Test edilecek dosya uzantıları\n\n---\n\n### DNS Subdomain Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `dns` → DNS subdomain discovery mode / DNS subdomain discovery modu\n- `-d` → Domain name / Domain adı\n- `-w` → Subdomain wordlist\n\n---\n\n### VHost Fuzzing\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster vhost -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `vhost` → Virtual host discovery mode / Virtual host discovery modu\n- `-u` → Base URL\n- `-w` → VHost wordlist\n\n---\n\n### Wordlist Usage / Wordlist Kullanımı\n\n**TR - Yaygın wordlistler:**\n**EN - Common wordlists:**\n```\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt                             # 4600 entries\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt     # 220k entries\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-files.txt  # 37k files\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n```\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-w` → Wordlist file path / Wordlist dosya yolu\n\n---\n\n### Status Code Filtering / Status Code Filtreleme\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-s` → Show only these status codes (whitelist) / Sadece bu status kodlarını göster (whitelist)\n- `200,204,301,302,307,401,403` → Relevant HTTP status codes / İlgili HTTP status kodları\n\n**Blacklist (negative filter) / Blacklist (negatif filtre):**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -b 404,403\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-b` → Don't show these status codes (blacklist) / Bu status kodlarını gösterme (blacklist)\n\n---\n\n### Recursive Discovery / Recursive Keşif\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -r\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-r` → Recursive mode (auto-enter found directories) / Recursive mode (bulunan dizinlere otomatik gir)\n\n**Depth control (3 levels) / Depth control (3 seviye):**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -r --depth 3\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--depth 3` → Maximum recursive depth / Maksimum recursive derinlik\n\n---\n\n### Output Saving / Output Kaydetme\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -o results.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-o` → Output file / Output dosyası\n\n**Quiet mode + output:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -q -o results.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-q` → Quiet mode (only results printed) / Quiet mode (sadece sonuçlar yazdırılır)\n\n---\n\n## 4. Advanced Usage / İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Multiple Extension Brute-Force / Çoklu Extension Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-words.txt -x php,asp,aspx,jsp,txt,bak,old,zip,tar,gz,sql,conf,inc,log\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x` → Extension list / Extension list\n- `php,asp,aspx,jsp,txt,bak,old,zip,tar,gz,sql,conf,inc,log` → Total 14 extensions / Toplam 14 extension\n\n---\n\n### Status/Length/Word/Line Based Filtering / Status/Length/Word/Line Tabanlı Filtreleme\n\n**Status code blacklist:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -b 404,403\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-b 404,403` → Hide 404 and 403 codes / 404 ve 403 kodlarını gizle\n\n---\n\n**Length-based filtering:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --exclude-length 1234\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--exclude-length 1234` → Hide results with response body length = 1234 / Response body length = 1234 olan sonuçları gizle\n\n**Multiple lengths:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --exclude-length 1234,5678\n```\n\n---\n\n### Proxy Through Gobuster (Burp/ZAP) / Proxy Üzerinden Gobuster (Burp/ZAP)\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--proxy` → HTTP proxy address (Burp/ZAP) / HTTP proxy adresi (Burp/ZAP)\n\n---\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --proxy socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--proxy socks5://...` → SOCKS5 proxy\n\n---\n\n### DNS Wildcard Detection / DNS Wildcard Tespiti\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w subdomains.txt --wildcard\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--wildcard` → Wildcard DNS detection enabled / Wildcard DNS detection etkin\n\n**TR:** *Gobuster wildcard pattern tespit ederse uyarır ve false-positive'leri filtreler.*\n**EN:** *Gobuster warns if wildcard pattern detected and filters false-positives.*\n\n---\n\n### Rate-Limit Bypass\n\n**Slow fuzzing (delay):**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt --delay 500ms -t 10\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `--delay 500ms` → 500ms delay between each request / Her istek arasında 500ms gecikme\n- `-t 10` → Low thread count (10) / Thread sayısı düşük (10)\n\n---\n\n**Custom User-Agent:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -a "Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1; +http://www.google.com/bot.html)"\n```\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-a` → Custom User-Agent\n\n---\n\n## 5. Annotated Commands (EXTENSIVE LIST) / Açıklamalı Komutlar (GENİŞ LİSTE)\n\n### Command 1: Simple Directory Brute-Force / Komut 1: Basit Directory Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://192.168.1.10 -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\nHedef URL'de yaygın directory adlarını test eder. 4600 kelimelik küçük wordlist ile hızlı tarama.\n\n**EN - Description:**\nTests common directory names on the target URL. Fast scan with 4600-word small wordlist.\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `dir` → Directory mode / Directory mod\n- `-u http://192.168.1.10` → Target URL / Hedef URL\n- `-w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt` → Wordlist file / Wordlist dosyası\n\n---\n\n### Command 2: Extension Brute-Force / Komut 2: Extension Brute-Force\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -x php,txt,html\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\nDirectory + PHP/TXT/HTML dosya keşfi. Her kelime için `admin`, `admin.php`, `admin.txt`, `admin.html` test edilir.\n\n**EN - Description:**\nDirectory + PHP/TXT/HTML file discovery. Tests `admin`, `admin.php`, `admin.txt`, `admin.html` for each word.\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x php,txt,html` → Extension list to test / Test edilecek extension listesi\n\n---\n\n### Command 3: Status Code Filtering / Komut 3: Status Code Filtreleme\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\nSadece ilgili status kodlarını göster. 404, 500 gibi noise gösterilmez.\n\n**EN - Description:**\nShow only relevant status codes. Noise like 404, 500 is not shown.\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403` → Whitelist status codes\n\n---\n\n## 6. Real Pentest Scenarios / Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Scenario 1: Large-Scale Directory Brute-Force / Senaryo 1: Büyük Ölçekli Directory Brute-Force\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nComprehensive directory discovery with 220k wordlist / 220k wordlist ile kapsamlı directory keşfi\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -x php,html,txt,bak -t 100 --timeout 15s -o big-scan.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- 220,000 words + 4 extensions = 880,000 requests / 220,000 kelime + 4 extension = 880,000 request\n- ~30-60 minutes with 100 threads / 100 thread ile ~30-60 dakika\n- 15s timeout (for slow servers) / Timeout 15s (yavaş server için)\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-w ...medium.txt` → 220k wordlist\n- `-x php,html,txt,bak` → 4 extensions\n- `-t 100` → 100 threads\n- `--timeout 15s` → 15 second timeout / 15 saniye timeout\n\n---\n\n### Scenario 2: Backup File Hunting with Multiple Extensions / Senaryo 2: Çoklu Extension ile Backup File Avı\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nFind backup files (source code leak) / Yedekleme dosyalarını bul (source code sızıntısı)\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-files.txt -x bak,old,backup,~,swp,tmp,save,orig,1,2,copy -t 50 -o backup-files.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- Backup extensions like `.bak`, `.old`, `~`, `.swp` / `.bak`, `.old`, `~`, `.swp` gibi backup uzantıları\n- 37k file wordlist\n- Source code leak detection / Source code leak tespiti\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x bak,old,backup,~,swp,tmp,save,orig,1,2,copy` → 11 backup extensions\n\n---\n\n### Scenario 3: Source Code Leak Discovery (.git, .svn, .env) / Senaryo 3: Source Code Sızıntısı Keşfi (.git, .svn, .env)\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nFind Git, SVN, .env files / Git, SVN, .env dosyalarını bul\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/web-all.txt -x git,svn,env,DS_Store,htaccess,htpasswd,sql,log,conf -t 50 -o source-leak.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- Sensitive files like `.git/HEAD`, `.git/config`, `.env`, `.htaccess` / `.git/HEAD`, `.git/config`, `.env`, `.htaccess` gibi hassas dosyalar\n- Web server misconfiguration detection / Web sunucu misconfiguration tespiti\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-x git,svn,env,DS_Store,htaccess,htpasswd,sql,log,conf` → Sensitive file extensions / Hassas dosya uzantıları\n\n**TR - Manuel kontrol:**\n**EN - Manual check:**\n```\ncurl http://target.com/.git/HEAD\ncurl http://target.com/.env\n```\n\n---\n\n### Scenario 4: DNS Zone Discovery + Wildcard Bypass / Senaryo 4: DNS Zone Keşfi + Wildcard Bypass\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nSubdomain discovery + wildcard DNS filtering / Subdomain keşfi + wildcard DNS filtering\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-110000.txt --wildcard -i -o dns-scan.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- 110,000 subdomain test\n- Automatic wildcard DNS detection and filtering / Wildcard DNS otomatik tespit ve filtreleme\n- Show IP addresses (`-i`) / IP adresleri göster (`-i`)\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `-d target.com` → Domain\n- `--wildcard` → Wildcard DNS detection\n- `-i` → Show IPs\n\n**TR - Wildcard test:**\n**EN - Wildcard test:**\n```\ndig randomnonexistent12345.target.com\n```\n**TR:** *Eğer response dönüyorsa wildcard aktif. Gobuster otomatik filtreler.*\n**EN:** *If response returns, wildcard is active. Gobuster automatically filters.*\n\n---\n\n### Scenario 5: VHost Brute-Force for Hidden Domains / Senaryo 5: VHost Brute-Force ile Gizli Domain Bulma\n\n**TR - Hedef:**  \n**EN - Objective:**  \nSites accessible with different Host header on the same IP / Aynı IP'de farklı Host header ile erişilebilen siteler\n\n**Command / Komut:**\n```\ngobuster vhost -u http://192.168.1.10 -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt --append-domain -t 50 -o vhosts.txt\n```\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**\n**EN - Description:**\n- Virtual host discovery\n- Finding internal panels, dev, staging sites / Internal panel, dev, staging siteleri bulma\n\n**TR - Argüman Açıklamaları:**\n**EN - Argument Explanations:**\n- `vhost` → VHost mode\n- `--append-domain` → Automatically append `.192.168.1.10` (manual domain for internal network) / `.192.168.1.10` ekle (iç ağda manuel domain)\n\n**TR - Manuel test:**\n**EN - Manual test:**\n```\ncurl -H "Host: admin.target.local" http://192.168.1.10\n```\n\n---\n\n## 7. Basic Arguments / Temel Argümanlar\n\n### `-u <URL>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nTarget URL / Hedef URL\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-w <wordlist>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nWordlist file path / Wordlist dosya yolu\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-t <threads>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nConcurrent thread count (default: 10) / Concurrent thread sayısı (default: 10)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -t 50\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-x <extensions>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nFile extensions (comma-separated) / Dosya uzantıları (virgülle ayrılmış)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -x php,txt,html\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-o <output>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nOutput file / Output dosyası\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -o results.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-q`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nQuiet mode (results only) / Quiet mode (sadece sonuçlar)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -q\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-k`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nSkip SSL certificate verification / SSL certificate verification kapatma\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u https://target.com -w wordlist.txt -k\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-s <status codes>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nShow only these status codes (whitelist) / Sadece bu status kodlarını göster (whitelist)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200,301,302\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-b <status codes>`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nDon't show these status codes (blacklist) / Bu status kodlarını gösterme (blacklist)\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -b 404,403\n```\n\n---\n\n### `-r`\n\n**TR - Açıklama:**  \n**EN - Description:**  \nFollow redirects\n\n**Example / Örnek:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -r\n```\n\n---\n\n## 8. Best Practices (Expert Level) / Best Practices (Uzman Seviye)\n\n### Correct Wordlist Selection (SecLists Recommendations) / Doğru Wordlist Seçimi (SecLists Önerileri)\n\n**TR - Başlangıç (Hızlı):**\n**EN - Beginner (Fast):**\n```\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt                # 4,600\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt # 4,700\n```\n\n**TR - Orta (Balanced):**\n**EN - Medium (Balanced):**\n```\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories.txt  # 30k\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-files.txt        # 17k\n```\n\n**TR - Agresif (Kapsamlı):**\n**EN - Aggressive (Comprehensive):**\n```\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt  # 220k\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-words.txt # 107k\n```\n\n**DNS:**\n```\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt   # 5k\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-110000.txt # 110k\n```\n\n---\n\n### Status-Code Filtering Strategies / Status-Code Filtreleme Stratejileri\n\n**Whitelist approach (recommended) / Whitelist yaklaşımı (önerilen):**\n```\n-s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403\n```\n**TR:** *Sadece ilgili kodları göster, noise azalt.*\n**EN:** *Show only relevant codes, reduce noise.*\n\n---\n\n**Blacklist approach / Blacklist yaklaşımı:**\n```\n-b 404,403\n```\n**TR:** *404 ve 403'ü gizle, geriye kalanları göster.*\n**EN:** *Hide 404 and 403, show the rest.*\n\n---\n\n**Wildcard test:**\n```\ncurl -I http://target.com/nonexistentpath12345\n```\n**TR:** *Response status ve length kontrol et. Eğer 200 dönüyorsa wildcard aktif.*\n**EN:** *Check response status and length. If 200 returns, wildcard is active.*\n\n---\n\n## 9. Common Mistakes / Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n### 1. Too High Threads → Target Crash / Çok Yüksek Thread → Hedef Çökmesi\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w huge-wordlist.txt -t 500\n```\n**TR:** *500 thread → Server crash, network congestion*\n**EN:** *500 threads → Server crash, network congestion*\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w huge-wordlist.txt -t 50 --timeout 10s\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Wrong Status-Code Filtering / Yanlış Status-Code Filtreleme\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200\n```\n**TR:** *301, 302, 403 gibi önemli kodları kaçırırsın*\n**EN:** *You miss important codes like 301, 302, 403*\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -s 200,204,301,302,307,401,403\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Wordlist Doesn't Match Technology (PHP/ASP) / Wordlist Teknolojisiyle Uyuşmuyor (PHP/ASP)\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\n# ASP.NET backend, PHP wordlist\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w php-wordlist.txt -x php\n```\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w generic-wordlist.txt -x asp,aspx,config\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Recursive Mode Not Used Correctly / Recursive Mod Doğru Kullanılmıyor\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w huge-wordlist.txt -r\n```\n**TR:** *Sonsuz döngü riski, çok uzun sürer*\n**EN:** *Infinite loop risk, takes too long*\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\n# First scan non-recursive / İlk tarama non-recursive\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com -w wordlist.txt -o dirs.txt\n\n# Manual recursive when interesting dirs found / İlginç dizinler bulunca manuel recursive\ngobuster dir -u http://target.com/admin -w wordlist.txt -r --depth 2\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Ignoring Wildcard DNS / Wildcard DNS Göz Ardı Etmek\n\n**Test:**\n```\ndig randomnonexistent12345.target.com\n```\n\n**WRONG / YANLIŞ:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w subdomains.txt\n```\n**TR:** *Wildcard aktifse tüm sonuçlar false-positive*\n**EN:** *If wildcard active, all results are false-positive*\n\n**CORRECT / DOĞRU:**\n```\ngobuster dns -d target.com -w subdomains.txt --wildcard\n```\n\n---\n\n## 10. Tips / İpuçları\n\n**Version check / Version kontrol:**\n```\ngobuster version\n```\n\n---\n\n**Help:**\n```\ngobuster help\ngobuster dir --help\ngobuster dns --help\ngobuster vhost --help\ngobuster fuzz --help\n```\n\n---\n\n**Wordlist line count:**\n```\nwc -l /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n**TR - Tahmini süre:**\n**EN - Estimated time:**\n```\n# Wordlist: 10,000 lines\n# Extensions: 3 (php,txt,html)\n# Total requests: 10,000 * 3 = 30,000\n# Threads: 50\n# Estimated: 30,000 / 50 = 600 seconds ≈ 10 minutes / dakika\n```\n\n---\n\n**TR - Real-time progress:**\n**EN - Real-time progress:**\n**TR:** Gobuster otomatik progress bar gösterir:\n**EN:** Gobuster automatically shows progress bar:\n```\nProgress: 1234 / 10000 (12.34%)\n```\n\n---\n\n**Quick wildcard test:**\n```\ncurl -I http://target.com/$(openssl rand -hex 16)\n```\n\n---\n\n**DNS resolver test:**\n```\ndig @8.8.8.8 target.com\n```\n\n---\n\n**Proxy test:**\n```\ncurl --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080 http://target.com\n```\n\n---\n\n## 11. Resources / Kaynaklar\n\n- **GitHub:** https://github.com/OJ/gobuster\n- **SecLists Wordlists:** https://github.com/danielmiessler/SecLists\n- **OWASP Testing Guide:** https://owasp.org/www-project-web-security-testing-guide/\n	{gobuster,dir,dns,vhost,fuzz,directory-bruteforce,subdomain,pentest}	{https://github.com/OJ/gobuster}	192	2026-01-23 22:21:30.128	2026-01-23 22:21:30.128
