612	Amass Cheatsheet	Amass Cheatsheet	# OWASP Amass - Advanced Network Mapping\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n### Pasif Keşif\n\n**Pasif subdomain enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com\n```\n\n**Pasif + kaynak göster:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -src\n```\n\n**Sadece belirli kaynaklar:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -include crtsh,virustotal\n```\n\n### Aktif Keşif\n\n**Aktif enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com\n```\n\n**Aktif + DNS resolution:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -p 80,443,8080\n```\n\n### Domain Enumeration\n\n**Basit enum:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n\n**Multiple domains:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com,example.com\n```\n\n**Domain list dosyası:**\n```\namass enum -df domains.txt\n```\n\n### Brute-Force Subdomain Keşfi\n\n**Brute-force wordlist:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/subdomains.txt\n```\n\n**Brute-force + min threshold:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -min-for-recursive 3\n```\n\n### Recursive Enumeration\n\n**Recursive discovery:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 2\n```\n\n**Recursive + brute-force:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -min-for-recursive 3\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Pasif + Aktif Birleşik Enumeration\n\n**Hybrid mode:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n*Default: Pasif + aktif birlikte çalışır*\n\n**Explicit hybrid:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -passive\namass enum -d target.com -active -dir output\n```\n\n**Full enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -brute -w wordlist.txt -active -src -o results.txt\n```\n\n### Alt Domain Brute-Force (Wordlist + Depth Yönetimi)\n\n**Deep brute-force:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -min-for-recursive 1\n```\n\n**Custom wordlist + depth:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w custom-wordlist.txt -min-for-recursive 3 -max-depth 5\n```\n\n**Wordlist + resolver tuning:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -rf resolvers.txt -max-dns-queries 20000\n```\n\n### Reverse DNS Mapping\n\n**Reverse DNS sweep:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\n```\n\n**ASN + reverse mapping:**\n```\namass intel -asn 15169\namass enum -d target.com -asn 15169\n```\n\n### ASN-Based Discovery\n\n**ASN intel:**\n```\namass intel -asn 15169 -whois\n```\n\n**ASN enumeration:**\n```\namass intel -org "Google LLC"\n```\n\n**ASN to enum:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois | grep ASN\namass enum -asn 15169\n```\n\n### DNS Resolvers Yönetimi\n\n**Custom resolvers:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**Trusted resolvers:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf trusted-resolvers.txt -dns-qps 200\n```\n\n**Public resolvers + tuning:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf public-resolvers.txt -timeout 5 -max-dns-queries 50000\n```\n\n### Alteration Attacks (Mutation)\n\n**Default alterations:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts\n```\n\n**No alterations:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -noalts\n```\n\n**Alterations + brute:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -brute -w wordlist.txt -alts\n```\n\n### Recursive Discovery\n\n**Recursive threshold:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 2\n```\n*2+ subdomains bulunursa recursive başlat*\n\n**Aggressive recursive:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 1 -max-depth 10\n```\n\n### Permutation Attack Modu\n\n**Alteration mode:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts\n```\n\n**Wordlist + alterations:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -brute -w wordlist.txt -alts -min-for-recursive 2\n```\n\n### Amass Config Dosyası Kullanımı\n\n**Config file:**\n```\namass enum -config /path/to/config.ini -d target.com\n```\n\n**Config.ini örneği:**\n```\n[scope]\nport = 80,443,8080,8443\n\n[resolvers]\nresolver = 8.8.8.8\nresolver = 1.1.1.1\n\n[bruteforce]\nenabled = true\nrecursive = true\nminimum_for_recursive = 2\n\n[data_sources.VirusTotal]\n[data_sources.VirusTotal.Credentials]\napikey = YOUR_VT_API_KEY\n\n[data_sources.Shodan]\n[data_sources.Shodan.Credentials]\napikey = YOUR_SHODAN_KEY\n```\n\n**Config usage:**\n```\namass enum -config config.ini -d target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n### API Key Kullanımı\n\n**VirusTotal:**\n```\nexport VIRUSTOTAL_API_KEY="your_key"\namass enum -d target.com -passive\n```\n\n**Shodan:**\n```\nexport SHODAN_API_KEY="your_key"\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n\n**Multiple APIs (config.ini):**\n```\n[data_sources.Shodan.Credentials]\napikey = SHODAN_KEY\n\n[data_sources.Censys.Credentials]\napikey = CENSYS_API_ID\nsecret = CENSYS_SECRET\n\n[data_sources.SecurityTrails.Credentials]\napikey = SECURITYTRAILS_KEY\n\n[data_sources.VirusTotal.Credentials]\napikey = VIRUSTOTAL_KEY\n```\n\n### OWASP Amass Visualization (viz)\n\n**Generate graph:**\n```\namass viz -d3 -dir output_directory\n```\n\n**Graphviz DOT:**\n```\namass viz -dot -dir output_directory\n```\n\n**GEXF format:**\n```\namass viz -gexf -dir output_directory\n```\n\n**Maltego transform:**\n```\namass viz -maltego -dir output_directory\n```\n\n### Graph Database Çıkışları (Neo4j)\n\n**Database export:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\namass db -dir output -show\n```\n\n**Neo4j import:**\n```\namass viz -dir output -d3 -o neo4j-graph.html\n```\n\n**Query database:**\n```\namass db -dir output -list\namass db -dir output -show -d target.com\n```\n\n### Network Mapping (Traceroute, Infrastructure Mapping)\n\n**Active network mapping:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -p 80,443,8080,8443\n```\n\n**Traceroute info:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -src\n```\n\n**Infrastructure discovery:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\namass track -d target.com\n```\n\n### Amass Intel → Organization Information Gathering\n\n**Organization intel:**\n```\namass intel -org "Target Corporation"\n```\n\n**ASN discovery:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -asn\n```\n\n**WHOIS enumeration:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\n```\n\n**Reverse WHOIS:**\n```\namass intel -whois -d target.com\n```\n\n### Rate-Limit ve DNS Resolver Tuning\n\n**Query rate limit:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 100\n```\n\n**Scraping rate:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rate 50\n```\n\n**Max DNS queries:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -max-dns-queries 10000\n```\n\n**Timeout tuning:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -timeout 10\n```\n\n### Brute-Force Optimizasyonu\n\n**Optimized brute:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -rf resolvers.txt -dns-qps 200 -max-dns-queries 50000\n```\n\n**Fast brute:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w top-10k.txt -dns-qps 500 -timeout 3\n```\n\n### Timers, Scraping, Source Prioritization\n\n**Timing control:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -timeout 10 -dns-qps 100 -rate 50\n```\n\n**Source priority (config):**\n```\n[scope]\ndomains = target.com\n\n[data_sources]\n[data_sources.VirusTotal]\nenabled = true\npriority = 1\n\n[data_sources.Shodan]\nenabled = true\npriority = 2\n```\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`enum`**\n*Subdomain enumeration modu.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n\n**`intel`**\n*Kurumsal bilgi toplama modu.*\n```\namass intel -org "Google LLC"\n```\n\n**`viz`**\n*Grafiksel çıktı oluştur.*\n```\namass viz -d3 -dir output\n```\n\n**`-d <domain>`**\n*Target domain.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n\n**`-src`**\n*Keşif kaynağını göster.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -src\n```\n\n**`-passive`**\n*Tamamen pasif enumeration.*\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com\n```\n\n**`-active`**\n*Aktif discovery (DNS resolution, port scan).*\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com\n```\n\n**`-brute`**\n*Brute-force subdomain keşfi.*\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-min-for-recursive <n>`**\n*Recursive threshold.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 3\n```\n\n**`-w <file>`**\n*Wordlist dosyası.*\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-rf <file>`**\n*Resolvers listesi.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**`-p <ports>`**\n*Port listesi.*\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -p 80,443,8080\n```\n\n**`-timeout <sec>`**\n*DNS timeout (saniye).*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -timeout 5\n```\n\n**`-ipv4`**\n*Sadece IPv4.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -ipv4\n```\n\n**`-ipv6`**\n*IPv6 dahil et.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -ipv6\n```\n\n**`-noalts`**\n*Alteration/mutation bypass.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -noalts\n```\n\n**`-alts`**\n*Alteration mode aktif.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts\n```\n\n### İleri Seviye Argümanlar\n\n**`-config <file>`**\n*Özel Amass config kullanımı.*\n```\namass enum -config config.ini -d target.com\n```\n\n**`-include <sources>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen kaynaklar.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -include crtsh,virustotal\n```\n\n**`-exclude <sources>`**\n*Belirtilen kaynakları hariç tut.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -exclude censys\n```\n\n**`-df <file>`**\n*Domain list dosyası.*\n```\namass enum -df domains.txt\n```\n\n**`-dir <directory>`**\n*Output klasörü (database).*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\n```\n\n**`-o <file>`**\n*Çıktı dosyası.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n**`-oA <prefix>`**\n*Tüm formatlarda çıktı.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -oA scan_results\n```\n\n**`-json <file>`**\n*JSON çıktı.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -json results.json\n```\n\n**`-log <file>`**\n*Verbose log.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -log amass.log\n```\n\n**`-dns-qps <n>`**\n*Query-per-second limiti.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 200\n```\n\n**`-rate <n>`**\n*Scraping hız limiti.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rate 50\n```\n\n**`-max-dns-queries <n>`**\n*Brute-force DNS query limiti.*\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -max-dns-queries 50000\n```\n\n**`-asn <number>`**\n*ASN tabanlı keşif.*\n```\namass intel -asn 15169\namass enum -asn 15169\n```\n\n**`-whois`**\n*WHOIS tabanlı domain mapping.*\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\n```\n\n**`-org <name>`**\n*Organization intel.*\n```\namass intel -org "Google LLC"\n```\n\n**`-max-depth <n>`**\n*Maximum recursive depth.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -max-depth 5\n```\n\n### Output / Database / Graph\n\n**`-oA <prefix>`**\n*text, json, graph çıktıları.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -oA results\n# Oluşturur: results.txt, results.json\n```\n\n**`-json <file>`**\n*Tam JSON veri.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -json output.json\n```\n\n**`viz -d3`**\n*D3.js HTML grafik.*\n```\namass viz -d3 -dir output\n```\n\n**`viz -dot`**\n*Graphviz DOT format.*\n```\namass viz -dot -dir output\n```\n\n**`viz -gexf`**\n*GEXF graph format.*\n```\namass viz -gexf -dir output\n```\n\n**`viz -maltego`**\n*Maltego transform.*\n```\namass viz -maltego -dir output\n```\n\n**`db -show`**\n*Database içeriğini göster.*\n```\namass db -dir output -show\n```\n\n**`db -list`**\n*Database listesi.*\n```\namass db -dir output -list\n```\n\n### Intel Mode Argümanları\n\n**`intel -d <domain>`**\n*Domain intel.*\n```\namass intel -d target.com\n```\n\n**`intel -asn <n>`**\n*ASN intel.*\n```\namass intel -asn 15169\n```\n\n**`intel -org <name>`**\n*Organization intel.*\n```\namass intel -org "Target Corp"\n```\n\n**`intel -whois`**\n*WHOIS enumeration.*\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\n```\n\n### Track Mode\n\n**`track -d <domain>`**\n*Değişim takibi.*\n```\namass track -d target.com -dir baseline\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Pasif subdomain enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -o passive-results.txt\n```\n*-passive: Sadece pasif kaynaklar (DNS kayıtları, sertifikalar, arama motorları), -d: Target domain, -o: Output dosyası*\n\n**Aktif + pasif hybrid:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -src -o hybrid-results.txt\n```\n*enum: Enumeration modu, -active: Aktif DNS resolution + port scan, -src: Kaynak göster*\n\n**Brute-force wordlist:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -min-for-recursive 3\n```\n*-brute: Brute-force modu, -w: Wordlist, -min-for-recursive 3: 3+ subdomain bulursa recursive başlat*\n\n**Recursive enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 2 -max-depth 5 -o recursive.txt\n```\n*-min-for-recursive 2: Threshold, -max-depth 5: 5 seviye depth*\n\n**Custom resolvers + rate tuning:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf resolvers.txt -dns-qps 200 -timeout 5\n```\n*-rf: Resolver listesi, -dns-qps 200: Saniyede 200 DNS query, -timeout 5: 5 saniye timeout*\n\n**ASN-based discovery:**\n```\namass intel -asn 15169 -whois\namass enum -asn 15169 -active\n```\n*intel -asn: ASN bilgi toplama, -whois: WHOIS enumeration, enum -asn: ASN'e ait tüm domainler*\n\n**Organization intel:**\n```\namass intel -org "Google LLC" -whois\n```\n*intel -org: Kurumsal bilgi toplama, -whois: WHOIS kayıtları*\n\n**Multiple domains:**\n```\namass enum -df domains.txt -active -o multi-domain-results.txt\n```\n*-df: Domain list dosyası*\n\n**JSON output:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -json results.json\n```\n*-json: JSON formatında çıktı*\n\n**Full enumeration + all outputs:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -brute -w wordlist.txt -active -src -oA full_scan\n```\n*-oA: Tüm formatlarda çıktı (txt, json)*\n\n**Config-based scan:**\n```\namass enum -config amass-config.ini -d target.com -o config-based.txt\n```\n*-config: Config dosyası kullan*\n\n**Visualization (D3):**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\namass viz -d3 -dir output -o graph.html\n```\n*viz -d3: D3.js interaktif grafik oluştur*\n\n**Graphviz DOT:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\namass viz -dot -dir output | dot -Tpng -o graph.png\n```\n*viz -dot: Graphviz DOT formatı*\n\n**Database query:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir amass_db\namass db -dir amass_db -show -d target.com\n```\n*db -show: Database içeriğini göster*\n\n**Alteration/mutation attack:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts -brute -w wordlist.txt\n```\n*-alts: Subdomain mutasyonları (dev-api, api-dev, dev.api, etc.)*\n\n**High-speed brute-force:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -rf resolvers.txt -dns-qps 500 -max-dns-queries 100000\n```\n*-dns-qps 500: Yüksek hız, -max-dns-queries 100000: 100k query limiti*\n\n**Stealth passive:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -include crtsh,threatcrowd -timeout 10 -o stealth.txt\n```\n*-passive: Aktif trafik yok, -include: Sadece belirtilen kaynaklar*\n\n**Port enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -p 80,443,8080,8443,3000,8000\n```\n*-p: Port listesi (aktif modda taranır)*\n\n**IPv4 only:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -ipv4 -active\n```\n*-ipv4: Sadece IPv4 sonuçları*\n\n**Track changes:**\n```\namass track -d target.com -dir baseline\n# Zaman sonra:\namass track -d target.com -dir baseline\n```\n*track: Baseline ile karşılaştırma, yeni/silinen subdomainleri gösterir*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Kurumsal Dış Saldırı Yüzeyi Haritalaması\n\n**Full asset discovery:**\n```\n# Stage 1: Intel\namass intel -org "Target Corporation" -whois > corp-intel.txt\n\n# Stage 2: Domain extraction\ncat corp-intel.txt | grep -Eo '[a-zA-Z0-9.-]+\\.[a-zA-Z]{2,}' | sort -u > domains.txt\n\n# Stage 3: Comprehensive enum\namass enum -df domains.txt -config amass-config.ini -active -brute -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -dir corp_enum -oA corporate_scan\n```\n\n**Visualization:**\n```\namass viz -d3 -dir corp_enum -o attack_surface.html\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: Subdomain Enumeration (Pasif + Aktif Hibrit)\n\n**Staged approach:**\n```\n# Stage 1: Pasif (stealth)\namass enum -passive -d target.com -config api-keys.ini -o passive.txt\n\n# Stage 2: Aktif (discovered domains)\namass enum -active -df passive.txt -p 80,443,8080 -o active.txt\n\n# Stage 3: Brute-force\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/subdomains.txt -min-for-recursive 3 -o brute.txt\n\n# Combine results\ncat passive.txt active.txt brute.txt | sort -u > all-subdomains.txt\n```\n\n### Senaryo 3: Shadow IT Tespiti\n\n**Organization-wide discovery:**\n```\namass intel -org "Company Name" -whois | tee org-intel.txt\n\n# Extract all domains\ngrep -Eo '([a-zA-Z0-9.-]+\\.[a-zA-Z]{2,})' org-intel.txt | sort -u > all-domains.txt\n\n# Enum all\namass enum -df all-domains.txt -active -config config.ini -oA shadow-it-scan\n\n# Cloud detection\ncat shadow-it-scan.txt | grep -E '(amazonaws\\.com|azurewebsites\\.net|cloudfunctions\\.net|storage\\.googleapis\\.com)'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: Public Asset Discovery\n\n**Multi-source passive:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -include crtsh,virustotal,threatcrowd,hackertarget,censys,shodan -src -o public-assets.txt\n```\n\n**API-powered discovery:**\n```\n# config.ini with all API keys\namass enum -config all-apis.ini -passive -d target.com -json public-assets.json\n```\n\n**Parse JSON:**\n```\ncat public-assets.json | jq -r '.name' | sort -u\n```\n\n### Senaryo 5: DNS Takeover Analizi (CNAME Zincirleri)\n\n**Enum + resolution:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -dir dns_takeover\n```\n\n**CNAME extraction:**\n```\namass db -dir dns_takeover -show -d target.com | grep CNAME\n```\n\n**Check dangling CNAMEs:**\n```\n# Extract CNAMEs\namass db -dir dns_takeover -show -d target.com | grep CNAME | awk '{print $3}' | sort -u > cnames.txt\n\n# Check resolution\nwhile read cname; do\n  dig +short $cname || echo "[POTENTIAL TAKEOVER] $cname"\ndone < cnames.txt\n```\n\n### Senaryo 6: Cloud Provider Enum (AWS, GCP, Azure)\n\n**Cloud subdomain discovery:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -brute -w cloud-wordlist.txt -o cloud-assets.txt\n\n# Filter cloud providers\ngrep -E '(amazonaws\\.com|s3\\.amazonaws\\.com|cloudfront\\.net|azurewebsites\\.net|blob\\.core\\.windows\\.net|storage\\.googleapis\\.com|cloudfunctions\\.net|appspot\\.com)' cloud-assets.txt\n```\n\n**S3 bucket discovery:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w s3-wordlist.txt | grep 's3\\.amazonaws\\.com'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 7: ASN Tabanlı Dış Yüzey Keşfi\n\n**ASN discovery:**\n```\n# Get ASN\namass intel -d target.com -whois | grep -i ASN\n\n# Enum ASN\namass intel -asn 15169 -whois > asn-intel.txt\n\n# Extract domains\ngrep -Eo '([a-zA-Z0-9.-]+\\.[a-zA-Z]{2,})' asn-intel.txt | sort -u > asn-domains.txt\n\n# Full enum\namass enum -df asn-domains.txt -active -dir asn_enum -oA asn-scan\n```\n\n### Senaryo 8: Permutation ve Mutation Tabanlı Saldırılar\n\n**Alteration attack:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts -min-for-recursive 2 -active -o mutations.txt\n```\n\n**Custom permutations:**\n```\n# Wordlist with common patterns\n# dev, stage, staging, prod, production, qa, test, uat, demo, beta, alpha\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w permutation-wordlist.txt -alts -o permutations.txt\n```\n\n**Example mutations:**\n```\napi.target.com\ndev-api.target.com\napi-dev.target.com\napi.dev.target.com\ndevapi.target.com\n```\n\n### Senaryo 9: Wordlist Brute-Force + Recursive Kombine\n\n**Multi-stage brute:**\n```\n# Stage 1: Top subdomains\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w top-10k.txt -min-for-recursive 1 -o stage1.txt\n\n# Stage 2: All wordlist\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -min-for-recursive 3 -max-depth 5 -o stage2.txt\n\n# Stage 3: Custom corporate wordlist\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w corporate-wordlist.txt -alts -min-for-recursive 2 -o stage3.txt\n```\n\n**Optimized brute:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w huge-wordlist.txt -rf trusted-resolvers.txt -dns-qps 300 -max-dns-queries 200000 -timeout 3 -o optimized-brute.txt\n```\n\n### Senaryo 10: DNS Resolver Rate-Limit Tuning\n\n**Baseline test:**\n```\n# Low rate\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 50 -timeout 10 -o baseline.txt\n```\n\n**Tuning:**\n```\n# Medium\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 100 -timeout 5 -rf resolvers.txt\n\n# High (trusted resolvers)\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 300 -timeout 3 -rf trusted.txt\n\n# Maximum (aggressive)\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -dns-qps 500 -max-dns-queries 100000\n```\n\n### Senaryo 11: Pasif Kaynaklarla Geniş Kapsamlı Footprint\n\n**All passive sources:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -config all-api-keys.ini -include crtsh,virustotal,censys,shodan,securitytrails,threatcrowd,hackertarget,riddler,netcraft -src -timeout 15 -o comprehensive-passive.txt\n```\n\n**Source analysis:**\n```\ncat comprehensive-passive.txt | cut -d'[' -f2 | cut -d']' -f1 | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n### Senaryo 12: JSON Output → Güvenlik Raporu Entegrasyonu\n\n**JSON generation:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -config config.ini -json scan-data.json\n```\n\n**Parse for report:**\n```\n# Extract subdomains\ncat scan-data.json | jq -r '.name' | sort -u > subdomains.txt\n\n# Extract IPs\ncat scan-data.json | jq -r '.addresses[]?.ip' | sort -u > ips.txt\n\n# Extract sources\ncat scan-data.json | jq -r '.sources[]?' | sort -u > sources.txt\n\n# Count by source\ncat scan-data.json | jq -r '.sources[]?' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n**Integration:**\n```\n# SIEM import (Splunk)\ncat scan-data.json | jq -c '.' | curl -X POST https://splunk:8088/services/collector/event -H "Authorization: Splunk TOKEN" -d @-\n\n# TheHive case creation\ncurl -X POST https://thehive/api/case -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" -d @scan-data.json\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Pasif Kaynakların Doğru Kullanımı:**\n\n**Multiple sources:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -include crtsh,virustotal,censys,shodan,threatcrowd -src\n```\n\n**Source reliability:**\n```\n# High reliability: crtsh, censys\n# Medium: virustotal, shodan\n# Low: scraping sources\n```\n\n**Validation:**\n```\n# Pasif sonuçları aktif doğrula\namass enum -passive -d target.com -o passive.txt\namass enum -active -df passive.txt -o validated.txt\n```\n\n**2. Çoklu API Key Optimizasyonu:**\n\n**Config.ini:**\n```\n[data_sources.VirusTotal.Credentials]\napikey = VT_KEY_1\n\n[data_sources.Shodan.Credentials]\napikey = SHODAN_KEY_1\n\n[data_sources.Censys.Credentials]\napikey = CENSYS_ID_1\nsecret = CENSYS_SECRET_1\n\n[data_sources.SecurityTrails.Credentials]\napikey = ST_KEY_1\n\n[data_sources.Passivetotal.Credentials]\nusername = PT_USER\napikey = PT_KEY\n```\n\n**Rate limits:**\n- VirusTotal: 4 requests/min (free)\n- Shodan: Unlimited (paid)\n- Censys: 120 requests/5min\n- SecurityTrails: 50 requests/month (free)\n\n**3. Aktif Discovery için Güvenli Hız Sınırları:**\n\n**Conservative:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 50 -rate 10 -timeout 10\n```\n\n**Moderate:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 100 -rate 25 -timeout 5\n```\n\n**Aggressive (trusted environment):**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 300 -timeout 3\n```\n\n**4. Brute-Force için Wordlist Seçimi:**\n\n**Size vs Quality:**\n```\n# Small (fast): top-1k.txt\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w top-1k.txt\n\n# Medium: top-10k.txt\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w top-10k.txt -min-for-recursive 3\n\n# Large: all.txt (100k+)\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -dns-qps 200\n```\n\n**Custom corporate:**\n```\n# department names, product names, tech stack\ndev, stage, prod, api, admin, portal, app, web, mail, vpn, etc.\n```\n\n**5. Config Dosyası ile Advanced Tuning:**\n\n**Production config.ini:**\n```\n[scope]\nport = 80,443,8080,8443\nasn = 15169,13335\n\n[scope.domains]\ndomain = target.com\n\n[scope.blacklist]\nsubdomain = test.target.com\n\n[resolvers]\nresolver = 1.1.1.1\nresolver = 8.8.8.8\nresolver = 9.9.9.9\n\n[bruteforce]\nenabled = true\nrecursive = true\nminimum_for_recursive = 2\nwordlist_file = /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt\n\n[alterations]\nenabled = true\nminimum_for_word_flip = 2\nedit_distance = 1\n\n[data_sources]\nminimum_ttl = 1440\n\n[data_sources.VirusTotal.Credentials]\napikey = YOUR_VT_KEY\n\n[data_sources.Shodan.Credentials]\napikey = YOUR_SHODAN_KEY\n```\n\n**6. Amass Verilerini SIEM / CTI Platformlarına Aktarma:**\n\n**JSON to Splunk:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -json output.json\ncat output.json | jq -c '{time: .timestamp, source: .sources[], domain: .name, ip: .addresses[]?.ip}' | curl -X POST https://splunk:8088/services/collector -H "Authorization: Splunk TOKEN" -d @-\n```\n\n**CSV export:**\n```\namass db -dir output -show -d target.com | awk '{print $1","$2","$3}' > export.csv\n```\n\n**7. DNS Resolver Doğruluğu:**\n\n**Trusted resolvers:**\n```\n1.1.1.1         # Cloudflare\n8.8.8.8         # Google\n9.9.9.9         # Quad9\n208.67.222.222  # OpenDNS\n```\n\n**Validation:**\n```\n# Test resolvers\nwhile read resolver; do\n  dig @$resolver target.com +short || echo "Failed: $resolver"\ndone < resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**8. Recursive Depth Yönetimi:**\n\n**Shallow (fast):**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 5 -max-depth 2\n```\n\n**Medium:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 3 -max-depth 5\n```\n\n**Deep (comprehensive):**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 1 -max-depth 10\n```\n\n**9. Grafik Çıktıların Analiz Edilmesi (viz):**\n\n**D3 interactive:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\namass viz -d3 -dir output -o graph.html\n# Browser'da aç: firefox graph.html\n```\n\n**Graphviz analysis:**\n```\namass viz -dot -dir output | dot -Tpng -o graph.png\namass viz -dot -dir output | dot -Tsvg -o graph.svg\n```\n\n**Network analysis:**\n```\namass viz -gexf -dir output\n# Import to Gephi for network analysis\n```\n\n**10. Rate-Limit Uyumlu Optimizasyon:**\n\n**Detection:**\n```\n# Monitor for rate limiting\namass enum -d target.com -log amass.log -dns-qps 200\ngrep -i "rate" amass.log\n```\n\n**Adaptive:**\n```\n# Start low\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 50\n\n# Increase if no errors\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 100\n\n# Max stable\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 200 -rf trusted.txt\n```\n\n**11. Attack Surface Management Pipeline:**\n\n**Continuous monitoring:**\n```\n#!/bin/bash\nDOMAIN="target.com"\nBASELINE_DIR="/var/amass/baseline"\nCURRENT_DIR="/var/amass/current_$(date +%Y%m%d)"\n\n# Initial baseline (first run only)\nif [ ! -d "$BASELINE_DIR" ]; then\n  amass enum -d $DOMAIN -config config.ini -dir $BASELINE_DIR -oA baseline\nfi\n\n# Current scan\namass enum -d $DOMAIN -config config.ini -dir $CURRENT_DIR -oA current\n\n# Track changes\namass track -d $DOMAIN -dir $BASELINE_DIR > changes.txt\n\n# Alert on new subdomains\nNEW=$(grep "^+" changes.txt | wc -l)\nif [ $NEW -gt 0 ]; then\n  echo "New subdomains detected: $NEW"\n  grep "^+" changes.txt | mail -s "New Assets Detected" security@target.com\nfi\n\n# Update baseline\ncp -r $CURRENT_DIR/* $BASELINE_DIR/\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. Sadece pasif keşif yapıp eksik sonuç almak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (pasif only)\namass enum -passive -d target.com\n\n# DOĞRU (hybrid)\namass enum -d target.com -active -config api-keys.ini\n```\n\n**2. Varsayılan resolvers kullanmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (system resolvers)\namass enum -d target.com\n\n# DOĞRU (custom resolvers)\namass enum -d target.com -rf trusted-resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**3. Recursive threshold yanlış ayarlanması:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (çok yüksek, recursive çalışmaz)\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 10\n\n# DOĞRU (dengeli)\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 2\n```\n\n**4. Yetersiz wordlist seçimi:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (çok küçük)\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w small-list.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (comprehensive)\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt\n```\n\n**5. API keysiz pasif keşfe güvenmek:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (limited results)\namass enum -passive -d target.com\n\n# DOĞRU (API-powered)\namass enum -passive -d target.com -config api-keys.ini\n```\n\n**6. Rate-limit aşımı:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (aggressive, rate-limited)\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 1000\n\n# DOĞRU (optimized)\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 200 -rf resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**7. Alan adı zinciri (CNAME) yanlış yorumlama:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (sadece subdomain listesi)\namass enum -d target.com -o results.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (resolution + CNAME mapping)\namass enum -d target.com -active -dir output\namass db -dir output -show | grep CNAME\n```\n\n**8. JSON çıktısı oluşturmamak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (sadece text)\namass enum -d target.com -o results.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (JSON for parsing)\namass enum -d target.com -json results.json -o results.txt\n```\n\n**9. Aktif modda firewall tetikleme:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (aggressive active)\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 500\n\n# DOĞRU (stealth)\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 50 -timeout 10 -rate 10\n```\n\n**10. Output directory kullanmamak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (data loss, no database)\namass enum -d target.com -o results.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (persistent database)\namass enum -d target.com -dir project_enum -oA results\n```\n\n## Data Sources Referansı\n\n**Pasif kaynaklar:**\n```\ncrtsh              # Certificate Transparency logs\nvirustotal         # VirusTotal passive DNS\ncensys             # Censys search engine\nshodan             # Shodan search engine\nsecuritytrails     # SecurityTrails DNS history\nthreatcrowd        # ThreatCrowd\nhackertarget       # HackerTarget\nriddler            # Riddler.io\nnetcraft           # Netcraft\ndnsdumpster        # DNSDumpster\nwayback            # Wayback Machine\n```\n\n**Aktif kaynaklar:**\n```\nDNS resolution\nReverse DNS\nPort scanning\nCertificate analysis\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**List data sources:**\n```\namass enum -list\n```\n\n**Check config:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -config config.ini -list\n```\n\n**Database operations:**\n```\namass db -dir output -list\namass db -dir output -show -d target.com\namass db -dir output -names\namass db -dir output -summary\n```\n\n**Export formats:**\n```\namass db -dir output -show -d target.com -o export.txt\namass viz -d3 -dir output -o graph.html\namass viz -dot -dir output | dot -Tpng > graph.png\n```\n\n**Version:**\n```\namass -version\n```\n\n**Help:**\n```\namass enum -h\namass intel -h\namass viz -h\namass db -h\n```\n	# OWASP Amass - Advanced Network Mapping\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n### Pasif Keşif\n\n**Pasif subdomain enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com\n```\n\n**Pasif + kaynak göster:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -src\n```\n\n**Sadece belirli kaynaklar:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -include crtsh,virustotal\n```\n\n### Aktif Keşif\n\n**Aktif enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com\n```\n\n**Aktif + DNS resolution:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -p 80,443,8080\n```\n\n### Domain Enumeration\n\n**Basit enum:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n\n**Multiple domains:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com,example.com\n```\n\n**Domain list dosyası:**\n```\namass enum -df domains.txt\n```\n\n### Brute-Force Subdomain Keşfi\n\n**Brute-force wordlist:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/subdomains.txt\n```\n\n**Brute-force + min threshold:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -min-for-recursive 3\n```\n\n### Recursive Enumeration\n\n**Recursive discovery:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 2\n```\n\n**Recursive + brute-force:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -min-for-recursive 3\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Pasif + Aktif Birleşik Enumeration\n\n**Hybrid mode:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n*Default: Pasif + aktif birlikte çalışır*\n\n**Explicit hybrid:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -passive\namass enum -d target.com -active -dir output\n```\n\n**Full enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -brute -w wordlist.txt -active -src -o results.txt\n```\n\n### Alt Domain Brute-Force (Wordlist + Depth Yönetimi)\n\n**Deep brute-force:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -min-for-recursive 1\n```\n\n**Custom wordlist + depth:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w custom-wordlist.txt -min-for-recursive 3 -max-depth 5\n```\n\n**Wordlist + resolver tuning:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -rf resolvers.txt -max-dns-queries 20000\n```\n\n### Reverse DNS Mapping\n\n**Reverse DNS sweep:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\n```\n\n**ASN + reverse mapping:**\n```\namass intel -asn 15169\namass enum -d target.com -asn 15169\n```\n\n### ASN-Based Discovery\n\n**ASN intel:**\n```\namass intel -asn 15169 -whois\n```\n\n**ASN enumeration:**\n```\namass intel -org "Google LLC"\n```\n\n**ASN to enum:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois | grep ASN\namass enum -asn 15169\n```\n\n### DNS Resolvers Yönetimi\n\n**Custom resolvers:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**Trusted resolvers:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf trusted-resolvers.txt -dns-qps 200\n```\n\n**Public resolvers + tuning:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf public-resolvers.txt -timeout 5 -max-dns-queries 50000\n```\n\n### Alteration Attacks (Mutation)\n\n**Default alterations:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts\n```\n\n**No alterations:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -noalts\n```\n\n**Alterations + brute:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -brute -w wordlist.txt -alts\n```\n\n### Recursive Discovery\n\n**Recursive threshold:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 2\n```\n*2+ subdomains bulunursa recursive başlat*\n\n**Aggressive recursive:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 1 -max-depth 10\n```\n\n### Permutation Attack Modu\n\n**Alteration mode:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts\n```\n\n**Wordlist + alterations:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -brute -w wordlist.txt -alts -min-for-recursive 2\n```\n\n### Amass Config Dosyası Kullanımı\n\n**Config file:**\n```\namass enum -config /path/to/config.ini -d target.com\n```\n\n**Config.ini örneği:**\n```\n[scope]\nport = 80,443,8080,8443\n\n[resolvers]\nresolver = 8.8.8.8\nresolver = 1.1.1.1\n\n[bruteforce]\nenabled = true\nrecursive = true\nminimum_for_recursive = 2\n\n[data_sources.VirusTotal]\n[data_sources.VirusTotal.Credentials]\napikey = YOUR_VT_API_KEY\n\n[data_sources.Shodan]\n[data_sources.Shodan.Credentials]\napikey = YOUR_SHODAN_KEY\n```\n\n**Config usage:**\n```\namass enum -config config.ini -d target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n### API Key Kullanımı\n\n**VirusTotal:**\n```\nexport VIRUSTOTAL_API_KEY="your_key"\namass enum -d target.com -passive\n```\n\n**Shodan:**\n```\nexport SHODAN_API_KEY="your_key"\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n\n**Multiple APIs (config.ini):**\n```\n[data_sources.Shodan.Credentials]\napikey = SHODAN_KEY\n\n[data_sources.Censys.Credentials]\napikey = CENSYS_API_ID\nsecret = CENSYS_SECRET\n\n[data_sources.SecurityTrails.Credentials]\napikey = SECURITYTRAILS_KEY\n\n[data_sources.VirusTotal.Credentials]\napikey = VIRUSTOTAL_KEY\n```\n\n### OWASP Amass Visualization (viz)\n\n**Generate graph:**\n```\namass viz -d3 -dir output_directory\n```\n\n**Graphviz DOT:**\n```\namass viz -dot -dir output_directory\n```\n\n**GEXF format:**\n```\namass viz -gexf -dir output_directory\n```\n\n**Maltego transform:**\n```\namass viz -maltego -dir output_directory\n```\n\n### Graph Database Çıkışları (Neo4j)\n\n**Database export:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\namass db -dir output -show\n```\n\n**Neo4j import:**\n```\namass viz -dir output -d3 -o neo4j-graph.html\n```\n\n**Query database:**\n```\namass db -dir output -list\namass db -dir output -show -d target.com\n```\n\n### Network Mapping (Traceroute, Infrastructure Mapping)\n\n**Active network mapping:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -p 80,443,8080,8443\n```\n\n**Traceroute info:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -src\n```\n\n**Infrastructure discovery:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\namass track -d target.com\n```\n\n### Amass Intel → Organization Information Gathering\n\n**Organization intel:**\n```\namass intel -org "Target Corporation"\n```\n\n**ASN discovery:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -asn\n```\n\n**WHOIS enumeration:**\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\n```\n\n**Reverse WHOIS:**\n```\namass intel -whois -d target.com\n```\n\n### Rate-Limit ve DNS Resolver Tuning\n\n**Query rate limit:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 100\n```\n\n**Scraping rate:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rate 50\n```\n\n**Max DNS queries:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -max-dns-queries 10000\n```\n\n**Timeout tuning:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -timeout 10\n```\n\n### Brute-Force Optimizasyonu\n\n**Optimized brute:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -rf resolvers.txt -dns-qps 200 -max-dns-queries 50000\n```\n\n**Fast brute:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w top-10k.txt -dns-qps 500 -timeout 3\n```\n\n### Timers, Scraping, Source Prioritization\n\n**Timing control:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -timeout 10 -dns-qps 100 -rate 50\n```\n\n**Source priority (config):**\n```\n[scope]\ndomains = target.com\n\n[data_sources]\n[data_sources.VirusTotal]\nenabled = true\npriority = 1\n\n[data_sources.Shodan]\nenabled = true\npriority = 2\n```\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`enum`**\n*Subdomain enumeration modu.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n\n**`intel`**\n*Kurumsal bilgi toplama modu.*\n```\namass intel -org "Google LLC"\n```\n\n**`viz`**\n*Grafiksel çıktı oluştur.*\n```\namass viz -d3 -dir output\n```\n\n**`-d <domain>`**\n*Target domain.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com\n```\n\n**`-src`**\n*Keşif kaynağını göster.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -src\n```\n\n**`-passive`**\n*Tamamen pasif enumeration.*\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com\n```\n\n**`-active`**\n*Aktif discovery (DNS resolution, port scan).*\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com\n```\n\n**`-brute`**\n*Brute-force subdomain keşfi.*\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-min-for-recursive <n>`**\n*Recursive threshold.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 3\n```\n\n**`-w <file>`**\n*Wordlist dosyası.*\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-rf <file>`**\n*Resolvers listesi.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**`-p <ports>`**\n*Port listesi.*\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -p 80,443,8080\n```\n\n**`-timeout <sec>`**\n*DNS timeout (saniye).*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -timeout 5\n```\n\n**`-ipv4`**\n*Sadece IPv4.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -ipv4\n```\n\n**`-ipv6`**\n*IPv6 dahil et.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -ipv6\n```\n\n**`-noalts`**\n*Alteration/mutation bypass.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -noalts\n```\n\n**`-alts`**\n*Alteration mode aktif.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts\n```\n\n### İleri Seviye Argümanlar\n\n**`-config <file>`**\n*Özel Amass config kullanımı.*\n```\namass enum -config config.ini -d target.com\n```\n\n**`-include <sources>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen kaynaklar.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -include crtsh,virustotal\n```\n\n**`-exclude <sources>`**\n*Belirtilen kaynakları hariç tut.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -exclude censys\n```\n\n**`-df <file>`**\n*Domain list dosyası.*\n```\namass enum -df domains.txt\n```\n\n**`-dir <directory>`**\n*Output klasörü (database).*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\n```\n\n**`-o <file>`**\n*Çıktı dosyası.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n**`-oA <prefix>`**\n*Tüm formatlarda çıktı.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -oA scan_results\n```\n\n**`-json <file>`**\n*JSON çıktı.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -json results.json\n```\n\n**`-log <file>`**\n*Verbose log.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -log amass.log\n```\n\n**`-dns-qps <n>`**\n*Query-per-second limiti.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 200\n```\n\n**`-rate <n>`**\n*Scraping hız limiti.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rate 50\n```\n\n**`-max-dns-queries <n>`**\n*Brute-force DNS query limiti.*\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -max-dns-queries 50000\n```\n\n**`-asn <number>`**\n*ASN tabanlı keşif.*\n```\namass intel -asn 15169\namass enum -asn 15169\n```\n\n**`-whois`**\n*WHOIS tabanlı domain mapping.*\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\n```\n\n**`-org <name>`**\n*Organization intel.*\n```\namass intel -org "Google LLC"\n```\n\n**`-max-depth <n>`**\n*Maximum recursive depth.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -max-depth 5\n```\n\n### Output / Database / Graph\n\n**`-oA <prefix>`**\n*text, json, graph çıktıları.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -oA results\n# Oluşturur: results.txt, results.json\n```\n\n**`-json <file>`**\n*Tam JSON veri.*\n```\namass enum -d target.com -json output.json\n```\n\n**`viz -d3`**\n*D3.js HTML grafik.*\n```\namass viz -d3 -dir output\n```\n\n**`viz -dot`**\n*Graphviz DOT format.*\n```\namass viz -dot -dir output\n```\n\n**`viz -gexf`**\n*GEXF graph format.*\n```\namass viz -gexf -dir output\n```\n\n**`viz -maltego`**\n*Maltego transform.*\n```\namass viz -maltego -dir output\n```\n\n**`db -show`**\n*Database içeriğini göster.*\n```\namass db -dir output -show\n```\n\n**`db -list`**\n*Database listesi.*\n```\namass db -dir output -list\n```\n\n### Intel Mode Argümanları\n\n**`intel -d <domain>`**\n*Domain intel.*\n```\namass intel -d target.com\n```\n\n**`intel -asn <n>`**\n*ASN intel.*\n```\namass intel -asn 15169\n```\n\n**`intel -org <name>`**\n*Organization intel.*\n```\namass intel -org "Target Corp"\n```\n\n**`intel -whois`**\n*WHOIS enumeration.*\n```\namass intel -d target.com -whois\n```\n\n### Track Mode\n\n**`track -d <domain>`**\n*Değişim takibi.*\n```\namass track -d target.com -dir baseline\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Pasif subdomain enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -o passive-results.txt\n```\n*-passive: Sadece pasif kaynaklar (DNS kayıtları, sertifikalar, arama motorları), -d: Target domain, -o: Output dosyası*\n\n**Aktif + pasif hybrid:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -src -o hybrid-results.txt\n```\n*enum: Enumeration modu, -active: Aktif DNS resolution + port scan, -src: Kaynak göster*\n\n**Brute-force wordlist:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -min-for-recursive 3\n```\n*-brute: Brute-force modu, -w: Wordlist, -min-for-recursive 3: 3+ subdomain bulursa recursive başlat*\n\n**Recursive enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 2 -max-depth 5 -o recursive.txt\n```\n*-min-for-recursive 2: Threshold, -max-depth 5: 5 seviye depth*\n\n**Custom resolvers + rate tuning:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -rf resolvers.txt -dns-qps 200 -timeout 5\n```\n*-rf: Resolver listesi, -dns-qps 200: Saniyede 200 DNS query, -timeout 5: 5 saniye timeout*\n\n**ASN-based discovery:**\n```\namass intel -asn 15169 -whois\namass enum -asn 15169 -active\n```\n*intel -asn: ASN bilgi toplama, -whois: WHOIS enumeration, enum -asn: ASN'e ait tüm domainler*\n\n**Organization intel:**\n```\namass intel -org "Google LLC" -whois\n```\n*intel -org: Kurumsal bilgi toplama, -whois: WHOIS kayıtları*\n\n**Multiple domains:**\n```\namass enum -df domains.txt -active -o multi-domain-results.txt\n```\n*-df: Domain list dosyası*\n\n**JSON output:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -json results.json\n```\n*-json: JSON formatında çıktı*\n\n**Full enumeration + all outputs:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -brute -w wordlist.txt -active -src -oA full_scan\n```\n*-oA: Tüm formatlarda çıktı (txt, json)*\n\n**Config-based scan:**\n```\namass enum -config amass-config.ini -d target.com -o config-based.txt\n```\n*-config: Config dosyası kullan*\n\n**Visualization (D3):**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\namass viz -d3 -dir output -o graph.html\n```\n*viz -d3: D3.js interaktif grafik oluştur*\n\n**Graphviz DOT:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\namass viz -dot -dir output | dot -Tpng -o graph.png\n```\n*viz -dot: Graphviz DOT formatı*\n\n**Database query:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir amass_db\namass db -dir amass_db -show -d target.com\n```\n*db -show: Database içeriğini göster*\n\n**Alteration/mutation attack:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts -brute -w wordlist.txt\n```\n*-alts: Subdomain mutasyonları (dev-api, api-dev, dev.api, etc.)*\n\n**High-speed brute-force:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -rf resolvers.txt -dns-qps 500 -max-dns-queries 100000\n```\n*-dns-qps 500: Yüksek hız, -max-dns-queries 100000: 100k query limiti*\n\n**Stealth passive:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -include crtsh,threatcrowd -timeout 10 -o stealth.txt\n```\n*-passive: Aktif trafik yok, -include: Sadece belirtilen kaynaklar*\n\n**Port enumeration:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -p 80,443,8080,8443,3000,8000\n```\n*-p: Port listesi (aktif modda taranır)*\n\n**IPv4 only:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -ipv4 -active\n```\n*-ipv4: Sadece IPv4 sonuçları*\n\n**Track changes:**\n```\namass track -d target.com -dir baseline\n# Zaman sonra:\namass track -d target.com -dir baseline\n```\n*track: Baseline ile karşılaştırma, yeni/silinen subdomainleri gösterir*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Kurumsal Dış Saldırı Yüzeyi Haritalaması\n\n**Full asset discovery:**\n```\n# Stage 1: Intel\namass intel -org "Target Corporation" -whois > corp-intel.txt\n\n# Stage 2: Domain extraction\ncat corp-intel.txt | grep -Eo '[a-zA-Z0-9.-]+\\.[a-zA-Z]{2,}' | sort -u > domains.txt\n\n# Stage 3: Comprehensive enum\namass enum -df domains.txt -config amass-config.ini -active -brute -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -dir corp_enum -oA corporate_scan\n```\n\n**Visualization:**\n```\namass viz -d3 -dir corp_enum -o attack_surface.html\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: Subdomain Enumeration (Pasif + Aktif Hibrit)\n\n**Staged approach:**\n```\n# Stage 1: Pasif (stealth)\namass enum -passive -d target.com -config api-keys.ini -o passive.txt\n\n# Stage 2: Aktif (discovered domains)\namass enum -active -df passive.txt -p 80,443,8080 -o active.txt\n\n# Stage 3: Brute-force\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/subdomains.txt -min-for-recursive 3 -o brute.txt\n\n# Combine results\ncat passive.txt active.txt brute.txt | sort -u > all-subdomains.txt\n```\n\n### Senaryo 3: Shadow IT Tespiti\n\n**Organization-wide discovery:**\n```\namass intel -org "Company Name" -whois | tee org-intel.txt\n\n# Extract all domains\ngrep -Eo '([a-zA-Z0-9.-]+\\.[a-zA-Z]{2,})' org-intel.txt | sort -u > all-domains.txt\n\n# Enum all\namass enum -df all-domains.txt -active -config config.ini -oA shadow-it-scan\n\n# Cloud detection\ncat shadow-it-scan.txt | grep -E '(amazonaws\\.com|azurewebsites\\.net|cloudfunctions\\.net|storage\\.googleapis\\.com)'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: Public Asset Discovery\n\n**Multi-source passive:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -include crtsh,virustotal,threatcrowd,hackertarget,censys,shodan -src -o public-assets.txt\n```\n\n**API-powered discovery:**\n```\n# config.ini with all API keys\namass enum -config all-apis.ini -passive -d target.com -json public-assets.json\n```\n\n**Parse JSON:**\n```\ncat public-assets.json | jq -r '.name' | sort -u\n```\n\n### Senaryo 5: DNS Takeover Analizi (CNAME Zincirleri)\n\n**Enum + resolution:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -dir dns_takeover\n```\n\n**CNAME extraction:**\n```\namass db -dir dns_takeover -show -d target.com | grep CNAME\n```\n\n**Check dangling CNAMEs:**\n```\n# Extract CNAMEs\namass db -dir dns_takeover -show -d target.com | grep CNAME | awk '{print $3}' | sort -u > cnames.txt\n\n# Check resolution\nwhile read cname; do\n  dig +short $cname || echo "[POTENTIAL TAKEOVER] $cname"\ndone < cnames.txt\n```\n\n### Senaryo 6: Cloud Provider Enum (AWS, GCP, Azure)\n\n**Cloud subdomain discovery:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -brute -w cloud-wordlist.txt -o cloud-assets.txt\n\n# Filter cloud providers\ngrep -E '(amazonaws\\.com|s3\\.amazonaws\\.com|cloudfront\\.net|azurewebsites\\.net|blob\\.core\\.windows\\.net|storage\\.googleapis\\.com|cloudfunctions\\.net|appspot\\.com)' cloud-assets.txt\n```\n\n**S3 bucket discovery:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w s3-wordlist.txt | grep 's3\\.amazonaws\\.com'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 7: ASN Tabanlı Dış Yüzey Keşfi\n\n**ASN discovery:**\n```\n# Get ASN\namass intel -d target.com -whois | grep -i ASN\n\n# Enum ASN\namass intel -asn 15169 -whois > asn-intel.txt\n\n# Extract domains\ngrep -Eo '([a-zA-Z0-9.-]+\\.[a-zA-Z]{2,})' asn-intel.txt | sort -u > asn-domains.txt\n\n# Full enum\namass enum -df asn-domains.txt -active -dir asn_enum -oA asn-scan\n```\n\n### Senaryo 8: Permutation ve Mutation Tabanlı Saldırılar\n\n**Alteration attack:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -alts -min-for-recursive 2 -active -o mutations.txt\n```\n\n**Custom permutations:**\n```\n# Wordlist with common patterns\n# dev, stage, staging, prod, production, qa, test, uat, demo, beta, alpha\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w permutation-wordlist.txt -alts -o permutations.txt\n```\n\n**Example mutations:**\n```\napi.target.com\ndev-api.target.com\napi-dev.target.com\napi.dev.target.com\ndevapi.target.com\n```\n\n### Senaryo 9: Wordlist Brute-Force + Recursive Kombine\n\n**Multi-stage brute:**\n```\n# Stage 1: Top subdomains\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w top-10k.txt -min-for-recursive 1 -o stage1.txt\n\n# Stage 2: All wordlist\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -min-for-recursive 3 -max-depth 5 -o stage2.txt\n\n# Stage 3: Custom corporate wordlist\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w corporate-wordlist.txt -alts -min-for-recursive 2 -o stage3.txt\n```\n\n**Optimized brute:**\n```\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w huge-wordlist.txt -rf trusted-resolvers.txt -dns-qps 300 -max-dns-queries 200000 -timeout 3 -o optimized-brute.txt\n```\n\n### Senaryo 10: DNS Resolver Rate-Limit Tuning\n\n**Baseline test:**\n```\n# Low rate\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 50 -timeout 10 -o baseline.txt\n```\n\n**Tuning:**\n```\n# Medium\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 100 -timeout 5 -rf resolvers.txt\n\n# High (trusted resolvers)\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 300 -timeout 3 -rf trusted.txt\n\n# Maximum (aggressive)\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w wordlist.txt -dns-qps 500 -max-dns-queries 100000\n```\n\n### Senaryo 11: Pasif Kaynaklarla Geniş Kapsamlı Footprint\n\n**All passive sources:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -config all-api-keys.ini -include crtsh,virustotal,censys,shodan,securitytrails,threatcrowd,hackertarget,riddler,netcraft -src -timeout 15 -o comprehensive-passive.txt\n```\n\n**Source analysis:**\n```\ncat comprehensive-passive.txt | cut -d'[' -f2 | cut -d']' -f1 | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n### Senaryo 12: JSON Output → Güvenlik Raporu Entegrasyonu\n\n**JSON generation:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -active -config config.ini -json scan-data.json\n```\n\n**Parse for report:**\n```\n# Extract subdomains\ncat scan-data.json | jq -r '.name' | sort -u > subdomains.txt\n\n# Extract IPs\ncat scan-data.json | jq -r '.addresses[]?.ip' | sort -u > ips.txt\n\n# Extract sources\ncat scan-data.json | jq -r '.sources[]?' | sort -u > sources.txt\n\n# Count by source\ncat scan-data.json | jq -r '.sources[]?' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n**Integration:**\n```\n# SIEM import (Splunk)\ncat scan-data.json | jq -c '.' | curl -X POST https://splunk:8088/services/collector/event -H "Authorization: Splunk TOKEN" -d @-\n\n# TheHive case creation\ncurl -X POST https://thehive/api/case -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" -d @scan-data.json\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Pasif Kaynakların Doğru Kullanımı:**\n\n**Multiple sources:**\n```\namass enum -passive -d target.com -include crtsh,virustotal,censys,shodan,threatcrowd -src\n```\n\n**Source reliability:**\n```\n# High reliability: crtsh, censys\n# Medium: virustotal, shodan\n# Low: scraping sources\n```\n\n**Validation:**\n```\n# Pasif sonuçları aktif doğrula\namass enum -passive -d target.com -o passive.txt\namass enum -active -df passive.txt -o validated.txt\n```\n\n**2. Çoklu API Key Optimizasyonu:**\n\n**Config.ini:**\n```\n[data_sources.VirusTotal.Credentials]\napikey = VT_KEY_1\n\n[data_sources.Shodan.Credentials]\napikey = SHODAN_KEY_1\n\n[data_sources.Censys.Credentials]\napikey = CENSYS_ID_1\nsecret = CENSYS_SECRET_1\n\n[data_sources.SecurityTrails.Credentials]\napikey = ST_KEY_1\n\n[data_sources.Passivetotal.Credentials]\nusername = PT_USER\napikey = PT_KEY\n```\n\n**Rate limits:**\n- VirusTotal: 4 requests/min (free)\n- Shodan: Unlimited (paid)\n- Censys: 120 requests/5min\n- SecurityTrails: 50 requests/month (free)\n\n**3. Aktif Discovery için Güvenli Hız Sınırları:**\n\n**Conservative:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 50 -rate 10 -timeout 10\n```\n\n**Moderate:**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 100 -rate 25 -timeout 5\n```\n\n**Aggressive (trusted environment):**\n```\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 300 -timeout 3\n```\n\n**4. Brute-Force için Wordlist Seçimi:**\n\n**Size vs Quality:**\n```\n# Small (fast): top-1k.txt\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w top-1k.txt\n\n# Medium: top-10k.txt\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w top-10k.txt -min-for-recursive 3\n\n# Large: all.txt (100k+)\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt -dns-qps 200\n```\n\n**Custom corporate:**\n```\n# department names, product names, tech stack\ndev, stage, prod, api, admin, portal, app, web, mail, vpn, etc.\n```\n\n**5. Config Dosyası ile Advanced Tuning:**\n\n**Production config.ini:**\n```\n[scope]\nport = 80,443,8080,8443\nasn = 15169,13335\n\n[scope.domains]\ndomain = target.com\n\n[scope.blacklist]\nsubdomain = test.target.com\n\n[resolvers]\nresolver = 1.1.1.1\nresolver = 8.8.8.8\nresolver = 9.9.9.9\n\n[bruteforce]\nenabled = true\nrecursive = true\nminimum_for_recursive = 2\nwordlist_file = /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt\n\n[alterations]\nenabled = true\nminimum_for_word_flip = 2\nedit_distance = 1\n\n[data_sources]\nminimum_ttl = 1440\n\n[data_sources.VirusTotal.Credentials]\napikey = YOUR_VT_KEY\n\n[data_sources.Shodan.Credentials]\napikey = YOUR_SHODAN_KEY\n```\n\n**6. Amass Verilerini SIEM / CTI Platformlarına Aktarma:**\n\n**JSON to Splunk:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -json output.json\ncat output.json | jq -c '{time: .timestamp, source: .sources[], domain: .name, ip: .addresses[]?.ip}' | curl -X POST https://splunk:8088/services/collector -H "Authorization: Splunk TOKEN" -d @-\n```\n\n**CSV export:**\n```\namass db -dir output -show -d target.com | awk '{print $1","$2","$3}' > export.csv\n```\n\n**7. DNS Resolver Doğruluğu:**\n\n**Trusted resolvers:**\n```\n1.1.1.1         # Cloudflare\n8.8.8.8         # Google\n9.9.9.9         # Quad9\n208.67.222.222  # OpenDNS\n```\n\n**Validation:**\n```\n# Test resolvers\nwhile read resolver; do\n  dig @$resolver target.com +short || echo "Failed: $resolver"\ndone < resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**8. Recursive Depth Yönetimi:**\n\n**Shallow (fast):**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 5 -max-depth 2\n```\n\n**Medium:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 3 -max-depth 5\n```\n\n**Deep (comprehensive):**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 1 -max-depth 10\n```\n\n**9. Grafik Çıktıların Analiz Edilmesi (viz):**\n\n**D3 interactive:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -dir output\namass viz -d3 -dir output -o graph.html\n# Browser'da aç: firefox graph.html\n```\n\n**Graphviz analysis:**\n```\namass viz -dot -dir output | dot -Tpng -o graph.png\namass viz -dot -dir output | dot -Tsvg -o graph.svg\n```\n\n**Network analysis:**\n```\namass viz -gexf -dir output\n# Import to Gephi for network analysis\n```\n\n**10. Rate-Limit Uyumlu Optimizasyon:**\n\n**Detection:**\n```\n# Monitor for rate limiting\namass enum -d target.com -log amass.log -dns-qps 200\ngrep -i "rate" amass.log\n```\n\n**Adaptive:**\n```\n# Start low\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 50\n\n# Increase if no errors\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 100\n\n# Max stable\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 200 -rf trusted.txt\n```\n\n**11. Attack Surface Management Pipeline:**\n\n**Continuous monitoring:**\n```\n#!/bin/bash\nDOMAIN="target.com"\nBASELINE_DIR="/var/amass/baseline"\nCURRENT_DIR="/var/amass/current_$(date +%Y%m%d)"\n\n# Initial baseline (first run only)\nif [ ! -d "$BASELINE_DIR" ]; then\n  amass enum -d $DOMAIN -config config.ini -dir $BASELINE_DIR -oA baseline\nfi\n\n# Current scan\namass enum -d $DOMAIN -config config.ini -dir $CURRENT_DIR -oA current\n\n# Track changes\namass track -d $DOMAIN -dir $BASELINE_DIR > changes.txt\n\n# Alert on new subdomains\nNEW=$(grep "^+" changes.txt | wc -l)\nif [ $NEW -gt 0 ]; then\n  echo "New subdomains detected: $NEW"\n  grep "^+" changes.txt | mail -s "New Assets Detected" security@target.com\nfi\n\n# Update baseline\ncp -r $CURRENT_DIR/* $BASELINE_DIR/\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. Sadece pasif keşif yapıp eksik sonuç almak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (pasif only)\namass enum -passive -d target.com\n\n# DOĞRU (hybrid)\namass enum -d target.com -active -config api-keys.ini\n```\n\n**2. Varsayılan resolvers kullanmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (system resolvers)\namass enum -d target.com\n\n# DOĞRU (custom resolvers)\namass enum -d target.com -rf trusted-resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**3. Recursive threshold yanlış ayarlanması:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (çok yüksek, recursive çalışmaz)\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 10\n\n# DOĞRU (dengeli)\namass enum -d target.com -min-for-recursive 2\n```\n\n**4. Yetersiz wordlist seçimi:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (çok küçük)\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w small-list.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (comprehensive)\namass enum -brute -d target.com -w /usr/share/amass/wordlists/all.txt\n```\n\n**5. API keysiz pasif keşfe güvenmek:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (limited results)\namass enum -passive -d target.com\n\n# DOĞRU (API-powered)\namass enum -passive -d target.com -config api-keys.ini\n```\n\n**6. Rate-limit aşımı:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (aggressive, rate-limited)\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 1000\n\n# DOĞRU (optimized)\namass enum -d target.com -dns-qps 200 -rf resolvers.txt\n```\n\n**7. Alan adı zinciri (CNAME) yanlış yorumlama:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (sadece subdomain listesi)\namass enum -d target.com -o results.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (resolution + CNAME mapping)\namass enum -d target.com -active -dir output\namass db -dir output -show | grep CNAME\n```\n\n**8. JSON çıktısı oluşturmamak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (sadece text)\namass enum -d target.com -o results.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (JSON for parsing)\namass enum -d target.com -json results.json -o results.txt\n```\n\n**9. Aktif modda firewall tetikleme:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (aggressive active)\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 500\n\n# DOĞRU (stealth)\namass enum -active -d target.com -dns-qps 50 -timeout 10 -rate 10\n```\n\n**10. Output directory kullanmamak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (data loss, no database)\namass enum -d target.com -o results.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (persistent database)\namass enum -d target.com -dir project_enum -oA results\n```\n\n## Data Sources Referansı\n\n**Pasif kaynaklar:**\n```\ncrtsh              # Certificate Transparency logs\nvirustotal         # VirusTotal passive DNS\ncensys             # Censys search engine\nshodan             # Shodan search engine\nsecuritytrails     # SecurityTrails DNS history\nthreatcrowd        # ThreatCrowd\nhackertarget       # HackerTarget\nriddler            # Riddler.io\nnetcraft           # Netcraft\ndnsdumpster        # DNSDumpster\nwayback            # Wayback Machine\n```\n\n**Aktif kaynaklar:**\n```\nDNS resolution\nReverse DNS\nPort scanning\nCertificate analysis\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**List data sources:**\n```\namass enum -list\n```\n\n**Check config:**\n```\namass enum -d target.com -config config.ini -list\n```\n\n**Database operations:**\n```\namass db -dir output -list\namass db -dir output -show -d target.com\namass db -dir output -names\namass db -dir output -summary\n```\n\n**Export formats:**\n```\namass db -dir output -show -d target.com -o export.txt\namass viz -d3 -dir output -o graph.html\namass viz -dot -dir output | dot -Tpng > graph.png\n```\n\n**Version:**\n```\namass -version\n```\n\n**Help:**\n```\namass enum -h\namass intel -h\namass viz -h\namass db -h\n```\n	{amass,recon,subdomain,osint,enum}	{https://github.com/OWASP/Amass,https://owasp.org/www-project-amass/}	196	2026-01-23 22:21:30.208	2026-01-23 22:21:30.208
