627	WPScan Cheatsheet	WPScan Cheatsheet	# WPScan - WordPress Security Scanner\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n**Basit WordPress taraması:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com\n```\n\n**Plugin enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p\n```\n\n**User enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u\n```\n\n**Vulnerable plugin detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### API Token Kullanımı\n\n**API token ile zafiyet tespiti:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token YOUR_API_TOKEN\n```\n*WPVulnDB API kullanarak güncel zafiyet bilgisi alır.*\n\n**API token + aggressive scan:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate ap,at,cb,dbe --plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n\n### User Enumeration Teknikleri\n\n**Author archive enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u\n```\n*Default: Author archives üzerinden kullanıcı tespiti*\n\n**Login error message enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u --plugins-detection passive\n```\n\n**Custom user ID range:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u1-100\n```\n*User ID 1-100 arası enumerate et*\n\n**Aggressive user enum:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u --plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n\n### Password Brute-Force\n\n**Username + password list:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --usernames admin,administrator --passwords /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt\n```\n\n**User file + password list:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --usernames users.txt --passwords passwords.txt\n```\n\n**XML-RPC brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P passwords.txt --password-attack xmlrpc\n```\n\n**wp-login brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P passwords.txt --password-attack wp-login\n```\n\n**Multi-threaded brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U users.txt -P passwords.txt -t 50\n```\n\n### Plugin / Theme Discovery\n\n**Passive plugin detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --plugins-detection passive\n```\n*Düşük trafik, sadece HTML parsing*\n\n**Aggressive plugin detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n*404 check, daha kapsamlı*\n\n**All plugins enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap\n```\n\n**Vulnerable plugins only:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**Theme enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate t\n```\n\n**All themes:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate at\n```\n\n**Vulnerable themes:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vt --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n### Version Detection\n\n**WordPress version:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp,vt,u\n```\n*Version + vulnerable plugins/themes + users*\n\n**Aggressive fingerprinting:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection aggressive --enumerate ap,at,cb,dbe\n```\n\n### Aggressive Scan / Passive Scan Farkları\n\n**Passive scan (stealth):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --plugins-detection passive --stealthy\n```\n*Düşük trafik, sadece görünür bilgiler*\n\n**Aggressive scan:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt --plugins-detection aggressive -t 20\n```\n*Yüksek trafik, 404 check, brute-force*\n\n### Proxy ile Tarama\n\n**HTTP proxy:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**Proxy + authentication:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://user:pass@127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n### Custom Header Ekleme\n\n**Single header:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --headers "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1"\n```\n\n**Multiple headers:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --headers "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" --headers "X-Custom: value"\n```\n\n**Cookie-based auth:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --cookie "wordpress_logged_in=cookie_value"\n```\n\n### Custom Wordlist Kullanma\n\n**Custom password wordlist:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P /path/to/custom-passwords.txt\n```\n\n**Custom username wordlist:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --usernames /path/to/usernames.txt -P passwords.txt\n```\n\n### Request Delay / Throttle Ayarları\n\n**Request throttle (delay):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --throttle 2000\n```\n*Her istek arasında 2000ms (2 saniye) bekle*\n\n**Slow scan (WAF bypass):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --throttle 3000 -t 5 --random-user-agent\n```\n\n### WAF / Rate-Limit Bypass Yaklaşımları\n\n**Random User-Agent:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --random-user-agent\n```\n\n**Custom User-Agent:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --user-agent "Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1)"\n```\n\n**Throttle + low threads:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --throttle 5000 -t 3 --random-user-agent\n```\n\n**Stealthy mode:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --stealthy --plugins-detection passive\n```\n\n### Sadece Belirli Modülleri Çalıştırma\n\n**Sadece user enum:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u --no-banner\n```\n\n**Sadece plugin + theme:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p,t\n```\n\n**Sadece vulnerable detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp,vt --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**Config backup check:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate cb\n```\n\n**DB export check:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate dbe\n```\n\n### Output Formatları\n\n**JSON output:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format json -o results.json\n```\n\n**CLI-NO-COLOR output:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format cli-no-color -o results.txt\n```\n\n**JSON + verbose:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format json -o scan.json -v\n```\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`--url <URL>`**\n*Hedef WordPress site URL'i (zorunlu).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com\n```\n\n**`--enumerate <options>`**\n*Enumerate etmek istenen öğeler (virgülle ayır).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p,u,t\n```\n\n**Enumerate seçenekleri:**\n- `u` - Users\n- `u[ID]` - User ID range (örn: u1-100)\n- `p` - Popular plugins\n- `ap` - All plugins\n- `vp` - Vulnerable plugins\n- `t` - Popular themes\n- `at` - All themes\n- `vt` - Vulnerable themes\n- `cb` - Config backups\n- `dbe` - DB exports\n- `m` - Media IDs\n\n**`--api-token <TOKEN>`**\n*WPVulnDB API token (zafiyet tespiti için).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token YOUR_TOKEN\n```\n\n**`-U, --usernames <list>`**\n*Brute-force için kullanıcı adı listesi.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin,administrator\nwpscan --url https://target.com --usernames users.txt\n```\n\n**`-P, --passwords <file>`**\n*Brute-force için şifre wordlist dosyası.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -P passwords.txt\n```\n\n**`--password-attack <mode>`**\n*Brute-force attack modu.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --password-attack xmlrpc\n```\n*Modlar: wp-login, xmlrpc, xmlrpc-multicall*\n\n**`-t, --max-threads <num>`**\n*Maksimum thread sayısı (default: 5).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -t 20\n```\n\n**`--throttle <ms>`**\n*İstekler arasında bekleme süresi (milisaniye).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --throttle 2000\n```\n\n**`--plugins-detection <mode>`**\n*Plugin tespit modu.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n*Modlar: mixed, passive, aggressive*\n\n**`--proxy <proxy>`**\n*Proxy server kullan.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**`--headers <header>`**\n*Custom HTTP header ekle (multiple kullanılabilir).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --headers "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1"\n```\n\n**`--cookie <cookie>`**\n*Cookie string gönder.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --cookie "session=abc123"\n```\n\n**`--random-user-agent`**\n*Her istekte rastgele User-Agent kullan.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --random-user-agent\n```\n\n**`--user-agent <ua>`**\n*Custom User-Agent belirt.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --user-agent "CustomBot/1.0"\n```\n\n**`--stealthy`**\n*Stealth mode: passive detection + low threads.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --stealthy\n```\n\n**`--ignore-main-redirect`**\n*Ana sayfa redirect'lerini yoksay.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --ignore-main-redirect\n```\n\n**`--disable-tls-checks`**\n*SSL/TLS sertifika doğrulamasını kapat.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --disable-tls-checks\n```\n\n**`--force`**\n*WordPress olmayan sitelerde taramayı zorla.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://maybe-wp.com --force\n```\n\n**`-v, --verbose`**\n*Verbose output.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -v\n```\n\n**`--format <format>`**\n*Output formatı.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format json\n```\n*Formatlar: cli, cli-no-color, json*\n\n**`-o, --output <file>`**\n*Sonuçları dosyaya kaydet.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n**`--no-banner`**\n*Banner gösterme.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --no-banner\n```\n\n**`--no-update`**\n*Başlangıçta update kontrolü yapma.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --no-update\n```\n\n**`--wp-content-dir <dir>`**\n*Custom wp-content dizini.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --wp-content-dir custom-content\n```\n\n**`--wp-plugins-dir <dir>`**\n*Custom wp-plugins dizini.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --wp-plugins-dir custom-plugins\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Temel WordPress taraması:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com\n```\n*--url: Hedef site. Default: WordPress version, theme, ve bazı plugin'leri tespit eder.*\n\n**Kapsamlı enumeration (API token ile):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt,cb,dbe\n```\n*--api-token: WPVulnDB erişimi, --enumerate ap: Tüm plugin'ler, at: Tüm theme'ler, u: Kullanıcılar, vp: Vulnerable plugins, vt: Vulnerable themes, cb: Config backups, dbe: DB exports*\n\n**User enumeration + brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u -U users.txt -P /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt -t 50\n```\n*--enumerate u: Kullanıcıları tespit et, -U: Kullanıcı listesi, -P: Şifre wordlist, -t 50: 50 thread*\n\n**Stealth tarama (WAF bypass):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --stealthy --random-user-agent --throttle 3000 --enumerate p\n```\n*--stealthy: Düşük trafik modu, --random-user-agent: UA rotation, --throttle 3000: 3 saniye delay, --enumerate p: Popular plugins*\n\n**Proxy üzerinden aggressive scan:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080 --enumerate ap,at --plugins-detection aggressive -t 20\n```\n*--proxy: Burp proxy, --enumerate ap,at: Tüm plugin/theme, --plugins-detection aggressive: 404 check, -t 20: 20 thread*\n\n**XML-RPC brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin --passwords passwords.txt --password-attack xmlrpc --throttle 1000\n```\n*-U admin: Admin kullanıcısı, --password-attack xmlrpc: XML-RPC multicall, --throttle 1000: 1 saniye delay*\n\n**Plugin vulnerability check:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp --format json -o vulnerabilities.json\n```\n*--api-token: API erişimi, --enumerate vp: Sadece vulnerable plugins, --format json: JSON çıktı, -o: Dosyaya kaydet*\n\n**Custom header + cookie authentication:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --headers "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" --cookie "session=xyz" --enumerate u\n```\n*--headers: Custom header, --cookie: Auth cookie, --enumerate u: User enumeration*\n\n**Specific user ID range:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u1-500\n```\n*--enumerate u1-500: User ID 1'den 500'e kadar enumerate et*\n\n**Config backup detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate cb --verbose\n```\n*--enumerate cb: wp-config.php backups, --verbose: Detaylı çıktı*\n\n**DB export detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate dbe\n```\n*--enumerate dbe: Database dump dosyaları (wp-content/backup-db/, etc.)*\n\n**All-in-one aggressive scan:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt,cb,dbe --plugins-detection aggressive -t 30 --random-user-agent -o full-scan.json --format json\n```\n*Tüm modüller aktif, aggressive detection, 30 thread, UA rotation, JSON output*\n\n**Passive reconnaissance:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection passive --enumerate p,t,u --no-banner -o passive-scan.txt\n```\n*--plugins-detection passive: Sadece HTML parse, aktif istek yok, --no-banner: Banner gizle*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Kurumsal WordPress Hızlı Asset Analizi\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://corporate-site.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp,vt,u --plugins-detection mixed --format json -o asset-analysis.json\n```\n*Vulnerable plugin/theme + users, mixed detection (hız + kapsam dengesi)*\n\n**Sonuç analizi:**\n```\ncat asset-analysis.json | jq '.version.number'\ncat asset-analysis.json | jq '.plugins[] | select(.vulnerabilities != [])'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: Plugin Zafiyetlerinin Sürüm Bazlı Doğrulanması\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp --plugins-detection aggressive --verbose\n```\n*Aggressive plugin detection + API zafiyet karşılaştırması*\n\n**Örnek çıktı:**\n```\n[+] contact-form-7 version 5.1.9 (out of date, latest is 5.8)\n | [!] 3 vulnerabilities identified:\n | [!] CVE-2020-35489 - File Upload\n```\n\n### Senaryo 3: Admin Hesabı Brute-Force\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u -U admin,administrator --passwords /usr/share/seclists/Passwords/Common-Credentials/10-million-password-list-top-10000.txt --password-attack xmlrpc -t 20 --throttle 500\n```\n*User enum + multi-threaded brute-force, XML-RPC multicall (hızlı)*\n\n**Rate-limit koruması varsa:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P passwords.txt --password-attack wp-login -t 5 --throttle 3000 --random-user-agent\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: WAF Arkasındaki WordPress Enumeration\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://waf-protected.com --stealthy --random-user-agent --headers "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1" --throttle 5000 --enumerate p,t --plugins-detection passive --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n*Stealth mode, UA rotation, IP spoofing header, 5 saniye delay, passive detection, Burp proxy*\n\n### Senaryo 5: Red-Team OSINT Amaçlı Subsite Taramaları\n\n```\n# Multiple site tarama script\nfor site in $(cat wordpress-sites.txt); do\n  wpscan --url $site --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp,vt,u --format json -o results/${site//\\//_}.json --no-banner\ndone\n```\n*Batch tarama, her site için JSON rapor*\n\n**Toplu analiz:**\n```\ncat results/*.json | jq -r '.version.number' | sort | uniq -c\n```\n\n### Senaryo 6: Büyük Wordlist ile Kontrollü Brute-Force\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin --passwords /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt --password-attack xmlrpc -t 10 --throttle 2000 --max-scan-duration 3600\n```\n*14M+ password, 10 thread, 2 saniye delay, 1 saat max duration*\n\n**Progress monitoring:**\n```\n# Terminal 2'de:\ntail -f ~/.wpscan/scan.log | grep -i "valid"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 7: Theme Backdoor Detection\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate at --plugins-detection aggressive --api-token TOKEN --verbose\n```\n*Tüm theme'leri tespit + zafiyet kontrolü*\n\n**Manuel doğrulama:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/themes/suspicious-theme/footer.php\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. API Kullanımıyla Zafiyet Doğrulama:**\n\n**API token alın:**\n```\n# https://wpscan.com/register adresinden ücretsiz token\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token YOUR_TOKEN\n```\n\n**Zafiyet raporlama:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp,vt --format json -o report.json\n```\n\n**JSON parse:**\n```\ncat report.json | jq '.plugins[] | select(.vulnerabilities != []) | {name: .slug, version: .version.number, vulns: .vulnerabilities[].title}'\n```\n\n**2. Yavaş Sitede Doğru Thread/Delay Ayarı:**\n\n**İlk test:**\n```\ntime curl -I https://slow-site.com\n# Response: 3.5 seconds\n```\n\n**Optimum ayarlar:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://slow-site.com -t 3 --throttle 4000 --request-timeout 10\n```\n*3 thread, 4 saniye delay, 10 saniye timeout*\n\n**3. False Positive Azaltma:**\n\n**Baseline belirleme:**\n```\n# 404 response kontrolü\ncurl -I https://target.com/definitely-nonexistent-plugin-12345/\n```\n\n**Aggressive + verification:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap --plugins-detection aggressive --verbose\n```\n\n**Manuel doğrulama:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/plugins/detected-plugin/readme.txt\n```\n\n**4. User-Agent Rotasyonu:**\n\n**Random UA:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --random-user-agent --enumerate p\n```\n\n**Custom UA (bot bypass):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --user-agent "Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1; +http://www.google.com/bot.html)"\n```\n\n**5. Plugin/Theme Verilerini Manuel Doğrulama:**\n\n**readme.txt kontrolü:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/plugins/plugin-name/readme.txt | grep "Stable tag"\n```\n\n**Changelog kontrolü:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/themes/theme-name/style.css | grep "Version"\n```\n\n**Directory listing check:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/plugins/\n```\n\n**6. Rate-Limit Handling:**\n\n**Adaptive throttling:**\n```\n# Başlangıç\nwpscan --url https://target.com -t 20 --throttle 1000\n\n# Rate-limit detection (429, 503)\n# Ayarı düşür:\nwpscan --url https://target.com -t 5 --throttle 3000\n```\n\n**7. Comprehensive Enumeration Strategy:**\n\n**Aşama 1: Passive recon**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection passive --enumerate p,t,u\n```\n\n**Aşama 2: Aggressive enum**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection aggressive --enumerate ap,at --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**Aşama 3: Vulnerability verification**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp,vt --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**8. Output Management:**\n\n**Structured logging:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format json -o scan-$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M).json\n```\n\n**Filtered output:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp | grep -A 5 "vulnerabilities"\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. URL format hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwpscan --url target.com\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com\n```\n*Protocol (http/https) gerekli*\n\n**2. API token olmadan zafiyet tespiti:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (sınırlı zafiyet bilgisi)\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**3. Aggressive scan rate-limit:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (rate-limit / IP ban)\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap -t 50\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap -t 10 --throttle 2000 --random-user-agent\n```\n\n**4. Brute-force without throttle:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (lockout risk)\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P huge-wordlist.txt -t 50\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P wordlist.txt -t 10 --throttle 2000\n```\n\n**5. SSL/TLS verification error:**\n```\n# Hata: SSL certificate problem\n# Çözüm:\nwpscan --url https://self-signed.com --disable-tls-checks\n```\n\n**6. Enumerate syntax hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate all\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt,cb,dbe\n```\n\n**7. Password file path hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (dosya bulunamadı)\nwpscan --url https://target.com -P passwords.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (absolute path)\nwpscan --url https://target.com -P /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt\n```\n\n**8. Redirect ignore unutmak:**\n```\n# Site redirect yapıyorsa (örn: https'e yönlendirme)\nwpscan --url http://target.com --ignore-main-redirect\n```\n\n**9. Output overwrite:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (önceki scan üzerine yazar)\nwpscan --url https://site1.com -o results.json\nwpscan --url https://site2.com -o results.json\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://site1.com -o site1-results.json\nwpscan --url https://site2.com -o site2-results.json\n```\n\n**10. Proxy authentication eksikliği:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (proxy auth gerekiyorsa)\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://user:pass@127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n## Enumerate Options Detay\n\n**Users (u):**\n```\n--enumerate u        # Default user enumeration\n--enumerate u1-100   # User ID 1-100\n--enumerate u[1,5,10,25]  # Specific user IDs\n```\n\n**Plugins (p):**\n```\n--enumerate p   # Popular plugins (~100)\n--enumerate ap  # All plugins (~80,000+)\n--enumerate vp  # Only vulnerable plugins (API token gerekli)\n```\n\n**Themes (t):**\n```\n--enumerate t   # Popular themes\n--enumerate at  # All themes\n--enumerate vt  # Only vulnerable themes (API token gerekli)\n```\n\n**Other:**\n```\n--enumerate cb  # Config backups (wp-config.php~, etc.)\n--enumerate dbe # DB exports (*.sql, *.sql.gz, etc.)\n--enumerate m   # Media IDs (attachment enumeration)\n```\n\n**Combination:**\n```\n--enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt,cb,dbe  # Full enumeration\n```\n\n## Password Attack Modes\n\n**wp-login:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --password-attack wp-login\n```\n*Standard wp-login.php brute-force*\n\n**xmlrpc:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --password-attack xmlrpc\n```\n*XML-RPC single request*\n\n**xmlrpc-multicall:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --password-attack xmlrpc-multicall\n```\n*XML-RPC multicall (hızlı, multiple password tek istekte)*\n\n## Plugins Detection Modes\n\n**passive:**\n```\n--plugins-detection passive\n```\n*Sadece HTML parsing, aktif istek yok*\n\n**aggressive:**\n```\n--plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n*404 check, directory listing, readme.txt kontrolü*\n\n**mixed:**\n```\n--plugins-detection mixed\n```\n*Default: passive + aggressive (dengeli)*\n\n## Output Formats\n\n**cli:**\n```\n--format cli -o results.txt\n```\n*Standart renkli terminal çıktısı*\n\n**cli-no-color:**\n```\n--format cli-no-color -o results.txt\n```\n*Renksiz text (log dosyaları için)*\n\n**json:**\n```\n--format json -o results.json\n```\n*JSON format (programmatic parsing)*\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**Hızlı zafiyet kontrolü:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp,vt --format json | jq '.plugins[] | select(.vulnerabilities != [])'\n```\n\n**User + brute-force kombine:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u -U $(wpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u --format json | jq -r '.users | keys[]') -P passwords.txt\n```\n\n**Batch scanning:**\n```\nwhile read url; do\n  wpscan --url $url --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp --format json -o ${url//\\//_}.json\ndone < urls.txt\n```\n\n**Custom wp-content path:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --wp-content-dir custom-content\n```\n\n**Plugin version extraction:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --format json | jq -r '.plugins[] | "\\(.slug): \\(.version.number)"'\n```\n	# WPScan - WordPress Security Scanner\n\n## Temel Kullanım\n\n**Basit WordPress taraması:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com\n```\n\n**Plugin enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p\n```\n\n**User enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u\n```\n\n**Vulnerable plugin detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp\n```\n\n## İleri Seviye Kullanım\n\n### API Token Kullanımı\n\n**API token ile zafiyet tespiti:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token YOUR_API_TOKEN\n```\n*WPVulnDB API kullanarak güncel zafiyet bilgisi alır.*\n\n**API token + aggressive scan:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate ap,at,cb,dbe --plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n\n### User Enumeration Teknikleri\n\n**Author archive enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u\n```\n*Default: Author archives üzerinden kullanıcı tespiti*\n\n**Login error message enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u --plugins-detection passive\n```\n\n**Custom user ID range:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u1-100\n```\n*User ID 1-100 arası enumerate et*\n\n**Aggressive user enum:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u --plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n\n### Password Brute-Force\n\n**Username + password list:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --usernames admin,administrator --passwords /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt\n```\n\n**User file + password list:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --usernames users.txt --passwords passwords.txt\n```\n\n**XML-RPC brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P passwords.txt --password-attack xmlrpc\n```\n\n**wp-login brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P passwords.txt --password-attack wp-login\n```\n\n**Multi-threaded brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U users.txt -P passwords.txt -t 50\n```\n\n### Plugin / Theme Discovery\n\n**Passive plugin detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --plugins-detection passive\n```\n*Düşük trafik, sadece HTML parsing*\n\n**Aggressive plugin detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n*404 check, daha kapsamlı*\n\n**All plugins enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap\n```\n\n**Vulnerable plugins only:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**Theme enumeration:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate t\n```\n\n**All themes:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate at\n```\n\n**Vulnerable themes:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vt --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n### Version Detection\n\n**WordPress version:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp,vt,u\n```\n*Version + vulnerable plugins/themes + users*\n\n**Aggressive fingerprinting:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection aggressive --enumerate ap,at,cb,dbe\n```\n\n### Aggressive Scan / Passive Scan Farkları\n\n**Passive scan (stealth):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --plugins-detection passive --stealthy\n```\n*Düşük trafik, sadece görünür bilgiler*\n\n**Aggressive scan:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt --plugins-detection aggressive -t 20\n```\n*Yüksek trafik, 404 check, brute-force*\n\n### Proxy ile Tarama\n\n**HTTP proxy:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n**SOCKS proxy:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**Proxy + authentication:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://user:pass@127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n### Custom Header Ekleme\n\n**Single header:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --headers "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1"\n```\n\n**Multiple headers:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --headers "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" --headers "X-Custom: value"\n```\n\n**Cookie-based auth:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --cookie "wordpress_logged_in=cookie_value"\n```\n\n### Custom Wordlist Kullanma\n\n**Custom password wordlist:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P /path/to/custom-passwords.txt\n```\n\n**Custom username wordlist:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --usernames /path/to/usernames.txt -P passwords.txt\n```\n\n### Request Delay / Throttle Ayarları\n\n**Request throttle (delay):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --throttle 2000\n```\n*Her istek arasında 2000ms (2 saniye) bekle*\n\n**Slow scan (WAF bypass):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --throttle 3000 -t 5 --random-user-agent\n```\n\n### WAF / Rate-Limit Bypass Yaklaşımları\n\n**Random User-Agent:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --random-user-agent\n```\n\n**Custom User-Agent:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --user-agent "Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1)"\n```\n\n**Throttle + low threads:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --throttle 5000 -t 3 --random-user-agent\n```\n\n**Stealthy mode:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --stealthy --plugins-detection passive\n```\n\n### Sadece Belirli Modülleri Çalıştırma\n\n**Sadece user enum:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u --no-banner\n```\n\n**Sadece plugin + theme:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p,t\n```\n\n**Sadece vulnerable detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp,vt --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**Config backup check:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate cb\n```\n\n**DB export check:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate dbe\n```\n\n### Output Formatları\n\n**JSON output:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format json -o results.json\n```\n\n**CLI-NO-COLOR output:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format cli-no-color -o results.txt\n```\n\n**JSON + verbose:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format json -o scan.json -v\n```\n\n## Argument Referansı\n\n### Temel Argümanlar\n\n**`--url <URL>`**\n*Hedef WordPress site URL'i (zorunlu).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com\n```\n\n**`--enumerate <options>`**\n*Enumerate etmek istenen öğeler (virgülle ayır).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p,u,t\n```\n\n**Enumerate seçenekleri:**\n- `u` - Users\n- `u[ID]` - User ID range (örn: u1-100)\n- `p` - Popular plugins\n- `ap` - All plugins\n- `vp` - Vulnerable plugins\n- `t` - Popular themes\n- `at` - All themes\n- `vt` - Vulnerable themes\n- `cb` - Config backups\n- `dbe` - DB exports\n- `m` - Media IDs\n\n**`--api-token <TOKEN>`**\n*WPVulnDB API token (zafiyet tespiti için).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token YOUR_TOKEN\n```\n\n**`-U, --usernames <list>`**\n*Brute-force için kullanıcı adı listesi.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin,administrator\nwpscan --url https://target.com --usernames users.txt\n```\n\n**`-P, --passwords <file>`**\n*Brute-force için şifre wordlist dosyası.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -P passwords.txt\n```\n\n**`--password-attack <mode>`**\n*Brute-force attack modu.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --password-attack xmlrpc\n```\n*Modlar: wp-login, xmlrpc, xmlrpc-multicall*\n\n**`-t, --max-threads <num>`**\n*Maksimum thread sayısı (default: 5).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -t 20\n```\n\n**`--throttle <ms>`**\n*İstekler arasında bekleme süresi (milisaniye).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --throttle 2000\n```\n\n**`--plugins-detection <mode>`**\n*Plugin tespit modu.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n*Modlar: mixed, passive, aggressive*\n\n**`--proxy <proxy>`**\n*Proxy server kullan.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy socks5://127.0.0.1:9050\n```\n\n**`--headers <header>`**\n*Custom HTTP header ekle (multiple kullanılabilir).*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --headers "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1"\n```\n\n**`--cookie <cookie>`**\n*Cookie string gönder.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --cookie "session=abc123"\n```\n\n**`--random-user-agent`**\n*Her istekte rastgele User-Agent kullan.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --random-user-agent\n```\n\n**`--user-agent <ua>`**\n*Custom User-Agent belirt.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --user-agent "CustomBot/1.0"\n```\n\n**`--stealthy`**\n*Stealth mode: passive detection + low threads.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --stealthy\n```\n\n**`--ignore-main-redirect`**\n*Ana sayfa redirect'lerini yoksay.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --ignore-main-redirect\n```\n\n**`--disable-tls-checks`**\n*SSL/TLS sertifika doğrulamasını kapat.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --disable-tls-checks\n```\n\n**`--force`**\n*WordPress olmayan sitelerde taramayı zorla.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://maybe-wp.com --force\n```\n\n**`-v, --verbose`**\n*Verbose output.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -v\n```\n\n**`--format <format>`**\n*Output formatı.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format json\n```\n*Formatlar: cli, cli-no-color, json*\n\n**`-o, --output <file>`**\n*Sonuçları dosyaya kaydet.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -o results.txt\n```\n\n**`--no-banner`**\n*Banner gösterme.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --no-banner\n```\n\n**`--no-update`**\n*Başlangıçta update kontrolü yapma.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --no-update\n```\n\n**`--wp-content-dir <dir>`**\n*Custom wp-content dizini.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --wp-content-dir custom-content\n```\n\n**`--wp-plugins-dir <dir>`**\n*Custom wp-plugins dizini.*\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --wp-plugins-dir custom-plugins\n```\n\n## Açıklamalı Komutlar\n\n**Temel WordPress taraması:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com\n```\n*--url: Hedef site. Default: WordPress version, theme, ve bazı plugin'leri tespit eder.*\n\n**Kapsamlı enumeration (API token ile):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt,cb,dbe\n```\n*--api-token: WPVulnDB erişimi, --enumerate ap: Tüm plugin'ler, at: Tüm theme'ler, u: Kullanıcılar, vp: Vulnerable plugins, vt: Vulnerable themes, cb: Config backups, dbe: DB exports*\n\n**User enumeration + brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u -U users.txt -P /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt -t 50\n```\n*--enumerate u: Kullanıcıları tespit et, -U: Kullanıcı listesi, -P: Şifre wordlist, -t 50: 50 thread*\n\n**Stealth tarama (WAF bypass):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --stealthy --random-user-agent --throttle 3000 --enumerate p\n```\n*--stealthy: Düşük trafik modu, --random-user-agent: UA rotation, --throttle 3000: 3 saniye delay, --enumerate p: Popular plugins*\n\n**Proxy üzerinden aggressive scan:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080 --enumerate ap,at --plugins-detection aggressive -t 20\n```\n*--proxy: Burp proxy, --enumerate ap,at: Tüm plugin/theme, --plugins-detection aggressive: 404 check, -t 20: 20 thread*\n\n**XML-RPC brute-force:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin --passwords passwords.txt --password-attack xmlrpc --throttle 1000\n```\n*-U admin: Admin kullanıcısı, --password-attack xmlrpc: XML-RPC multicall, --throttle 1000: 1 saniye delay*\n\n**Plugin vulnerability check:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp --format json -o vulnerabilities.json\n```\n*--api-token: API erişimi, --enumerate vp: Sadece vulnerable plugins, --format json: JSON çıktı, -o: Dosyaya kaydet*\n\n**Custom header + cookie authentication:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --headers "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" --cookie "session=xyz" --enumerate u\n```\n*--headers: Custom header, --cookie: Auth cookie, --enumerate u: User enumeration*\n\n**Specific user ID range:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u1-500\n```\n*--enumerate u1-500: User ID 1'den 500'e kadar enumerate et*\n\n**Config backup detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate cb --verbose\n```\n*--enumerate cb: wp-config.php backups, --verbose: Detaylı çıktı*\n\n**DB export detection:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate dbe\n```\n*--enumerate dbe: Database dump dosyaları (wp-content/backup-db/, etc.)*\n\n**All-in-one aggressive scan:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt,cb,dbe --plugins-detection aggressive -t 30 --random-user-agent -o full-scan.json --format json\n```\n*Tüm modüller aktif, aggressive detection, 30 thread, UA rotation, JSON output*\n\n**Passive reconnaissance:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection passive --enumerate p,t,u --no-banner -o passive-scan.txt\n```\n*--plugins-detection passive: Sadece HTML parse, aktif istek yok, --no-banner: Banner gizle*\n\n## Gerçek Pentest Senaryoları\n\n### Senaryo 1: Kurumsal WordPress Hızlı Asset Analizi\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://corporate-site.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp,vt,u --plugins-detection mixed --format json -o asset-analysis.json\n```\n*Vulnerable plugin/theme + users, mixed detection (hız + kapsam dengesi)*\n\n**Sonuç analizi:**\n```\ncat asset-analysis.json | jq '.version.number'\ncat asset-analysis.json | jq '.plugins[] | select(.vulnerabilities != [])'\n```\n\n### Senaryo 2: Plugin Zafiyetlerinin Sürüm Bazlı Doğrulanması\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp --plugins-detection aggressive --verbose\n```\n*Aggressive plugin detection + API zafiyet karşılaştırması*\n\n**Örnek çıktı:**\n```\n[+] contact-form-7 version 5.1.9 (out of date, latest is 5.8)\n | [!] 3 vulnerabilities identified:\n | [!] CVE-2020-35489 - File Upload\n```\n\n### Senaryo 3: Admin Hesabı Brute-Force\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u -U admin,administrator --passwords /usr/share/seclists/Passwords/Common-Credentials/10-million-password-list-top-10000.txt --password-attack xmlrpc -t 20 --throttle 500\n```\n*User enum + multi-threaded brute-force, XML-RPC multicall (hızlı)*\n\n**Rate-limit koruması varsa:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P passwords.txt --password-attack wp-login -t 5 --throttle 3000 --random-user-agent\n```\n\n### Senaryo 4: WAF Arkasındaki WordPress Enumeration\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://waf-protected.com --stealthy --random-user-agent --headers "X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1" --throttle 5000 --enumerate p,t --plugins-detection passive --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n*Stealth mode, UA rotation, IP spoofing header, 5 saniye delay, passive detection, Burp proxy*\n\n### Senaryo 5: Red-Team OSINT Amaçlı Subsite Taramaları\n\n```\n# Multiple site tarama script\nfor site in $(cat wordpress-sites.txt); do\n  wpscan --url $site --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp,vt,u --format json -o results/${site//\\//_}.json --no-banner\ndone\n```\n*Batch tarama, her site için JSON rapor*\n\n**Toplu analiz:**\n```\ncat results/*.json | jq -r '.version.number' | sort | uniq -c\n```\n\n### Senaryo 6: Büyük Wordlist ile Kontrollü Brute-Force\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin --passwords /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt --password-attack xmlrpc -t 10 --throttle 2000 --max-scan-duration 3600\n```\n*14M+ password, 10 thread, 2 saniye delay, 1 saat max duration*\n\n**Progress monitoring:**\n```\n# Terminal 2'de:\ntail -f ~/.wpscan/scan.log | grep -i "valid"\n```\n\n### Senaryo 7: Theme Backdoor Detection\n\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate at --plugins-detection aggressive --api-token TOKEN --verbose\n```\n*Tüm theme'leri tespit + zafiyet kontrolü*\n\n**Manuel doğrulama:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/themes/suspicious-theme/footer.php\n```\n\n## Best Practices\n\n**1. API Kullanımıyla Zafiyet Doğrulama:**\n\n**API token alın:**\n```\n# https://wpscan.com/register adresinden ücretsiz token\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token YOUR_TOKEN\n```\n\n**Zafiyet raporlama:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp,vt --format json -o report.json\n```\n\n**JSON parse:**\n```\ncat report.json | jq '.plugins[] | select(.vulnerabilities != []) | {name: .slug, version: .version.number, vulns: .vulnerabilities[].title}'\n```\n\n**2. Yavaş Sitede Doğru Thread/Delay Ayarı:**\n\n**İlk test:**\n```\ntime curl -I https://slow-site.com\n# Response: 3.5 seconds\n```\n\n**Optimum ayarlar:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://slow-site.com -t 3 --throttle 4000 --request-timeout 10\n```\n*3 thread, 4 saniye delay, 10 saniye timeout*\n\n**3. False Positive Azaltma:**\n\n**Baseline belirleme:**\n```\n# 404 response kontrolü\ncurl -I https://target.com/definitely-nonexistent-plugin-12345/\n```\n\n**Aggressive + verification:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap --plugins-detection aggressive --verbose\n```\n\n**Manuel doğrulama:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/plugins/detected-plugin/readme.txt\n```\n\n**4. User-Agent Rotasyonu:**\n\n**Random UA:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --random-user-agent --enumerate p\n```\n\n**Custom UA (bot bypass):**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --user-agent "Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Googlebot/2.1; +http://www.google.com/bot.html)"\n```\n\n**5. Plugin/Theme Verilerini Manuel Doğrulama:**\n\n**readme.txt kontrolü:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/plugins/plugin-name/readme.txt | grep "Stable tag"\n```\n\n**Changelog kontrolü:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/themes/theme-name/style.css | grep "Version"\n```\n\n**Directory listing check:**\n```\ncurl https://target.com/wp-content/plugins/\n```\n\n**6. Rate-Limit Handling:**\n\n**Adaptive throttling:**\n```\n# Başlangıç\nwpscan --url https://target.com -t 20 --throttle 1000\n\n# Rate-limit detection (429, 503)\n# Ayarı düşür:\nwpscan --url https://target.com -t 5 --throttle 3000\n```\n\n**7. Comprehensive Enumeration Strategy:**\n\n**Aşama 1: Passive recon**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection passive --enumerate p,t,u\n```\n\n**Aşama 2: Aggressive enum**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --plugins-detection aggressive --enumerate ap,at --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**Aşama 3: Vulnerability verification**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp,vt --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**8. Output Management:**\n\n**Structured logging:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --format json -o scan-$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M).json\n```\n\n**Filtered output:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp | grep -A 5 "vulnerabilities"\n```\n\n## Sık Yapılan Hatalar\n\n**1. URL format hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwpscan --url target.com\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com\n```\n*Protocol (http/https) gerekli*\n\n**2. API token olmadan zafiyet tespiti:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (sınırlı zafiyet bilgisi)\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate vp --api-token TOKEN\n```\n\n**3. Aggressive scan rate-limit:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (rate-limit / IP ban)\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap -t 50\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap -t 10 --throttle 2000 --random-user-agent\n```\n\n**4. Brute-force without throttle:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (lockout risk)\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P huge-wordlist.txt -t 50\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com -U admin -P wordlist.txt -t 10 --throttle 2000\n```\n\n**5. SSL/TLS verification error:**\n```\n# Hata: SSL certificate problem\n# Çözüm:\nwpscan --url https://self-signed.com --disable-tls-checks\n```\n\n**6. Enumerate syntax hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate all\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt,cb,dbe\n```\n\n**7. Password file path hatası:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (dosya bulunamadı)\nwpscan --url https://target.com -P passwords.txt\n\n# DOĞRU (absolute path)\nwpscan --url https://target.com -P /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt\n```\n\n**8. Redirect ignore unutmak:**\n```\n# Site redirect yapıyorsa (örn: https'e yönlendirme)\nwpscan --url http://target.com --ignore-main-redirect\n```\n\n**9. Output overwrite:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (önceki scan üzerine yazar)\nwpscan --url https://site1.com -o results.json\nwpscan --url https://site2.com -o results.json\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://site1.com -o site1-results.json\nwpscan --url https://site2.com -o site2-results.json\n```\n\n**10. Proxy authentication eksikliği:**\n```\n# YANLIŞ (proxy auth gerekiyorsa)\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8080\n\n# DOĞRU\nwpscan --url https://target.com --proxy http://user:pass@127.0.0.1:8080\n```\n\n## Enumerate Options Detay\n\n**Users (u):**\n```\n--enumerate u        # Default user enumeration\n--enumerate u1-100   # User ID 1-100\n--enumerate u[1,5,10,25]  # Specific user IDs\n```\n\n**Plugins (p):**\n```\n--enumerate p   # Popular plugins (~100)\n--enumerate ap  # All plugins (~80,000+)\n--enumerate vp  # Only vulnerable plugins (API token gerekli)\n```\n\n**Themes (t):**\n```\n--enumerate t   # Popular themes\n--enumerate at  # All themes\n--enumerate vt  # Only vulnerable themes (API token gerekli)\n```\n\n**Other:**\n```\n--enumerate cb  # Config backups (wp-config.php~, etc.)\n--enumerate dbe # DB exports (*.sql, *.sql.gz, etc.)\n--enumerate m   # Media IDs (attachment enumeration)\n```\n\n**Combination:**\n```\n--enumerate ap,at,u,vp,vt,cb,dbe  # Full enumeration\n```\n\n## Password Attack Modes\n\n**wp-login:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --password-attack wp-login\n```\n*Standard wp-login.php brute-force*\n\n**xmlrpc:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --password-attack xmlrpc\n```\n*XML-RPC single request*\n\n**xmlrpc-multicall:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --password-attack xmlrpc-multicall\n```\n*XML-RPC multicall (hızlı, multiple password tek istekte)*\n\n## Plugins Detection Modes\n\n**passive:**\n```\n--plugins-detection passive\n```\n*Sadece HTML parsing, aktif istek yok*\n\n**aggressive:**\n```\n--plugins-detection aggressive\n```\n*404 check, directory listing, readme.txt kontrolü*\n\n**mixed:**\n```\n--plugins-detection mixed\n```\n*Default: passive + aggressive (dengeli)*\n\n## Output Formats\n\n**cli:**\n```\n--format cli -o results.txt\n```\n*Standart renkli terminal çıktısı*\n\n**cli-no-color:**\n```\n--format cli-no-color -o results.txt\n```\n*Renksiz text (log dosyaları için)*\n\n**json:**\n```\n--format json -o results.json\n```\n*JSON format (programmatic parsing)*\n\n## İpuçları\n\n**Hızlı zafiyet kontrolü:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp,vt --format json | jq '.plugins[] | select(.vulnerabilities != [])'\n```\n\n**User + brute-force kombine:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u -U $(wpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate u --format json | jq -r '.users | keys[]') -P passwords.txt\n```\n\n**Batch scanning:**\n```\nwhile read url; do\n  wpscan --url $url --api-token TOKEN --enumerate vp --format json -o ${url//\\//_}.json\ndone < urls.txt\n```\n\n**Custom wp-content path:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --wp-content-dir custom-content\n```\n\n**Plugin version extraction:**\n```\nwpscan --url https://target.com --enumerate p --format json | jq -r '.plugins[] | "\\(.slug): \\(.version.number)"'\n```\n	{wpscan,wordpress,enum,vuln,security}	{https://wpscan.com/,https://github.com/wpscanteam/wpscan}	191	2026-01-23 22:21:30.357	2026-01-23 22:21:30.357
